        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><table class=\"c8\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>CHAPTER I.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000017\">I GO TO STYLES</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER II.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000332\">THE 16TH AND 17TH OF JULY</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER III.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000547\">THE NIGHT OF THE TRAGEDY</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER IV.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000716\">POIROT INVESTIGATES</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER V.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001313\">“IT ISN’T STRYCHNINE, IS IT?”</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER VI.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002138\">THE INQUEST</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER VII.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002537\">POIROT PAYS HIS DEBTS</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER VIII.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002826\">FRESH SUSPICIONS</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER IX.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003269\">DR. BAUERSTEIN</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER X.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003718\">THE ARREST</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER XI.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004199\">THE CASE FOR THE PROSECUTION</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER XII.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004714\">THE LAST LINK</$link></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CHAPTER XIII.  </td>\n<td><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004865\">POIROT EXPLAINS</$link></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER I.<br>\nI GO TO STYLES</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The intense interest aroused in the public by what was known at the time as “The Styles Case” has now somewhat subsided. Nevertheless, in view of the world-wide notoriety which attended it, I have been asked, both by my friend Poirot and the family themselves, to write an account of the whole story. This, we trust, will effectually silence the sensational rumours which still persist.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I will therefore briefly set down the circumstances which led to my being connected with the affair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had been invalided home from the Front; and, after spending some months in a rather depressing Convalescent Home, was given a month’s sick leave. Having no near relations or friends, I was trying to make up my mind what to do, when I ran across John Cavendish. I had seen very little of him for some years. Indeed, I had never known him particularly well. He was a good fifteen years my senior, for one thing, though he hardly looked his forty-five years. As a boy, though, I had often stayed at Styles, his mother’s place in Essex.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had a good yarn about old times, and it ended in his inviting me down to Styles to spend my leave there.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The mater will be delighted to see you again—after all those years,” he added.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your mother keeps well?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes. I suppose you know that she has married again?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I am afraid I showed my surprise rather plainly. Mrs. Cavendish, who had married John’s father when he was a widower with two sons, had been a handsome woman of middle-age as I remembered her. She certainly could not be a day less than seventy now. I recalled her as an energetic, autocratic personality, somewhat inclined to charitable and social notoriety, with a fondness for opening bazaars and playing the Lady Bountiful. She was a most generous woman, and possessed a considerable fortune of her own.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Their country-place, Styles Court, had been purchased by Mr. Cavendish early in their married life. He had been completely under his wife’s ascendancy, so much so that, on dying, he left the place to her for her lifetime, as well as the larger part of his income; an arrangement that was distinctly unfair to his two sons. Their step-mother, however, had always been most generous to them; indeed, they were so young at the time of their father’s remarriage that they always thought of her as their own mother.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence, the younger, had been a delicate youth. He had qualified as a doctor but early relinquished the profession of medicine, and lived at home while pursuing literary ambitions; though his verses never had any marked success.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John practised for some time as a barrister, but had finally settled down to the more congenial life of a country squire. He had married two years ago, and had taken his wife to live at Styles, though I entertained a shrewd suspicion that he would have preferred his mother to increase his allowance, which would have enabled him to have a home of his own. Mrs. Cavendish, however, was a lady who liked to make her own plans, and expected other people to fall in with them, and in this case she certainly had the whip hand, namely: the purse strings.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John noticed my surprise at the news of his mother’s remarriage and smiled rather ruefully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Rotten little bounder too!” he said savagely. “I can tell you, Hastings, it’s making life jolly difficult for us. As for Evie—you remember Evie?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, I suppose she was after your time. She’s the mater’s factotum, companion, Jack of all trades! A great sport—old Evie! Not precisely young and beautiful, but as game as they make them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You were going to say——?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, this fellow! He turned up from nowhere, on the pretext of being a second cousin or something of Evie’s, though she didn’t seem particularly keen to acknowledge the relationship. The fellow is an absolute outsider, anyone can see that. He’s got a great black beard, and wears patent leather boots in all weathers! But the mater cottoned to him at once, took him on as secretary—you know how she’s always running a hundred societies?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, of course the war has turned the hundreds into thousands. No doubt the fellow was very useful to her. But you could have knocked us all down with a feather when, three months ago, she suddenly announced that she and Alfred were engaged! The fellow must be at least twenty years younger than she is! It’s simply bare-faced fortune hunting; but there you are—she is her own mistress, and she’s married him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It must be a difficult situation for you all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Difficult! It’s damnable!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Thus it came about that, three days later, I descended from the train at Styles St. Mary, an absurd little station, with no apparent reason for existence, perched up in the midst of green fields and country lanes. John Cavendish was waiting on the platform, and piloted me out to the car.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Got a drop or two of petrol still, you see,” he remarked. “Mainly owing to the mater’s activities.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The village of Styles St. Mary was situated about two miles from the little station, and Styles Court lay a mile the other side of it. It was a still, warm day in early July. As one looked out over the flat Essex country, lying so green and peaceful under the afternoon sun, it seemed almost impossible to believe that, not so very far away, a great war was running its appointed course. I felt I had suddenly strayed into another world. As we turned in at the lodge gates, John said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m afraid you’ll find it very quiet down here, Hastings.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow, that’s just what I want.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, it’s pleasant enough if you want to lead the idle life. I drill with the volunteers twice a week, and lend a hand at the farms. My wife works regularly ‘on the land’. She is up at five every morning to milk, and keeps at it steadily until lunchtime. It’s a jolly good life taking it all round—if it weren’t for that fellow Alfred Inglethorp!” He checked the car suddenly, and glanced at his watch. “I wonder if we’ve time to pick up Cynthia. No, she’ll have started from the hospital by now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Cynthia! That’s not your wife?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, Cynthia is a protégée of my mother’s, the daughter of an old schoolfellow of hers, who married a rascally solicitor. He came a cropper, and the girl was left an orphan and penniless. My mother came to the rescue, and Cynthia has been with us nearly two years now. She works in the Red Cross Hospital at Tadminster, seven miles away.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As he spoke the last words, we drew up in front of the fine old house. A lady in a stout tweed skirt, who was bending over a flower bed, straightened herself at our approach.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hullo, Evie, here’s our wounded hero! Mr. Hastings—Miss Howard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard shook hands with a hearty, almost painful, grip. I had an impression of very blue eyes in a sunburnt face. She was a pleasant-looking woman of about forty, with a deep voice, almost manly in its stentorian tones, and had a large sensible square body, with feet to match—these last encased in good thick boots. Her conversation, I soon found, was couched in the telegraphic style.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Weeds grow like house afire. Can’t keep even with ’em. Shall press you in. Better be careful.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m sure I shall be only too delighted to make myself useful,” I responded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t say it. Never does. Wish you hadn’t later.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’re a cynic, Evie,” said John, laughing. “Where’s tea to-day—inside or out?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Out. Too fine a day to be cooped up in the house.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come on then, you’ve done enough gardening for to-day. ‘The labourer is worthy of his hire’, you know. Come and be refreshed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” said Miss Howard, drawing off her gardening gloves, “I’m inclined to agree with you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She led the way round the house to where tea was spread under the shade of a large sycamore.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A figure rose from one of the basket chairs, and came a few steps to meet us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My wife, Hastings,” said John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shall never forget my first sight of Mary Cavendish. Her tall, slender form, outlined against the bright light; the vivid sense of slumbering fire that seemed to find expression only in those wonderful tawny eyes of hers, remarkable eyes, different from any other woman’s that I have ever known; the intense power of stillness she possessed, which nevertheless conveyed the impression of a wild untamed spirit in an exquisitely civilised body—all these things are burnt into my memory. I shall never forget them.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She greeted me with a few words of pleasant welcome in a low clear voice, and I sank into a basket chair feeling distinctly glad that I had accepted John’s invitation. Mrs. Cavendish gave me some tea, and her few quiet remarks heightened my first impression of her as a thoroughly fascinating woman. An appreciative listener is always stimulating, and I described, in a humorous manner, certain incidents of my Convalescent Home, in a way which, I flatter myself, greatly amused my hostess. John, of course, good fellow though he is, could hardly be called a brilliant conversationalist.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At that moment a well remembered voice floated through the open French window near at hand:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you’ll write to the Princess after tea, Alfred? I’ll write to Lady Tadminster for the second day, myself. Or shall we wait until we hear from the Princess? In case of a refusal, Lady Tadminster might open it the first day, and Mrs. Crosbie the second. Then there’s the Duchess—about the school fête.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was the murmur of a man’s voice, and then Mrs. Inglethorp’s rose in reply:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, certainly. After tea will do quite well. You are so thoughtful, Alfred dear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The French window swung open a little wider, and a handsome white-haired old lady, with a somewhat masterful cast of features, stepped out of it on to the lawn. A man followed her, a suggestion of deference in his manner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mrs. Inglethorp greeted me with effusion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, if it isn’t too delightful to see you again, Mr. Hastings, after all these years. Alfred, darling, Mr. Hastings—my husband.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked with some curiosity at “Alfred darling”. He certainly struck a rather alien note. I did not wonder at John objecting to his beard. It was one of the longest and blackest I have ever seen. He wore gold-rimmed pince-nez, and had a curious impassivity of feature. It struck me that he might look natural on a stage, but was strangely out of place in real life. His voice was rather deep and unctuous. He placed a wooden hand in mine and said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is a pleasure, Mr. Hastings.” Then, turning to his wife: “Emily dearest, I think that cushion is a little damp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She beamed fondly on him, as he substituted another with every demonstration of the tenderest care. Strange infatuation of an otherwise sensible woman!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With the presence of Mr. Inglethorp, a sense of constraint and veiled hostility seemed to settle down upon the company. Miss Howard, in particular, took no pains to conceal her feelings. Mrs. Inglethorp, however, seemed to notice nothing unusual. Her volubility, which I remembered of old, had lost nothing in the intervening years, and she poured out a steady flood of conversation, mainly on the subject of the forthcoming bazaar which she was organizing and which was to take place shortly. Occasionally she referred to her husband over a question of days or dates. His watchful and attentive manner never varied. From the very first I took a firm and rooted dislike to him, and I flatter myself that my first judgments are usually fairly shrewd.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Presently Mrs. Inglethorp turned to give some instructions about letters to Evelyn Howard, and her husband addressed me in his painstaking voice:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is soldiering your regular profession, Mr. Hastings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, before the war I was in Lloyd’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you will return there after it is over?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps. Either that or a fresh start altogether.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary Cavendish leant forward.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What would you really choose as a profession, if you could just consult your inclination?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, that depends.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No secret hobby?” she asked. “Tell me—you’re drawn to something? Everyone is—usually something absurd.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ll laugh at me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I’ve always had a secret hankering to be a detective!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The real thing—Scotland Yard? Or Sherlock Holmes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, Sherlock Holmes by all means. But really, seriously, I am awfully drawn to it. I came across a man in Belgium once, a very famous detective, and he quite inflamed me. He was a marvellous little fellow. He used to say that all good detective work was a mere matter of method. My system is based on his—though of course I have progressed rather further. He was a funny little man, a great dandy, but wonderfully clever.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Like a good detective story myself,” remarked Miss Howard. “Lots of nonsense written, though. Criminal discovered in last chapter. Everyone dumbfounded. Real crime—you’d know at once.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There have been a great number of undiscovered crimes,” I argued.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t mean the police, but the people that are right in it. The family. You couldn’t really hoodwink them. They’d know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then,” I said, much amused, “you think that if you were mixed up in a crime, say a murder, you’d be able to spot the murderer right off?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course I should. Mightn’t be able to prove it to a pack of lawyers. But I’m certain I’d know. I’d feel it in my fingertips if he came near me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It might be a ‘she’,” I suggested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Might. But murder’s a violent crime. Associate it more with a man.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in a case of poisoning.” Mrs. Cavendish’s clear voice startled me. “Dr. Bauerstein was saying yesterday that, owing to the general ignorance of the more uncommon poisons among the medical profession, there were probably countless cases of poisoning quite unsuspected.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, Mary, what a gruesome conversation!” cried Mrs. Inglethorp. “It makes me feel as if a goose were walking over my grave. Oh, there’s Cynthia!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A young girl in V.A.D. uniform ran lightly across the lawn.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, Cynthia, you are late to-day. This is Mr. Hastings—Miss Murdoch.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia Murdoch was a fresh-looking young creature, full of life and vigour. She tossed off her little V.A.D. cap, and I admired the great loose waves of her auburn hair, and the smallness and whiteness of the hand she held out to claim her tea. With dark eyes and eyelashes she would have been a beauty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She flung herself down on the ground beside John, and as I handed her a plate of sandwiches she smiled up at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sit down here on the grass, do. It’s ever so much nicer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I dropped down obediently.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You work at Tadminster, don’t you, Miss Murdoch?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“For my sins.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do they bully you, then?” I asked, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should like to see them!” cried Cynthia with dignity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have got a cousin who is nursing,” I remarked. “And she is terrified of ‘Sisters’.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t wonder. Sisters <i>are</i>, you know, Mr. Hastings. They simp-ly <i>are</i>! You’ve no idea! But I’m not a nurse, thank heaven, I work in the dispensary.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How many people do you poison?” I asked, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia smiled too.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, hundreds!” she said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Cynthia,” called Mrs. Inglethorp, “do you think you could write a few notes for me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, Aunt Emily.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She jumped up promptly, and something in her manner reminded me that her position was a dependent one, and that Mrs. Inglethorp, kind as she might be in the main, did not allow her to forget it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My hostess turned to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John will show you your room. Supper is at half-past seven. We have given up late dinner for some time now. Lady Tadminster, our Member’s wife—she was the late Lord Abbotsbury’s daughter—does the same. She agrees with me that one must set an example of economy. We are quite a war household; nothing is wasted here—every scrap of waste paper, even, is saved and sent away in sacks.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I expressed my appreciation, and John took me into the house and up the broad staircase, which forked right and left half-way to different wings of the building. My room was in the left wing, and looked out over the park.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John left me, and a few minutes later I saw him from my window walking slowly across the grass arm in arm with Cynthia Murdoch. I heard Mrs. Inglethorp call “Cynthia” impatiently, and the girl started and ran back to the house. At the same moment, a man stepped out from the shadow of a tree and walked slowly in the same direction. He looked about forty, very dark with a melancholy clean-shaven face. Some violent emotion seemed to be mastering him. He looked up at my window as he passed, and I recognized him, though he had changed much in the fifteen years that had elapsed since we last met. It was John’s younger brother, Lawrence Cavendish. I wondered what it was that had brought that singular expression to his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then I dismissed him from my mind, and returned to the contemplation of my own affairs.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The evening passed pleasantly enough; and I dreamed that night of that enigmatical woman, Mary Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The next morning dawned bright and sunny, and I was full of the anticipation of a delightful visit.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not see Mrs. Cavendish until lunch-time, when she volunteered to take me for a walk, and we spent a charming afternoon roaming in the woods, returning to the house about five.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we entered the large hall, John beckoned us both into the smoking-room. I saw at once by his face that something disturbing had occurred. We followed him in, and he shut the door after us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look here, Mary, there’s the deuce of a mess. Evie’s had a row with Alfred Inglethorp, and she’s off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Evie? Off?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John nodded gloomily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; you see she went to the mater, and—Oh,—here’s Evie herself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard entered. Her lips were set grimly together, and she carried a small suit-case. She looked excited and determined, and slightly on the defensive.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At any rate,” she burst out, “I’ve spoken my mind!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Evelyn,” cried Mrs. Cavendish, “this can’t be true!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard nodded grimly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“True enough! Afraid I said some things to Emily she won’t forget or forgive in a hurry. Don’t mind if they’ve only sunk in a bit. Probably water off a duck’s back, though. I said right out: ‘You’re an old woman, Emily, and there’s no fool like an old fool. The man’s twenty years younger than you, and don’t you fool yourself as to what he married you for. Money! Well, don’t let him have too much of it. Farmer Raikes has got a very pretty young wife. Just ask your Alfred how much time he spends over there.’ She was very angry. Natural! I went on, ‘I’m going to warn you, whether you like it or not. That man would as soon murder you in your bed as look at you. He’s a bad lot. You can say what you like to me, but remember what I’ve told you. He’s a bad lot!’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What did she say?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard made an extremely expressive grimace.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Darling Alfred’—‘dearest Alfred’—‘wicked calumnies’ —‘wicked lies’—‘wicked woman’—to accuse her ‘dear husband!’ The sooner I left her house the better. So I’m off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But not now?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This minute!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For a moment we sat and stared at her. Finally John Cavendish, finding his persuasions of no avail, went off to look up the trains. His wife followed him, murmuring something about persuading Mrs. Inglethorp to think better of it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As she left the room, Miss Howard’s face changed. She leant towards me eagerly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Hastings, you’re honest. I can trust you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was a little startled. She laid her hand on my arm, and sank her voice to a whisper.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look after her, Mr. Hastings. My poor Emily. They’re a lot of sharks—all of them. Oh, I know what I’m talking about. There isn’t one of them that’s not hard up and trying to get money out of her. I’ve protected her as much as I could. Now I’m out of the way, they’ll impose upon her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course, Miss Howard,” I said, “I’ll do everything I can, but I’m sure you’re excited and overwrought.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She interrupted me by slowly shaking her forefinger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Young man, trust me. I’ve lived in the world rather longer than you have. All I ask you is to keep your eyes open. You’ll see what I mean.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The throb of the motor came through the open window, and Miss Howard rose and moved to the door. John’s voice sounded outside. With her hand on the handle, she turned her head over her shoulder, and beckoned to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Above all, Mr. Hastings, watch that devil—her husband!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was no time for more. Miss Howard was swallowed up in an eager chorus of protests and good-byes. The Inglethorps did not appear.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As the motor drove away, Mrs. Cavendish suddenly detached herself from the group, and moved across the drive to the lawn to meet a tall bearded man who had been evidently making for the house. The colour rose in her cheeks as she held out her hand to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who is that?” I asked sharply, for instinctively I distrusted the man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s Dr. Bauerstein,” said John shortly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And who is Dr. Bauerstein?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s staying in the village doing a rest cure, after a bad nervous breakdown. He’s a London specialist; a very clever man—one of the greatest living experts on poisons, I believe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And he’s a great friend of Mary’s,” put in Cynthia, the irrepressible.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John Cavendish frowned and changed the subject.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come for a stroll, Hastings. This has been a most rotten business. She always had a rough tongue, but there is no stauncher friend in England than Evelyn Howard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He took the path through the plantation, and we walked down to the village through the woods which bordered one side of the estate.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we passed through one of the gates on our way home again, a pretty young woman of gipsy type coming in the opposite direction bowed and smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s a pretty girl,” I remarked appreciatively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John’s face hardened.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is Mrs. Raikes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The one that Miss Howard——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly,” said John, with rather unnecessary abruptness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I thought of the white-haired old lady in the big house, and that vivid wicked little face that had just smiled into ours, and a vague chill of foreboding crept over me. I brushed it aside.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Styles is really a glorious old place,” I said to John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He nodded rather gloomily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it’s a fine property. It’ll be mine some day—should be mine now by rights, if my father had only made a decent will. And then I shouldn’t be so damned hard up as I am now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hard up, are you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Hastings, I don’t mind telling you that I’m at my wits’ end for money.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Couldn’t your brother help you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Lawrence? He’s gone through every penny he ever had, publishing rotten verses in fancy bindings. No, we’re an impecunious lot. My mother’s always been awfully good to us, I must say. That is, up to now. Since her marriage, of course——” he broke off, frowning.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For the first time I felt that, with Evelyn Howard, something indefinable had gone from the atmosphere. Her presence had spelt security. Now that security was removed—and the air seemed rife with suspicion. The sinister face of Dr. Bauerstein recurred to me unpleasantly. A vague suspicion of everyone and everything filled my mind. Just for a moment I had a premonition of approaching evil.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER II.<br>\nTHE 16TH AND 17TH OF JULY</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had arrived at Styles on the 5th of July. I come now to the events of the 16th and 17th of that month. For the convenience of the reader I will recapitulate the incidents of those days in as exact a manner as possible. They were elicited subsequently at the trial by a process of long and tedious cross-examinations.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I received a letter from Evelyn Howard a couple of days after her departure, telling me she was working as a nurse at the big hospital in Middlingham, a manufacturing town some fifteen miles away, and begging me to let her know if Mrs. Inglethorp should show any wish to be reconciled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The only fly in the ointment of my peaceful days was Mrs. Cavendish’s extraordinary, and, for my part, unaccountable preference for the society of Dr. Bauerstein. What she saw in the man I cannot imagine, but she was always asking him up to the house, and often went off for long expeditions with him. I must confess that I was quite unable to see his attraction.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The 16th of July fell on a Monday. It was a day of turmoil. The famous bazaar had taken place on Saturday, and an entertainment, in connection with the same charity, at which Mrs. Inglethorp was to recite a War poem, was to be held that night. We were all busy during the morning arranging and decorating the Hall in the village where it was to take place. We had a late luncheon and spent the afternoon resting in the garden. I noticed that John’s manner was somewhat unusual. He seemed very excited and restless.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After tea, Mrs. Inglethorp went to lie down to rest before her efforts in the evening and I challenged Mary Cavendish to a single at tennis.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>About a quarter to seven, Mrs. Inglethorp called us that we should be late as supper was early that night. We had rather a scramble to get ready in time; and before the meal was over the motor was waiting at the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The entertainment was a great success, Mrs. Inglethorp’s recitation receiving tremendous applause. There were also some tableaux in which Cynthia took part. She did not return with us, having been asked to a supper party, and to remain the night with some friends who had been acting with her in the tableaux.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The following morning, Mrs. Inglethorp stayed in bed to breakfast, as she was rather overtired; but she appeared in her briskest mood about 12.30, and swept Lawrence and myself off to a luncheon party.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Such a charming invitation from Mrs. Rolleston. Lady Tadminster’s sister, you know. The Rollestons came over with the Conqueror—one of our oldest families.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary had excused herself on the plea of an engagement with Dr. Bauerstein.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had a pleasant luncheon, and as we drove away Lawrence suggested that we should return by Tadminster, which was barely a mile out of our way, and pay a visit to Cynthia in her dispensary. Mrs. Inglethorp replied that this was an excellent idea, but as she had several letters to write she would drop us there, and we could come back with Cynthia in the pony-trap.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We were detained under suspicion by the hospital porter, until Cynthia appeared to vouch for us, looking very cool and sweet in her long white overall. She took us up to her sanctum, and introduced us to her fellow dispenser, a rather awe-inspiring individual, whom Cynthia cheerily addressed as “Nibs.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What a lot of bottles!” I exclaimed, as my eye travelled round the small room. “Do you really know what’s in them all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Say something original,” groaned Cynthia. “Every single person who comes up here says that. We are really thinking of bestowing a prize on the first individual who does <i>not</i> say: ‘What a lot of bottles!’ And I know the next thing you’re going to say is: ‘How many people have you poisoned?’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I pleaded guilty with a laugh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you people only knew how fatally easy it is to poison someone by mistake, you wouldn’t joke about it. Come on, let’s have tea. We’ve got all sorts of secret stores in that cupboard. No, Lawrence—that’s the poison cupboard. The big cupboard—that’s right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had a very cheery tea, and assisted Cynthia to wash up afterwards. We had just put away the last tea-spoon when a knock came at the door. The countenances of Cynthia and Nibs were suddenly petrified into a stern and forbidding expression.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come in,” said Cynthia, in a sharp professional tone.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A young and rather scared looking nurse appeared with a bottle which she proffered to Nibs, who waved her towards Cynthia with the somewhat enigmatical remark:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>I</i>’m not really here to-day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia took the bottle and examined it with the severity of a judge.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This should have been sent up this morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sister is very sorry. She forgot.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sister should read the rules outside the door.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I gathered from the little nurse’s expression that there was not the least likelihood of her having the hardihood to retail this message to the dreaded “Sister”.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So now it can’t be done until to-morrow,” finished Cynthia.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t you think you could possibly let us have it to-night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” said Cynthia graciously, “we are very busy, but if we have time it shall be done.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The little nurse withdrew, and Cynthia promptly took a jar from the shelf, refilled the bottle, and placed it on the table outside the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I laughed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Discipline must be maintained?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. Come out on our little balcony. You can see all the outside wards there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I followed Cynthia and her friend and they pointed out the different wards to me. Lawrence remained behind, but after a few moments Cynthia called to him over her shoulder to come and join us. Then she looked at her watch.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing more to do, Nibs?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All right. Then we can lock up and go.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had seen Lawrence in quite a different light that afternoon. Compared to John, he was an astoundingly difficult person to get to know. He was the opposite of his brother in almost every respect, being unusually shy and reserved. Yet he had a certain charm of manner, and I fancied that, if one really knew him well, one could have a deep affection for him. I had always fancied that his manner to Cynthia was rather constrained, and that she on her side was inclined to be shy of him. But they were both gay enough this afternoon, and chatted together like a couple of children.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we drove through the village, I remembered that I wanted some stamps, so accordingly we pulled up at the post office.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As I came out again, I cannoned into a little man who was just entering. I drew aside and apologised, when suddenly, with a loud exclamation, he clasped me in his arms and kissed me warmly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mon ami</i> Hastings!” he cried. “It is indeed <i>mon ami</i> Hastings!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot!” I exclaimed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I turned to the pony-trap.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is a very pleasant meeting for me, Miss Cynthia. This is my old friend, Monsieur Poirot, whom I have not seen for years.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, we know Monsieur Poirot,” said Cynthia gaily. “But I had no idea he was a friend of yours.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, indeed,” said Poirot seriously. “I know Mademoiselle Cynthia. It is by the charity of that good Mrs. Inglethorp that I am here.” Then, as I looked at him inquiringly: “Yes, my friend, she had kindly extended hospitality to seven of my countrypeople who, alas, are refugees from their native land. We Belgians will always remember her with gratitude.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was an extraordinary looking little man. He was hardly more than five feet, four inches, but carried himself with great dignity. His head was exactly the shape of an egg, and he always perched it a little on one side. His moustache was very stiff and military. The neatness of his attire was almost incredible. I believe a speck of dust would have caused him more pain than a bullet wound. Yet this quaint dandified little man who, I was sorry to see, now limped badly, had been in his time one of the most celebrated members of the Belgian police. As a detective, his <i>flair</i> had been extraordinary, and he had achieved triumphs by unravelling some of the most baffling cases of the day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He pointed out to me the little house inhabited by him and his fellow Belgians, and I promised to go and see him at an early date. Then he raised his hat with a flourish to Cynthia, and we drove away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s a dear little man,” said Cynthia. “I’d no idea you knew him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ve been entertaining a celebrity unawares,” I replied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, for the rest of the way home, I recited to them the various exploits and triumphs of Hercule Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We arrived back in a very cheerful mood. As we entered the hall, Mrs. Inglethorp came out of her boudoir. She looked flushed and upset.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, it’s you,” she said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is there anything the matter, Aunt Emily?” asked Cynthia.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly not,” said Mrs. Inglethorp sharply. “What should there be?” Then catching sight of Dorcas, the parlourmaid, going into the dining-room, she called to her to bring some stamps into the boudoir.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, m’m.” The old servant hesitated, then added diffidently: “Don’t you think, m’m, you’d better get to bed? You’re looking very tired.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps you’re right, Dorcas—yes—no—not now. I’ve some letters I must finish by post-time. Have you lighted the fire in my room as I told you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, m’m.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I’ll go to bed directly after supper.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She went into the boudoir again, and Cynthia stared after her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Goodness gracious! I wonder what’s up?” she said to Lawrence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He did not seem to have heard her, for without a word he turned on his heel and went out of the house.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I suggested a quick game of tennis before supper and, Cynthia agreeing, I ran upstairs to fetch my racquet.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mrs. Cavendish was coming down the stairs. It may have been my fancy, but she, too, was looking odd and disturbed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Had a good walk with Dr. Bauerstein?” I asked, trying to appear as indifferent as I could.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I didn’t go,” she replied abruptly. “Where is Mrs. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the boudoir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Her hand clenched itself on the banisters, then she seemed to nerve herself for some encounter, and went rapidly past me down the stairs across the hall to the boudoir, the door of which she shut behind her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As I ran out to the tennis court a few moments later, I had to pass the open boudoir window, and was unable to help overhearing the following scrap of dialogue. Mary Cavendish was saying in the voice of a woman desperately controlling herself:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you won’t show it to me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To which Mrs. Inglethorp replied:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Mary, it has nothing to do with that matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then show it to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I tell you it is not what you imagine. It does not concern you in the least.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To which Mary Cavendish replied, with a rising bitterness:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course, I might have known you would shield him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia was waiting for me, and greeted me eagerly with:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I say! There’s been the most awful row! I’ve got it all out of Dorcas.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What kind of a row?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Between Aunt Emily and <i>him</i>. I do hope she’s found him out at last!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was Dorcas there, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course not. She ‘happened to be near the door’. It was a real old bust-up. I do wish I knew what it was all about.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I thought of Mrs. Raikes’s gipsy face, and Evelyn Howard’s warnings, but wisely decided to hold my peace, whilst Cynthia exhausted every possible hypothesis, and cheerfully hoped, “Aunt Emily will send him away, and will never speak to him again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was anxious to get hold of John, but he was nowhere to be seen. Evidently something very momentous had occurred that afternoon. I tried to forget the few words I had overheard; but, do what I would, I could not dismiss them altogether from my mind. What was Mary Cavendish’s concern in the matter?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Inglethorp was in the drawing-room when I came down to supper. His face was impassive as ever, and the strange unreality of the man struck me afresh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mrs. Inglethorp came down last. She still looked agitated, and during the meal there was a somewhat constrained silence. Inglethorp was unusually quiet. As a rule, he surrounded his wife with little attentions, placing a cushion at her back, and altogether playing the part of the devoted husband. Immediately after supper, Mrs. Inglethorp retired to her boudoir again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Send my coffee in here, Mary,” she called. “I’ve just five minutes to catch the post.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia and I went and sat by the open window in the drawing-room. Mary Cavendish brought our coffee to us. She seemed excited.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you young people want lights, or do you enjoy the twilight?” she asked. “Will you take Mrs. Inglethorp her coffee, Cynthia? I will pour it out.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not trouble, Mary,” said Inglethorp. “I will take it to Emily.” He poured it out, and went out of the room carrying it carefully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence followed him, and Mrs. Cavendish sat down by us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We three sat for some time in silence. It was a glorious night, hot and still. Mrs. Cavendish fanned herself gently with a palm leaf.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s almost too hot,” she murmured. “We shall have a thunderstorm.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Alas, that these harmonious moments can never endure! My paradise was rudely shattered by the sound of a well known, and heartily disliked, voice in the hall.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dr. Bauerstein!” exclaimed Cynthia. “What a funny time to come.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I glanced jealously at Mary Cavendish, but she seemed quite undisturbed, the delicate pallor of her cheeks did not vary.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few moments, Alfred Inglethorp had ushered the doctor in, the latter laughing, and protesting that he was in no fit state for a drawing-room. In truth, he presented a sorry spectacle, being literally plastered with mud.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What have you been doing, doctor?” cried Mrs. Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must make my apologies,” said the doctor. “I did not really mean to come in, but Mr. Inglethorp insisted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Bauerstein, you are in a plight,” said John, strolling in from the hall. “Have some coffee, and tell us what you have been up to.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, I will.” He laughed rather ruefully, as he described how he had discovered a very rare species of fern in an inaccessible place, and in his efforts to obtain it had lost his footing, and slipped ignominiously into a neighbouring pond.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The sun soon dried me off,” he added, “but I’m afraid my appearance is very disreputable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At this juncture, Mrs. Inglethorp called to Cynthia from the hall, and the girl ran out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Just carry up my despatch-case, will you, dear? I’m going to bed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The door into the hall was a wide one. I had risen when Cynthia did, John was close by me. There were therefore three witnesses who could swear that Mrs. Inglethorp was carrying her coffee, as yet untasted, in her hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My evening was utterly and entirely spoilt by the presence of Dr. Bauerstein. It seemed to me the man would never go. He rose at last, however, and I breathed a sigh of relief.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ll walk down to the village with you,” said Mr. Inglethorp. “I must see our agent over those estate accounts.” He turned to John. “No one need sit up. I will take the latch-key.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER III.<br>\nTHE NIGHT OF THE TRAGEDY</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To make this part of my story clear, I append the following plan of the first floor of Styles. The servants’ rooms are reached through the door B. They have no communication with the right wing, where the Inglethorps’ rooms were situated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><div class=\"fig c9\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005247\"><img src=\"OEBPS/4521246603420151278_ill_001.png\" alt=\"Illustration:\"></$link></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It seemed to be the middle of the night when I was awakened by Lawrence Cavendish. He had a candle in his hand, and the agitation of his face told me at once that something was seriously wrong.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What’s the matter?” I asked, sitting up in bed, and trying to collect my scattered thoughts.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We are afraid my mother is very ill. She seems to be having some kind of fit. Unfortunately she has locked herself in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ll come at once.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I sprang out of bed; and, pulling on a dressing-gown, followed Lawrence along the passage and the gallery to the right wing of the house.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John Cavendish joined us, and one or two of the servants were standing round in a state of awe-stricken excitement. Lawrence turned to his brother.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you think we had better do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Never, I thought, had his indecision of character been more apparent.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John rattled the handle of Mrs. Inglethorp’s door violently, but with no effect. It was obviously locked or bolted on the inside. The whole household was aroused by now. The most alarming sounds were audible from the interior of the room. Clearly something must be done.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Try going through Mr. Inglethorp’s room, sir,” cried Dorcas. “Oh, the poor mistress!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly I realized that Alfred Inglethorp was not with us—that he alone had given no sign of his presence. John opened the door of his room. It was pitch dark, but Lawrence was following with the candle, and by its feeble light we saw that the bed had not been slept in, and that there was no sign of the room having been occupied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We went straight to the connecting door. That, too, was locked or bolted on the inside. What was to be done?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, dear, sir,” cried Dorcas, wringing her hands, “what ever shall we do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We must try and break the door in, I suppose. It’ll be a tough job, though. Here, let one of the maids go down and wake Baily and tell him to go for Dr. Wilkins at once. Now then, we’ll have a try at the door. Half a moment, though, isn’t there a door into Miss Cynthia’s rooms?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, but that’s always bolted. It’s never been undone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, we might just see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He ran rapidly down the corridor to Cynthia’s room. Mary Cavendish was there, shaking the girl—who must have been an unusually sound sleeper—and trying to wake her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a moment or two he was back.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No good. That’s bolted too. We must break in the door. I think this one is a shade less solid than the one in the passage.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We strained and heaved together. The framework of the door was solid, and for a long time it resisted our efforts, but at last we felt it give beneath our weight, and finally, with a resounding crash, it was burst open.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We stumbled in together, Lawrence still holding his candle. Mrs. Inglethorp was lying on the bed, her whole form agitated by violent convulsions, in one of which she must have overturned the table beside her. As we entered, however, her limbs relaxed, and she fell back upon the pillows.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John strode across the room, and lit the gas. Turning to Annie, one of the housemaids, he sent her downstairs to the dining-room for brandy. Then he went across to his mother whilst I unbolted the door that gave on the corridor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I turned to Lawrence, to suggest that I had better leave them now that there was no further need of my services, but the words were frozen on my lips. Never have I seen such a ghastly look on any man’s face. He was white as chalk, the candle he held in his shaking hand was sputtering onto the carpet, and his eyes, petrified with terror, or some such kindred emotion, stared fixedly over my head at a point on the further wall. It was as though he had seen something that turned him to stone. I instinctively followed the direction of his eyes, but I could see nothing unusual. The still feebly flickering ashes in the grate, and the row of prim ornaments on the mantelpiece, were surely harmless enough.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The violence of Mrs. Inglethorp’s attack seemed to be passing. She was able to speak in short gasps.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Better now—very sudden—stupid of me—to lock myself in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A shadow fell on the bed and, looking up, I saw Mary Cavendish standing near the door with her arm around Cynthia. She seemed to be supporting the girl, who looked utterly dazed and unlike herself. Her face was heavily flushed, and she yawned repeatedly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poor Cynthia is quite frightened,” said Mrs. Cavendish in a low clear voice. She herself, I noticed, was dressed in her white land smock. Then it must be later than I thought. I saw that a faint streak of daylight was showing through the curtains of the windows, and that the clock on the mantelpiece pointed to close upon five o’clock.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A strangled cry from the bed startled me. A fresh access of pain seized the unfortunate old lady. The convulsions were of a violence terrible to behold. Everything was confusion. We thronged round her, powerless to help or alleviate. A final convulsion lifted her from the bed, until she appeared to rest upon her head and her heels, with her body arched in an extraordinary manner. In vain Mary and John tried to administer more brandy. The moments flew. Again the body arched itself in that peculiar fashion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At that moment, Dr. Bauerstein pushed his way authoritatively into the room. For one instant he stopped dead, staring at the figure on the bed, and, at the same instant, Mrs. Inglethorp cried out in a strangled voice, her eyes fixed on the doctor:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Alfred—Alfred——” Then she fell back motionless on the pillows.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a stride, the doctor reached the bed, and seizing her arms worked them energetically, applying what I knew to be artificial respiration. He issued a few short sharp orders to the servants. An imperious wave of his hand drove us all to the door. We watched him, fascinated, though I think we all knew in our hearts that it was too late, and that nothing could be done now. I could see by the expression on his face that he himself had little hope.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Finally he abandoned his task, shaking his head gravely. At that moment, we heard footsteps outside, and Dr. Wilkins, Mrs. Inglethorp’s own doctor, a portly, fussy little man, came bustling in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few words Dr. Bauerstein explained how he had happened to be passing the lodge gates as the car came out, and had run up to the house as fast as he could, whilst the car went on to fetch Dr. Wilkins. With a faint gesture of the hand, he indicated the figure on the bed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ve—ry sad. Ve—ry sad,” murmured Dr. Wilkins. “Poor dear lady. Always did far too much—far too much—against my advice. I warned her. Her heart was far from strong. ‘Take it easy,’ I said to her, ‘Take—it—easy’. But no—her zeal for good works was too great. Nature rebelled. Na—ture—re—belled.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dr. Bauerstein, I noticed, was watching the local doctor narrowly. He still kept his eyes fixed on him as he spoke.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The convulsions were of a peculiar violence, Dr. Wilkins. I am sorry you were not here in time to witness them. They were quite—tetanic in character.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” said Dr. Wilkins wisely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should like to speak to you in private,” said Dr. Bauerstein. He turned to John. “You do not object?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We all trooped out into the corridor, leaving the two doctors alone, and I heard the key turned in the lock behind us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We went slowly down the stairs. I was violently excited. I have a certain talent for deduction, and Dr. Bauerstein’s manner had started a flock of wild surmises in my mind. Mary Cavendish laid her hand upon my arm.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it? Why did Dr. Bauerstein seem so—peculiar?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked at her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you know what I think?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Listen!” I looked round, the others were out of earshot. I lowered my voice to a whisper. “I believe she has been poisoned! I’m certain Dr. Bauerstein suspects it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>What?</i>” She shrank against the wall, the pupils of her eyes dilating wildly. Then, with a sudden cry that startled me, she cried out: “No, no—not that—not that!” And breaking from me, fled up the stairs. I followed her, afraid that she was going to faint. I found her leaning against the bannisters, deadly pale. She waved me away impatiently.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no—leave me. I’d rather be alone. Let me just be quiet for a minute or two. Go down to the others.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I obeyed her reluctantly. John and Lawrence were in the dining-room. I joined them. We were all silent, but I suppose I voiced the thoughts of us all when I at last broke it by saying:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where is Mr. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s not in the house.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our eyes met. Where <i>was</i> Alfred Inglethorp? His absence was strange and inexplicable. I remembered Mrs. Inglethorp’s dying words. What lay beneath them? What more could she have told us, if she had had time?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At last we heard the doctors descending the stairs. Dr. Wilkins was looking important and excited, and trying to conceal an inward exultation under a manner of decorous calm. Dr. Bauerstein remained in the background, his grave bearded face unchanged. Dr. Wilkins was the spokesman for the two. He addressed himself to John:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Cavendish, I should like your consent to a post-mortem.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is that necessary?” asked John gravely. A spasm of pain crossed his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Absolutely,” said Dr. Bauerstein.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You mean by that——?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That neither Dr. Wilkins nor myself could give a death certificate under the circumstances.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John bent his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In that case, I have no alternative but to agree.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you,” said Dr. Wilkins briskly. “We propose that it should take place to-morrow night—or rather to-night.” And he glanced at the daylight. “Under the circumstances, I am afraid an inquest can hardly be avoided—these formalities are necessary, but I beg that you won’t distress yourselves.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a pause, and then Dr. Bauerstein drew two keys from his pocket, and handed them to John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“These are the keys of the two rooms. I have locked them and, in my opinion, they would be better kept locked for the present.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The doctors then departed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had been turning over an idea in my head, and I felt that the moment had now come to broach it. Yet I was a little chary of doing so. John, I knew, had a horror of any kind of publicity, and was an easygoing optimist, who preferred never to meet trouble half-way. It might be difficult to convince him of the soundness of my plan. Lawrence, on the other hand, being less conventional, and having more imagination, I felt I might count upon as an ally. There was no doubt that the moment had come for me to take the lead.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John,” I said, “I am going to ask you something.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You remember my speaking of my friend Poirot? The Belgian who is here? He has been a most famous detective.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I want you to let me call him in—to investigate this matter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What—now? Before the post-mortem?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, time is an advantage if—if—there has been foul play.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Rubbish!” cried Lawrence angrily. “In my opinion the whole thing is a mare’s nest of Bauerstein’s! Wilkins hadn’t an idea of such a thing, until Bauerstein put it into his head. But, like all specialists, Bauerstein’s got a bee in his bonnet. Poisons are his hobby, so of course he sees them everywhere.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I confess that I was surprised by Lawrence’s attitude. He was so seldom vehement about anything.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John hesitated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I can’t feel as you do, Lawrence,” he said at last. “I’m inclined to give Hastings a free hand, though I should prefer to wait a bit. We don’t want any unnecessary scandal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no,” I cried eagerly, “you need have no fear of that. Poirot is discretion itself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well, then, have it your own way. I leave it in your hands. Though, if it is as we suspect, it seems a clear enough case. God forgive me if I am wronging him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked at my watch. It was six o’clock. I determined to lose no time.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Five minutes’ delay, however, I allowed myself. I spent it in ransacking the library until I discovered a medical book which gave a description of strychnine poisoning.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER IV.<br>\nPOIROT INVESTIGATES</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The house which the Belgians occupied in the village was quite close to the park gates. One could save time by taking a narrow path through the long grass, which cut off the detours of the winding drive. So I, accordingly, went that way. I had nearly reached the lodge, when my attention was arrested by the running figure of a man approaching me. It was Mr. Inglethorp. Where had he been? How did he intend to explain his absence?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He accosted me eagerly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My God! This is terrible! My poor wife! I have only just heard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where have you been?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Denby kept me late last night. It was one o’clock before we’d finished. Then I found that I’d forgotten the latch-key after all. I didn’t want to arouse the household, so Denby gave me a bed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you hear the news?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wilkins knocked Denby up to tell him. My poor Emily! She was so self-sacrificing—such a noble character. She over-taxed her strength.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A wave of revulsion swept over me. What a consummate hypocrite the man was!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must hurry on,” I said, thankful that he did not ask me whither I was bound.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few minutes I was knocking at the door of Leastways Cottage.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Getting no answer, I repeated my summons impatiently. A window above me was cautiously opened, and Poirot himself looked out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He gave an exclamation of surprise at seeing me. In a few brief words, I explained the tragedy that had occurred, and that I wanted his help.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wait, my friend, I will let you in, and you shall recount to me the affair whilst I dress.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few moments he had unbarred the door, and I followed him up to his room. There he installed me in a chair, and I related the whole story, keeping back nothing, and omitting no circumstance, however insignificant, whilst he himself made a careful and deliberate toilet.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I told him of my awakening, of Mrs. Inglethorp’s dying words, of her husband’s absence, of the quarrel the day before, of the scrap of conversation between Mary and her mother-in-law that I had overheard, of the former quarrel between Mrs. Inglethorp and Evelyn Howard, and of the latter’s innuendoes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was hardly as clear as I could wish. I repeated myself several times, and occasionally had to go back to some detail that I had forgotten. Poirot smiled kindly on me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The mind is confused? Is it not so? Take time, <i>mon ami</i>. You are agitated; you are excited—it is but natural. Presently, when we are calmer, we will arrange the facts, neatly, each in his proper place. We will examine—and reject. Those of importance we will put on one side; those of no importance, pouf!”—he screwed up his cherub-like face, and puffed comically enough—“blow them away!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s all very well,” I objected, “but how are you going to decide what is important, and what isn’t? That always seems the difficulty to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head energetically. He was now arranging his moustache with exquisite care.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not so. <i>Voyons!</i> One fact leads to another—so we continue. Does the next fit in with that? <i>A merveille!</i> Good! We can proceed. This next little fact—no! Ah, that is curious! There is something missing—a link in the chain that is not there. We examine. We search. And that little curious fact, that possibly paltry little detail that will not tally, we put it here!” He made an extravagant gesture with his hand. “It is significant! It is tremendous!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Y—es——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” Poirot shook his forefinger so fiercely at me that I quailed before it. “Beware! Peril to the detective who says: ‘It is so small—it does not matter. It will not agree. I will forget it.’ That way lies confusion! Everything matters.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know. You always told me that. That’s why I have gone into all the details of this thing whether they seemed to me relevant or not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And I am pleased with you. You have a good memory, and you have given me the facts faithfully. Of the order in which you present them, I say nothing—truly, it is deplorable! But I make allowances—you are upset. To that I attribute the circumstance that you have omitted one fact of paramount importance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is that?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have not told me if Mrs. Inglethorp ate well last night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I stared at him. Surely the war had affected the little man’s brain. He was carefully engaged in brushing his coat before putting it on, and seemed wholly engrossed in the task.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t remember,” I said. “And, anyway, I don’t see——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not see? But it is of the first importance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I can’t see why,” I said, rather nettled. “As far as I can remember, she didn’t eat much. She was obviously upset, and it had taken her appetite away. That was only natural.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” said Poirot thoughtfully, “it was only natural.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He opened a drawer, and took out a small despatch-case, then turned to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now I am ready. We will proceed to the château, and study matters on the spot. Excuse me, <i>mon ami</i>, you dressed in haste, and your tie is on one side. Permit me.” With a deft gesture, he rearranged it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Ça y est!</i> Now, shall we start?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We hurried up the village, and turned in at the lodge gates. Poirot stopped for a moment, and gazed sorrowfully over the beautiful expanse of park, still glittering with morning dew.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So beautiful, so beautiful, and yet, the poor family, plunged in sorrow, prostrated with grief.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He looked at me keenly as he spoke, and I was aware that I reddened under his prolonged gaze.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Was the family prostrated by grief? Was the sorrow at Mrs. Inglethorp’s death so great? I realized that there was an emotional lack in the atmosphere. The dead woman had not the gift of commanding love. Her death was a shock and a distress, but she would not be passionately regretted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot seemed to follow my thoughts. He nodded his head gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, you are right,” he said, “it is not as though there was a blood tie. She has been kind and generous to these Cavendishes, but she was not their own mother. Blood tells—always remember that—blood tells.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I said, “I wish you would tell me why you wanted to know if Mrs. Inglethorp ate well last night? I have been turning it over in my mind, but I can’t see how it has anything to do with the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He was silent for a minute or two as we walked along, but finally he said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not mind telling you—though, as you know, it is not my habit to explain until the end is reached. The present contention is that Mrs. Inglethorp died of strychnine poisoning, presumably administered in her coffee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, what time was the coffee served?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About eight o’clock.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Therefore she drank it between then and half-past eight—certainly not much later. Well, strychnine is a fairly rapid poison. Its effects would be felt very soon, probably in about an hour. Yet, in Mrs. Inglethorp’s case, the symptoms do not manifest themselves until five o’clock the next morning: nine hours! But a heavy meal, taken at about the same time as the poison, might retard its effects, though hardly to that extent. Still, it is a possibility to be taken into account. But, according to you, she ate very little for supper, and yet the symptoms do not develop until early the next morning! Now that is a curious circumstance, my friend. Something may arise at the autopsy to explain it. In the meantime, remember it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we neared the house, John came out and met us. His face looked weary and haggard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is a very dreadful business, Monsieur Poirot,” he said. “Hastings has explained to you that we are anxious for no publicity?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I comprehend perfectly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You see, it is only suspicion so far. We have nothing to go upon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. It is a matter of precaution only.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John turned to me, taking out his cigarette-case, and lighting a cigarette as he did so.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You know that fellow Inglethorp is back?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I met him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John flung the match into an adjacent flower bed, a proceeding which was too much for Poirot’s feelings. He retrieved it, and buried it neatly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s jolly difficult to know how to treat him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That difficulty will not exist long,” pronounced Poirot quietly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John looked puzzled, not quite understanding the portent of this cryptic saying. He handed the two keys which Dr. Bauerstein had given him to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Show Monsieur Poirot everything he wants to see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The rooms are locked?” asked Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dr. Bauerstein considered it advisable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then he is very sure. Well, that simplifies matters for us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We went up together to the room of the tragedy. For convenience I append a plan of the room and the principal articles of furniture in it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><div class=\"fig c9\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005248\"><img src=\"OEBPS/4521246603420151278_ill_002.png\" alt=\"Illustration:\"></$link></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot locked the door on the inside, and proceeded to a minute inspection of the room. He darted from one object to the other with the agility of a grasshopper. I remained by the door, fearing to obliterate any clues. Poirot, however, did not seem grateful to me for my forbearance.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What have you, my friend,” he cried, “that you remain there like—how do you say it?—ah, yes, the stuck pig?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I explained that I was afraid of obliterating any foot-marks.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Foot-marks? But what an idea! There has already been practically an army in the room! What foot-marks are we likely to find? No, come here and aid me in my search. I will put down my little case until I need it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He did so, on the round table by the window, but it was an ill-advised proceeding; for, the top of it being loose, it tilted up, and precipitated the despatch-case on the floor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Eh voilà une table!</i>” cried Poirot. “Ah, my friend, one may live in a big house and yet have no comfort.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After which piece of moralizing, he resumed his search.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A small purple despatch-case, with a key in the lock, on the writing-table, engaged his attention for some time. He took out the key from the lock, and passed it to me to inspect. I saw nothing peculiar, however. It was an ordinary key of the Yale type, with a bit of twisted wire through the handle.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Next, he examined the framework of the door we had broken in, assuring himself that the bolt had really been shot. Then he went to the door opposite leading into Cynthia’s room. That door was also bolted, as I had stated. However, he went to the length of unbolting it, and opening and shutting it several times; this he did with the utmost precaution against making any noise. Suddenly something in the bolt itself seemed to rivet his attention. He examined it carefully, and then, nimbly whipping out a pair of small forceps from his case, he drew out some minute particle which he carefully sealed up in a tiny envelope.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>On the chest of drawers there was a tray with a spirit lamp and a small saucepan on it. A small quantity of a dark fluid remained in the saucepan, and an empty cup and saucer that had been drunk out of stood near it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I wondered how I could have been so unobservant as to overlook this. Here was a clue worth having. Poirot delicately dipped his finger into liquid, and tasted it gingerly. He made a grimace.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Cocoa—with—I think—rum in it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He passed on to the debris on the floor, where the table by the bed had been overturned. A reading-lamp, some books, matches, a bunch of keys, and the crushed fragments of a coffee-cup lay scattered about.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, this is curious,” said Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must confess that I see nothing particularly curious about it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not? Observe the lamp—the chimney is broken in two places; they lie there as they fell. But see, the coffee-cup is absolutely smashed to powder.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” I said wearily, “I suppose someone must have stepped on it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly,” said Poirot, in an odd voice. “Someone stepped on it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He rose from his knees, and walked slowly across to the mantelpiece, where he stood abstractedly fingering the ornaments, and straightening them—a trick of his when he was agitated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mon ami</i>,” he said, turning to me, “somebody stepped on that cup, grinding it to powder, and the reason they did so was either because it contained strychnine or—which is far more serious—because it did not contain strychnine!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I made no reply. I was bewildered, but I knew that it was no good asking him to explain. In a moment or two he roused himself, and went on with his investigations. He picked up the bunch of keys from the floor, and twirling them round in his fingers finally selected one, very bright and shining, which he tried in the lock of the purple despatch-case. It fitted, and he opened the box, but after a moment’s hesitation, closed and relocked it, and slipped the bunch of keys, as well as the key that had originally stood in the lock, into his own pocket.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have no authority to go through these papers. But it should be done—at once!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He then made a very careful examination of the drawers of the wash-stand. Crossing the room to the left-hand window, a round stain, hardly visible on the dark brown carpet, seemed to interest him particularly. He went down on his knees, examining it minutely—even going so far as to smell it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Finally, he poured a few drops of the cocoa into a test tube, sealing it up carefully. His next proceeding was to take out a little notebook.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have found in this room,” he said, writing busily, “six points of interest. Shall I enumerate them, or will you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, you,” I replied hastily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well, then. One, a coffee-cup that has been ground into powder; two, a despatch-case with a key in the lock; three, a stain on the floor.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That may have been done some time ago,” I interrupted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, for it is still perceptibly damp and smells of coffee. Four, a fragment of some dark green fabric—only a thread or two, but recognizable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” I cried. “That was what you sealed up in the envelope.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. It may turn out to be a piece of one of Mrs. Inglethorp’s own dresses, and quite unimportant. We shall see. Five, <i>this</i>!” With a dramatic gesture, he pointed to a large splash of candle grease on the floor by the writing-table. “It must have been done since yesterday, otherwise a good housemaid would have at once removed it with blotting-paper and a hot iron. One of my best hats once—but that is not to the point.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was very likely done last night. We were very agitated. Or perhaps Mrs. Inglethorp herself dropped her candle.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You brought only one candle into the room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Lawrence Cavendish was carrying it. But he was very upset. He seemed to see something over here”—I indicated the mantelpiece—“that absolutely paralysed him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is interesting,” said Poirot quickly. “Yes, it is suggestive”—his eye sweeping the whole length of the wall—“but it was not his candle that made this great patch, for you perceive that this is white grease; whereas Monsieur Lawrence’s candle, which is still on the dressing-table, is pink. On the other hand, Mrs. Inglethorp had no candlestick in the room, only a reading-lamp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then,” I said, “what do you deduce?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To which my friend only made a rather irritating reply, urging me to use my own natural faculties.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the sixth point?” I asked. “I suppose it is the sample of cocoa.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” said Poirot thoughtfully. “I might have included that in the six, but I did not. No, the sixth point I will keep to myself for the present.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He looked quickly round the room. “There is nothing more to be done here, I think, unless”—he stared earnestly and long at the dead ashes in the grate. “The fire burns—and it destroys. But by chance—there might be—let us see!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Deftly, on hands and knees, he began to sort the ashes from the grate into the fender, handling them with the greatest caution. Suddenly, he gave a faint exclamation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The forceps, Hastings!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I quickly handed them to him, and with skill he extracted a small piece of half charred paper.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There, <i>mon ami!</i>” he cried. “What do you think of that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I scrutinized the fragment. This is an exact reproduction of it:—</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><div class=\"fig c9\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005249\"><img src=\"OEBPS/4521246603420151278_ill_003.png\" alt=\"Illustration:\"></$link></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was puzzled. It was unusually thick, quite unlike ordinary notepaper. Suddenly an idea struck me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot!” I cried. “This is a fragment of a will!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked up at him sharply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are not surprised?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” he said gravely, “I expected it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I relinquished the piece of paper, and watched him put it away in his case, with the same methodical care that he bestowed on everything. My brain was in a whirl. What was this complication of a will? Who had destroyed it? The person who had left the candle grease on the floor? Obviously. But how had anyone gained admission? All the doors had been bolted on the inside.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, my friend,” said Poirot briskly, “we will go. I should like to ask a few questions of the parlourmaid—Dorcas, her name is, is it not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We passed through Alfred Inglethorp’s room, and Poirot delayed long enough to make a brief but fairly comprehensive examination of it. We went out through that door, locking both it and that of Mrs. Inglethorp’s room as before.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I took him down to the boudoir which he had expressed a wish to see, and went myself in search of Dorcas.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>When I returned with her, however, the boudoir was empty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I cried, “where are you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am here, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He had stepped outside the French window, and was standing, apparently lost in admiration, before the various shaped flower beds.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Admirable!” he murmured. “Admirable! What symmetry! Observe that crescent; and those diamonds—their neatness rejoices the eye. The spacing of the plants, also, is perfect. It has been recently done; is it not so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I believe they were at it yesterday afternoon. But come in—Dorcas is here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Eh bien, eh bien!</i> Do not grudge me a moment’s satisfaction of the eye.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but this affair is more important.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And how do you know that these fine begonias are not of equal importance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shrugged my shoulders. There was really no arguing with him if he chose to take that line.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not agree? But such things have been. Well, we will come in and interview the brave Dorcas.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas was standing in the boudoir, her hands folded in front of her, and her grey hair rose in stiff waves under her white cap. She was the very model and picture of a good old-fashioned servant.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In her attitude towards Poirot, she was inclined to be suspicious, but he soon broke down her defences. He drew forward a chair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pray be seated, mademoiselle.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have been with your mistress many years, is it not so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ten years, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is a long time, and very faithful service. You were much attached to her, were you not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She was a very good mistress to me, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you will not object to answering a few questions. I put them to you with Mr. Cavendish’s full approval.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, certainly, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I will begin by asking you about the events of yesterday afternoon. Your mistress had a quarrel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. But I don’t know that I ought——” Dorcas hesitated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked at her keenly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My good Dorcas, it is necessary that I should know every detail of that quarrel as fully as possible. Do not think that you are betraying your mistress’s secrets. Your mistress lies dead, and it is necessary that we should know all—if we are to avenge her. Nothing can bring her back to life, but we do hope, if there has been foul play, to bring the murderer to justice.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Amen to that,” said Dorcas fiercely. “And, naming no names, there’s <i>one</i> in this house that none of us could ever abide! And an ill day it was when first <i>he</i> darkened the threshold.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot waited for her indignation to subside, and then, resuming his business-like tone, he asked:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, as to this quarrel? What is the first you heard of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, sir, I happened to be going along the hall outside yesterday——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What time was that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I couldn’t say exactly, sir, but it wasn’t tea-time by a long way. Perhaps four o’clock—or it may have been a bit later. Well, sir, as I said, I happened to be passing along, when I heard voices very loud and angry in here. I didn’t exactly mean to listen, but—well, there it is. I stopped. The door was shut, but the mistress was speaking very sharp and clear, and I heard what she said quite plainly. ‘You have lied to me, and deceived me,’ she said. I didn’t hear what Mr. Inglethorp replied. He spoke a good bit lower than she did—but she answered: ‘How dare you? I have kept you and clothed you and fed you! You owe everything to me! And this is how you repay me! By bringing disgrace upon our name!’ Again I didn’t hear what he said, but she went on: ‘Nothing that you can say will make any difference. I see my duty clearly. My mind is made up. You need not think that any fear of publicity, or scandal between husband and wife will deter me.’ Then I thought I heard them coming out, so I went off quickly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are sure it was Mr. Inglethorp’s voice you heard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, sir, whose else’s could it be?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, what happened next?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Later, I came back to the hall; but it was all quiet. At five o’clock, Mrs. Inglethorp rang the bell and told me to bring her a cup of tea—nothing to eat—to the boudoir. She was looking dreadful—so white and upset. ‘Dorcas,’ she says, ‘I’ve had a great shock.’ ‘I’m sorry for that, m’m,’ I says. ‘You’ll feel better after a nice hot cup of tea, m’m.’ She had something in her hand. I don’t know if it was a letter, or just a piece of paper, but it had writing on it, and she kept staring at it, almost as if she couldn’t believe what was written there. She whispered to herself, as though she had forgotten I was there: ‘These few words—and everything’s changed.’ And then she says to me: ‘Never trust a man, Dorcas, they’re not worth it!’ I hurried off, and got her a good strong cup of tea, and she thanked me, and said she’d feel better when she’d drunk it. ‘I don’t know what to do,’ she says. ‘Scandal between husband and wife is a dreadful thing, Dorcas. I’d rather hush it up if I could.’ Mrs. Cavendish came in just then, so she didn’t say any more.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She still had the letter, or whatever it was, in her hand?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What would she be likely to do with it afterwards?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I don’t know, sir, I expect she would lock it up in that purple case of hers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is that where she usually kept important papers?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. She brought it down with her every morning, and took it up every night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did she lose the key of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She missed it yesterday at lunch-time, sir, and told me to look carefully for it. She was very much put out about it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But she had a duplicate key?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas was looking very curiously at him and, to tell the truth, so was I. What was all this about a lost key? Poirot smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind, Dorcas, it is my business to know things. Is this the key that was lost?” He drew from his pocket the key that he had found in the lock of the despatch-case upstairs.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas’s eyes looked as though they would pop out of her head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s it, sir, right enough. But where did you find it? I looked everywhere for it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, but you see it was not in the same place yesterday as it was to-day. Now, to pass to another subject, had your mistress a dark green dress in her wardrobe?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas was rather startled by the unexpected question.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Are you quite sure?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Has anyone else in the house got a green dress?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas reflected.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Cynthia has a green evening dress.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Light or dark green?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A light green, sir; a sort of chiffon, they call it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, that is not what I want. And nobody else has anything green?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir—not that I know of.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot’s face did not betray a trace of whether he was disappointed or otherwise. He merely remarked:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good, we will leave that and pass on. Have you any reason to believe that your mistress was likely to take a sleeping powder last night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not <i>last</i> night, sir, I know she didn’t.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why do you know so positively?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because the box was empty. She took the last one two days ago, and she didn’t have any more made up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are quite sure of that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Positive, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then that is cleared up! By the way, your mistress didn’t ask you to sign any paper yesterday?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To sign a paper? No, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When Mr. Hastings and Mr. Lawrence came in yesterday evening, they found your mistress busy writing letters. I suppose you can give me no idea to whom these letters were addressed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m afraid I couldn’t, sir. I was out in the evening. Perhaps Annie could tell you, though she’s a careless girl. Never cleared the coffee-cups away last night. That’s what happens when I’m not here to look after things.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot lifted his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Since they have been left, Dorcas, leave them a little longer, I pray you. I should like to examine them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What time did you go out last evening?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About six o’clock, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, Dorcas, that is all I have to ask you.” He rose and strolled to the window. “I have been admiring these flower beds. How many gardeners are employed here, by the way?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only three now, sir. Five, we had, before the war, when it was kept as a gentleman’s place should be. I wish you could have seen it then, sir. A fair sight it was. But now there’s only old Manning, and young William, and a new-fashioned woman gardener in breeches and such-like. Ah, these are dreadful times!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The good times will come again, Dorcas. At least, we hope so. Now, will you send Annie to me here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you know that Mrs. Inglethorp took sleeping powders?” I asked, in lively curiosity, as Dorcas left the room. “And about the lost key and the duplicate?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One thing at a time. As to the sleeping powders, I knew by this.” He suddenly produced a small cardboard box, such as chemists use for powders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did you find it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the wash-stand drawer in Mrs. Inglethorp’s bedroom. It was Number Six of my catalogue.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I suppose, as the last powder was taken two days ago, it is not of much importance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Probably not, but do you notice anything that strikes you as peculiar about this box?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I examined it closely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I can’t say that I do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look at the label.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I read the label carefully: “‘One powder to be taken at bedtime, if required. Mrs. Inglethorp.’ No, I see nothing unusual.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not the fact that there is no chemist’s name?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” I exclaimed. “To be sure, that is odd!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you ever known a chemist to send out a box like that, without his printed name?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I can’t say that I have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was becoming quite excited, but Poirot damped my ardour by remarking:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yet the explanation is quite simple. So do not intrigue yourself, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>An audible creaking proclaimed the approach of Annie, so I had no time to reply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Annie was a fine, strapping girl, and was evidently labouring under intense excitement, mingled with a certain ghoulish enjoyment of the tragedy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot came to the point at once, with a business-like briskness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I sent for you, Annie, because I thought you might be able to tell me something about the letters Mrs. Inglethorp wrote last night. How many were there? And can you tell me any of the names and addresses?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Annie considered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There were four letters, sir. One was to Miss Howard, and one was to Mr. Wells, the lawyer, and the other two I don’t think I remember, sir—oh, yes, one was to Ross’s, the caterers in Tadminster. The other one, I don’t remember.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Think,” urged Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Annie racked her brains in vain.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m sorry, sir, but it’s clean gone. I don’t think I can have noticed it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It does not matter,” said Poirot, not betraying any sign of disappointment. “Now I want to ask you about something else. There is a saucepan in Mrs. Inglethorp’s room with some cocoa in it. Did she have that every night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, it was put in her room every evening, and she warmed it up in the night—whenever she fancied it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What was it? Plain cocoa?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, made with milk, with a teaspoonful of sugar, and two teaspoonfuls of rum in it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who took it to her room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Always?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“At what time?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I went to draw the curtains, as a rule, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you bring it straight up from the kitchen then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, you see there’s not much room on the gas stove, so cook used to make it early, before putting the vegetables on for supper. Then I used to bring it up, and put it on the table by the swing door, and take it into her room later.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The swing door is in the left wing, is it not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the table, is it on this side of the door, or on the farther—servants’ side?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s this side, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What time did you bring it up last night?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About quarter-past seven, I should say, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And when did you take it into Mrs. Inglethorp’s room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I went to shut up, sir. About eight o’clock. Mrs. Inglethorp came up to bed before I’d finished.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, between seven-fifteen and eight o’clock, the cocoa was standing on the table in the left wing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.” Annie had been growing redder and redder in the face, and now she blurted out unexpectedly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And if there <i>was</i> salt in it, sir, it wasn’t me. I never took the salt near it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What makes you think there was salt in it?” asked Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Seeing it on the tray, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You saw some salt on the tray?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Coarse kitchen salt, it looked. I never noticed it when I took the tray up, but when I came to take it into the mistress’s room I saw it at once, and I suppose I ought to have taken it down again, and asked cook to make some fresh. But I was in a hurry, because Dorcas was out, and I thought maybe the cocoa itself was all right, and the salt had only gone on the tray. So I dusted it off with my apron, and took it in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had the utmost difficulty in controlling my excitement. Unknown to herself, Annie had provided us with an important piece of evidence. How she would have gaped if she had realized that her “coarse kitchen salt” was strychnine, one of the most deadly poisons known to mankind. I marvelled at Poirot’s calm. His self-control was astonishing. I awaited his next question with impatience, but it disappointed me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When you went into Mrs. Inglethorp’s room, was the door leading into Miss Cynthia’s room bolted?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh! Yes, sir; it always was. It had never been opened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the door into Mr. Inglethorp’s room? Did you notice if that was bolted too?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Annie hesitated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I couldn’t rightly say, sir; it was shut but I couldn’t say whether it was bolted or not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When you finally left the room, did Mrs. Inglethorp bolt the door after you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, not then, but I expect she did later. She usually did lock it at night. The door into the passage, that is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you notice any candle grease on the floor when you did the room yesterday?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Candle grease? Oh, no, sir. Mrs. Inglethorp didn’t have a candle, only a reading-lamp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, if there had been a large patch of candle grease on the floor, you think you would have been sure to have seen it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, and I would have taken it out with a piece of blotting-paper and a hot iron.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then Poirot repeated the question he had put to Dorcas:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did your mistress ever have a green dress?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nor a mantle, nor a cape, nor a—how do you call it?—a sports coat?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not green, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nor anyone else in the house?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Annie reflected.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are sure of that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Bien!</i> That is all I want to know. Thank you very much.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a nervous giggle, Annie took herself creakingly out of the room. My pent-up excitement burst forth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I cried, “I congratulate you! This is a great discovery.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is a great discovery?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, that it was the cocoa and not the coffee that was poisoned. That explains everything! Of course it did not take effect until the early morning, since the cocoa was only drunk in the middle of the night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So you think that the cocoa—mark well what I say, Hastings, the <i>cocoa</i>—contained strychnine?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course! That salt on the tray, what else could it have been?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It might have been salt,” replied Poirot placidly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shrugged my shoulders. If he was going to take the matter that way, it was no good arguing with him. The idea crossed my mind, not for the first time, that poor old Poirot was growing old. Privately I thought it lucky that he had associated with him someone of a more receptive type of mind.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was surveying me with quietly twinkling eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are not pleased with me, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Poirot,” I said coldly, “it is not for me to dictate to you. You have a right to your own opinion, just as I have to mine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A most admirable sentiment,” remarked Poirot, rising briskly to his feet. “Now I have finished with this room. By the way, whose is the smaller desk in the corner?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Inglethorp’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” He tried the roll top tentatively. “Locked. But perhaps one of Mrs. Inglethorp’s keys would open it.” He tried several, twisting and turning them with a practiced hand, and finally uttering an ejaculation of satisfaction. “<i>Voilà!</i> It is not the key, but it will open it at a pinch.” He slid back the roll top, and ran a rapid eye over the neatly filed papers. To my surprise, he did not examine them, merely remarking approvingly as he relocked the desk: “Decidedly, he is a man of method, this Mr. Inglethorp!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A “man of method” was, in Poirot’s estimation, the highest praise that could be bestowed on any individual.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I felt that my friend was not what he had been as he rambled on disconnectedly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There were no stamps in his desk, but there might have been, eh, <i>mon ami?</i> There might have been? Yes”—his eyes wandered round the room—“this boudoir has nothing more to tell us. It did not yield much. Only this.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He pulled a crumpled envelope out of his pocket, and tossed it over to me. It was rather a curious document. A plain, dirty looking old envelope with a few words scrawled across it, apparently at random. The following is a facsimile of it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><div class=\"fig c9\"><$link to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005250\"><img src=\"OEBPS/4521246603420151278_ill_004.png\" alt=\"Illustration:\"></$link></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER V.<br>\n“IT ISN’T STRYCHNINE, IS IT?”</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did you find this?” I asked Poirot, in lively curiosity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the waste-paper basket. You recognise the handwriting?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it is Mrs. Inglethorp’s. But what does it mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot say—but it is suggestive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A wild idea flashed across me. Was it possible that Mrs. Inglethorp’s mind was deranged? Had she some fantastic idea of demoniacal possession? And, if that were so, was it not also possible that she might have taken her own life?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was about to expound these theories to Poirot, when his own words distracted me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come,” he said, “now to examine the coffee-cups!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Poirot! What on earth is the good of that, now that we know about the cocoa?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, <i>là là!</i> That miserable cocoa!” cried Poirot flippantly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He laughed with apparent enjoyment, raising his arms to heaven in mock despair, in what I could not but consider the worst possible taste.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And, anyway,” I said, with increasing coldness, “as Mrs. Inglethorp took her coffee upstairs with her, I do not see what you expect to find, unless you consider it likely that we shall discover a packet of strychnine on the coffee tray!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was sobered at once.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come, come, my friend,” he said, slipping his arms through mine. “<i>Ne vous fâchez pas!</i> Allow me to interest myself in my coffee-cups, and I will respect your cocoa. There! Is it a bargain?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He was so quaintly humorous that I was forced to laugh; and we went together to the drawing-room, where the coffee-cups and tray remained undisturbed as we had left them.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot made me recapitulate the scene of the night before, listening very carefully, and verifying the position of the various cups.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So Mrs. Cavendish stood by the tray—and poured out. Yes. Then she came across to the window where you sat with Mademoiselle Cynthia. Yes. Here are the three cups. And the cup on the mantelpiece, half drunk, that would be Mr. Lawrence Cavendish’s. And the one on the tray?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John Cavendish’s. I saw him put it down there.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good. One, two, three, four, five—but where, then, is the cup of Mr. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He does not take coffee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then all are accounted for. One moment, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With infinite care, he took a drop or two from the grounds in each cup, sealing them up in separate test tubes, tasting each in turn as he did so. His physiognomy underwent a curious change. An expression gathered there that I can only describe as half puzzled, and half relieved.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Bien!</i>” he said at last. “It is evident! I had an idea—but clearly I was mistaken. Yes, altogether I was mistaken. Yet it is strange. But no matter!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, with a characteristic shrug, he dismissed whatever it was that was worrying him from his mind. I could have told him from the beginning that this obsession of his over the coffee was bound to end in a blind alley, but I restrained my tongue. After all, though he was old, Poirot had been a great man in his day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Breakfast is ready,” said John Cavendish, coming in from the hall. “You will breakfast with us, Monsieur Poirot?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot acquiesced. I observed John. Already he was almost restored to his normal self. The shock of the events of the last night had upset him temporarily, but his equable poise soon swung back to the normal. He was a man of very little imagination, in sharp contrast with his brother, who had, perhaps, too much.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Ever since the early hours of the morning, John had been hard at work, sending telegrams—one of the first had gone to Evelyn Howard—writing notices for the papers, and generally occupying himself with the melancholy duties that a death entails.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“May I ask how things are proceeding?” he said. “Do your investigations point to my mother having died a natural death—or—or must we prepare ourselves for the worst?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think, Mr. Cavendish,” said Poirot gravely, “that you would do well not to buoy yourself up with any false hopes. Can you tell me the views of the other members of the family?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My brother Lawrence is convinced that we are making a fuss over nothing. He says that everything points to its being a simple case of heart failure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He does, does he? That is very interesting—very interesting,” murmured Poirot softly. “And Mrs. Cavendish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A faint cloud passed over John’s face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have not the least idea what my wife’s views on the subject are.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The answer brought a momentary stiffness in its train. John broke the rather awkward silence by saying with a slight effort:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I told you, didn’t I, that Mr. Inglethorp has returned?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot bent his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s an awkward position for all of us. Of course one has to treat him as usual—but, hang it all, one’s gorge does rise at sitting down to eat with a possible murderer!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded sympathetically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I quite understand. It is a very difficult situation for you, Mr. Cavendish. I would like to ask you one question. Mr. Inglethorp’s reason for not returning last night was, I believe, that he had forgotten the latch-key. Is not that so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose you are quite sure that the latch-key <i>was</i> forgotten—that he did not take it after all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have no idea. I never thought of looking. We always keep it in the hall drawer. I’ll go and see if it’s there now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot held up his hand with a faint smile.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, Mr. Cavendish, it is too late now. I am certain that you would find it. If Mr. Inglethorp did take it, he has had ample time to replace it by now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But do you think——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think nothing. If anyone had chanced to look this morning before his return, and seen it there, it would have been a valuable point in his favour. That is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John looked perplexed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do not worry,” said Poirot smoothly. “I assure you that you need not let it trouble you. Since you are so kind, let us go and have some breakfast.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Everyone was assembled in the dining-room. Under the circumstances, we were naturally not a cheerful party. The reaction after a shock is always trying, and I think we were all suffering from it. Decorum and good breeding naturally enjoined that our demeanour should be much as usual, yet I could not help wondering if this self-control were really a matter of great difficulty. There were no red eyes, no signs of secretly indulged grief. I felt that I was right in my opinion that Dorcas was the person most affected by the personal side of the tragedy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I pass over Alfred Inglethorp, who acted the bereaved widower in a manner that I felt to be disgusting in its hypocrisy. Did he know that we suspected him, I wondered. Surely he could not be unaware of the fact, conceal it as we would. Did he feel some secret stirring of fear, or was he confident that his crime would go unpunished? Surely the suspicion in the atmosphere must warn him that he was already a marked man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But did everyone suspect him? What about Mrs. Cavendish? I watched her as she sat at the head of the table, graceful, composed, enigmatic. In her soft grey frock, with white ruffles at the wrists falling over her slender hands, she looked very beautiful. When she chose, however, her face could be sphinx-like in its inscrutability. She was very silent, hardly opening her lips, and yet in some queer way I felt that the great strength of her personality was dominating us all.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And little Cynthia? Did she suspect? She looked very tired and ill, I thought. The heaviness and languor of her manner were very marked. I asked her if she were feeling ill, and she answered frankly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I’ve got the most beastly headache.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have another cup of coffee, mademoiselle?” said Poirot solicitously. “It will revive you. It is unparalleled for the <i>mal de tête</i>.” He jumped up and took her cup.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No sugar,” said Cynthia, watching him, as he picked up the sugar-tongs.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No sugar? You abandon it in the war-time, eh?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I never take it in coffee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Sacré!</i>” murmured Poirot to himself, as he brought back the replenished cup.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Only I heard him, and glancing up curiously at the little man I saw that his face was working with suppressed excitement, and his eyes were as green as a cat’s. He had heard or seen something that had affected him strongly—but what was it? I do not usually label myself as dense, but I must confess that nothing out of the ordinary had attracted <i>my</i> attention.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In another moment, the door opened and Dorcas appeared.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Wells to see you, sir,” she said to John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I remembered the name as being that of the lawyer to whom Mrs. Inglethorp had written the night before.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John rose immediately.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Show him into my study.” Then he turned to us. “My mother’s lawyer,” he explained. And in a lower voice: “He is also Coroner—you understand. Perhaps you would like to come with me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We acquiesced and followed him out of the room. John strode on ahead and I took the opportunity of whispering to Poirot:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There will be an inquest then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded absently. He seemed absorbed in thought; so much so that my curiosity was aroused.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it? You are not attending to what I say.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is true, my friend. I am much worried.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because Mademoiselle Cynthia does not take sugar in her coffee.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What? You cannot be serious?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I am most serious. Ah, there is something there that I do not understand. My instinct was right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What instinct?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The instinct that led me to insist on examining those coffee-cups. <i>Chut!</i> no more now!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We followed John into his study, and he closed the door behind us.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Wells was a pleasant man of middle-age, with keen eyes, and the typical lawyer’s mouth. John introduced us both, and explained the reason of our presence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will understand, Wells,” he added, “that this is all strictly private. We are still hoping that there will turn out to be no need for investigation of any kind.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite so, quite so,” said Mr. Wells soothingly. “I wish we could have spared you the pain and publicity of an inquest, but of course it’s quite unavoidable in the absence of a doctor’s certificate.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I suppose so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Clever man, Bauerstein. Great authority on toxicology, I believe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed,” said John with a certain stiffness in his manner. Then he added rather hesitatingly: “Shall we have to appear as witnesses—all of us, I mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You, of course—and ah—er—Mr.—er—Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A slight pause ensued before the lawyer went on in his soothing manner:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Any other evidence will be simply confirmatory, a mere matter of form.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A faint expression of relief swept over John’s face. It puzzled me, for I saw no occasion for it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you know of nothing to the contrary,” pursued Mr. Wells, “I had thought of Friday. That will give us plenty of time for the doctor’s report. The post-mortem is to take place to-night, I believe?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then that arrangement will suit you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perfectly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I need not tell you, my dear Cavendish, how distressed I am at this most tragic affair.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can you give us no help in solving it, monsieur?” interposed Poirot, speaking for the first time since we had entered the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, we heard that Mrs. Inglethorp wrote to you last night. You should have received the letter this morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did, but it contains no information. It is merely a note asking me to call upon her this morning, as she wanted my advice on a matter of great importance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She gave you no hint as to what that matter might be?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Unfortunately, no.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is a pity,” said John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A great pity,” agreed Poirot gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was silence. Poirot remained lost in thought for a few minutes. Finally he turned to the lawyer again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Wells, there is one thing I should like to ask you—that is, if it is not against professional etiquette. In the event of Mrs. Inglethorp’s death, who would inherit her money?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The lawyer hesitated a moment, and then replied:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The knowledge will be public property very soon, so if Mr. Cavendish does not object——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all,” interpolated John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not see any reason why I should not answer your question. By her last will, dated August of last year, after various unimportant legacies to servants, etc., she gave her entire fortune to her stepson, Mr. John Cavendish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was not that—pardon the question, Mr. Cavendish—rather unfair to her other stepson, Mr. Lawrence Cavendish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I do not think so. You see, under the terms of their father’s will, while John inherited the property, Lawrence, at his stepmother’s death, would come into a considerable sum of money. Mrs. Inglethorp left her money to her elder stepson, knowing that he would have to keep up Styles. It was, to my mind, a very fair and equitable distribution.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see. But I am right in saying, am I not, that by your English law that will was automatically revoked when Mrs. Inglethorp remarried?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Wells bowed his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As I was about to proceed, Monsieur Poirot, that document is now null and void.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Hein!</i>” said Poirot. He reflected for a moment, and then asked: “Was Mrs. Inglethorp herself aware of that fact?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not know. She may have been.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She was,” said John unexpectedly. “We were discussing the matter of wills being revoked by marriage only yesterday.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! One more question, Mr. Wells. You say ‘her last will.’ Had Mrs. Inglethorp, then, made several former wills?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On an average, she made a new will at least once a year,” said Mr. Wells imperturbably. “She was given to changing her mind as to her testamentary dispositions, now benefiting one, now another member of her family.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Suppose,” suggested Poirot, “that, unknown to you, she had made a new will in favour of someone who was not, in any sense of the word, a member of the family—we will say Miss Howard, for instance—would you be surprised?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in the least.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” Poirot seemed to have exhausted his questions.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I drew close to him, while John and the lawyer were debating the question of going through Mrs. Inglethorp’s papers.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you think Mrs. Inglethorp made a will leaving all her money to Miss Howard?” I asked in a low voice, with some curiosity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then why did you ask?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hush!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John Cavendish had turned to Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will you come with us, Monsieur Poirot? We are going through my mother’s papers. Mr. Inglethorp is quite willing to leave it entirely to Mr. Wells and myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which simplifies matters very much,” murmured the lawyer. “As technically, of course, he was entitled——” He did not finish the sentence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We will look through the desk in the boudoir first,” explained John, “and go up to her bedroom afterwards. She kept her most important papers in a purple despatch-case, which we must look through carefully.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” said the lawyer, “it is quite possible that there may be a later will than the one in my possession.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There <i>is</i> a later will.” It was Poirot who spoke.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?” John and the lawyer looked at him startled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Or, rather,” pursued my friend imperturbably, “there <i>was</i> one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean—there was one? Where is it now?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Burnt!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Burnt?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. See here.” He took out the charred fragment we had found in the grate in Mrs. Inglethorp’s room, and handed it to the lawyer with a brief explanation of when and where he had found it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But possibly this is an old will?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not think so. In fact I am almost certain that it was made no earlier than yesterday afternoon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?” “Impossible!” broke simultaneously from both men.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot turned to John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you will allow me to send for your gardener, I will prove it to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, of course—but I don’t see——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot raised his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do as I ask you. Afterwards you shall question as much as you please.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well.” He rang the bell.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas answered it in due course.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dorcas, will you tell Manning to come round and speak to me here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas withdrew.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We waited in a tense silence. Poirot alone seemed perfectly at his ease, and dusted a forgotten corner of the bookcase.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The clumping of hobnailed boots on the gravel outside proclaimed the approach of Manning. John looked questioningly at Poirot. The latter nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come inside, Manning,” said John, “I want to speak to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Manning came slowly and hesitatingly through the French window, and stood as near it as he could. He held his cap in his hands, twisting it very carefully round and round. His back was much bent, though he was probably not as old as he looked, but his eyes were sharp and intelligent, and belied his slow and rather cautious speech.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Manning,” said John, “this gentleman will put some questions to you which I want you to answer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yessir,” mumbled Manning.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot stepped forward briskly. Manning’s eye swept over him with a faint contempt.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You were planting a bed of begonias round by the south side of the house yesterday afternoon, were you not, Manning?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, me and Willum.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And Mrs. Inglethorp came to the window and called you, did she not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, she did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tell me in your own words exactly what happened after that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, sir, nothing much. She just told Willum to go on his bicycle down to the village, and bring back a form of will, or such-like—I don’t know what exactly—she wrote it down for him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, he did, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what happened next?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We went on with the begonias, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did not Mrs. Inglethorp call you again?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, both me and Willum, she called.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She made us come right in, and sign our names at the bottom of a long paper—under where she’d signed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you see anything of what was written above her signature?” asked Poirot sharply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, there was a bit of blotting paper over that part.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you signed where she told you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, first me and then Willum.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What did she do with it afterwards?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, sir, she slipped it into a long envelope, and put it inside a sort of purple box that was standing on the desk.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What time was it when she first called you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About four, I should say, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not earlier? Couldn’t it have been about half-past three?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I shouldn’t say so, sir. It would be more likely to be a bit after four—not before it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, Manning, that will do,” said Poirot pleasantly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The gardener glanced at his master, who nodded, whereupon Manning lifted a finger to his forehead with a low mumble, and backed cautiously out of the window.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We all looked at each other.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” murmured John. “What an extraordinary coincidence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How—a coincidence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That my mother should have made a will on the very day of her death!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Wells cleared his throat and remarked drily:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Are you so sure it is a coincidence, Cavendish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your mother, you tell me, had a violent quarrel with—someone yesterday afternoon——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?” cried John again. There was a tremor in his voice, and he had gone very pale.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In consequence of that quarrel, your mother very suddenly and hurriedly makes a new will. The contents of that will we shall never know. She told no one of its provisions. This morning, no doubt, she would have consulted me on the subject—but she had no chance. The will disappears, and she takes its secret with her to her grave. Cavendish, I much fear there is no coincidence there. Monsieur Poirot, I am sure you agree with me that the facts are very suggestive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Suggestive, or not,” interrupted John, “we are most grateful to Monsieur Poirot for elucidating the matter. But for him, we should never have known of this will. I suppose, I may not ask you, monsieur, what first led you to suspect the fact?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot smiled and answered:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A scribbled over old envelope, and a freshly planted bed of begonias.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John, I think, would have pressed his questions further, but at that moment the loud purr of a motor was audible, and we all turned to the window as it swept past.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Evie!” cried John. “Excuse me, Wells.” He went hurriedly out into the hall.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked inquiringly at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard,” I explained.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, I am glad she has come. There is a woman with a head and a heart too, Hastings. Though the good God gave her no beauty!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I followed John’s example, and went out into the hall, where Miss Howard was endeavouring to extricate herself from the voluminous mass of veils that enveloped her head. As her eyes fell on me, a sudden pang of guilt shot through me. This was the woman who had warned me so earnestly, and to whose warning I had, alas, paid no heed! How soon, and how contemptuously, I had dismissed it from my mind. Now that she had been proved justified in so tragic a manner, I felt ashamed. She had known Alfred Inglethorp only too well. I wondered whether, if she had remained at Styles, the tragedy would have taken place, or would the man have feared her watchful eyes?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was relieved when she shook me by the hand, with her well remembered painful grip. The eyes that met mine were sad, but not reproachful; that she had been crying bitterly, I could tell by the redness of her eyelids, but her manner was unchanged from its old gruffness.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Started the moment I got the wire. Just come off night duty. Hired car. Quickest way to get here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you had anything to eat this morning, Evie?” asked John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I thought not. Come along, breakfast’s not cleared away yet, and they’ll make you some fresh tea.” He turned to me. “Look after her, Hastings, will you? Wells is waiting for me. Oh, here’s Monsieur Poirot. He’s helping us, you know, Evie.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard shook hands with Poirot, but glanced suspiciously over her shoulder at John.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean—helping us?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Helping us to investigate.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing to investigate. Have they taken him to prison yet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Taken who to prison?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who? Alfred Inglethorp, of course!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Evie, do be careful. Lawrence is of the opinion that my mother died from heart seizure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“More fool, Lawrence!” retorted Miss Howard. “Of course Alfred Inglethorp murdered poor Emily—as I always told you he would.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Evie, don’t shout so. Whatever we may think or suspect, it is better to say as little as possible for the present. The inquest isn’t until Friday.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not until fiddlesticks!” The snort Miss Howard gave was truly magnificent. “You’re all off your heads. The man will be out of the country by then. If he’s any sense, he won’t stay here tamely and wait to be hanged.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John Cavendish looked at her helplessly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know what it is,” she accused him, “you’ve been listening to the doctors. Never should. What do they know? Nothing at all—or just enough to make them dangerous. I ought to know—my own father was a doctor. That little Wilkins is about the greatest fool that even I have ever seen. Heart seizure! Sort of thing he would say. Anyone with any sense could see at once that her husband had poisoned her. I always said he’d murder her in her bed, poor soul. Now he’s done it. And all you can do is to murmur silly things about ‘heart seizure’ and ‘inquest on Friday.’ You ought to be ashamed of yourself, John Cavendish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you want me to do?” asked John, unable to help a faint smile. “Dash it all, Evie, I can’t haul him down to the local police station by the scruff of his neck.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, you might do something. Find out how he did it. He’s a crafty beggar. Dare say he soaked fly papers. Ask cook if she’s missed any.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It occurred to me very forcibly at that moment that to harbour Miss Howard and Alfred Inglethorp under the same roof, and keep the peace between them, was likely to prove a Herculean task, and I did not envy John. I could see by the expression of his face that he fully appreciated the difficulty of the position. For the moment, he sought refuge in retreat, and left the room precipitately.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas brought in fresh tea. As she left the room, Poirot came over from the window where he had been standing, and sat down facing Miss Howard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mademoiselle,” he said gravely, “I want to ask you something.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ask away,” said the lady, eyeing him with some disfavour.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I want to be able to count upon your help.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ll help you to hang Alfred with pleasure,” she replied gruffly. “Hanging’s too good for him. Ought to be drawn and quartered, like in good old times.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We are at one then,” said Poirot, “for I, too, want to hang the criminal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Alfred Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Him, or another.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No question of another. Poor Emily was never murdered until <i>he</i> came along. I don’t say she wasn’t surrounded by sharks—she was. But it was only her purse they were after. Her life was safe enough. But along comes Mr. Alfred Inglethorp—and within two months—hey presto!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Believe me, Miss Howard,” said Poirot very earnestly, “if Mr. Inglethorp is the man, he shall not escape me. On my honour, I will hang him as high as Haman!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s better,” said Miss Howard more enthusiastically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I must ask you to trust me. Now your help may be very valuable to me. I will tell you why. Because, in all this house of mourning, yours are the only eyes that have wept.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard blinked, and a new note crept into the gruffness of her voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you mean that I was fond of her—yes, I was. You know, Emily was a selfish old woman in her way. She was very generous, but she always wanted a return. She never let people forget what she had done for them—and, that way she missed love. Don’t think she ever realized it, though, or felt the lack of it. Hope not, anyway. I was on a different footing. I took my stand from the first. ‘So many pounds a year I’m worth to you. Well and good. But not a penny piece besides—not a pair of gloves, nor a theatre ticket.’ She didn’t understand—was very offended sometimes. Said I was foolishly proud. It wasn’t that—but I couldn’t explain. Anyway, I kept my self-respect. And so, out of the whole bunch, I was the only one who could allow myself to be fond of her. I watched over her. I guarded her from the lot of them, and then a glib-tongued scoundrel comes along, and pooh! all my years of devotion go for nothing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded sympathetically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I understand, mademoiselle, I understand all you feel. It is most natural. You think that we are lukewarm—that we lack fire and energy—but trust me, it is not so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John stuck his head in at this juncture, and invited us both to come up to Mrs. Inglethorp’s room, as he and Mr. Wells had finished looking through the desk in the boudoir.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we went up the stairs, John looked back to the dining-room door, and lowered his voice confidentially:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look here, what’s going to happen when these two meet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head helplessly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve told Mary to keep them apart if she can.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will she be able to do so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Lord only knows. There’s one thing, Inglethorp himself won’t be too keen on meeting her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ve got the keys still, haven’t you, Poirot?” I asked, as we reached the door of the locked room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Taking the keys from Poirot, John unlocked it, and we all passed in. The lawyer went straight to the desk, and John followed him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My mother kept most of her important papers in this despatch-case, I believe,” he said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot drew out the small bunch of keys.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Permit me. I locked it, out of precaution, this morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it’s not locked now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Impossible!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“See.” And John lifted the lid as he spoke.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Milles tonnerres!</i>” cried Poirot, dumbfounded. “And I—who have both the keys in my pocket!” He flung himself upon the case. Suddenly he stiffened. “<i>Eh voilà une affaire!</i> This lock has been forced.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot laid down the case again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But who forced it? Why should they? When? But the door was locked?” These exclamations burst from us disjointedly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot answered them categorically—almost mechanically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who? That is the question. Why? Ah, if I only knew. When? Since I was here an hour ago. As to the door being locked, it is a very ordinary lock. Probably any other of the doorkeys in this passage would fit it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We stared at one another blankly. Poirot had walked over to the mantelpiece. He was outwardly calm, but I noticed his hands, which from long force of habit were mechanically straightening the spill vases on the mantelpiece, were shaking violently.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“See here, it was like this,” he said at last. “There was something in that case—some piece of evidence, slight in itself perhaps, but still enough of a clue to connect the murderer with the crime. It was vital to him that it should be destroyed before it was discovered and its significance appreciated. Therefore, he took the risk, the great risk, of coming in here. Finding the case locked, he was obliged to force it, thus betraying his presence. For him to take that risk, it must have been something of great importance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what was it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” cried Poirot, with a gesture of anger. “That, I do not know! A document of some kind, without doubt, possibly the scrap of paper Dorcas saw in her hand yesterday afternoon. And I—” his anger burst forth freely—“miserable animal that I am! I guessed nothing! I have behaved like an imbecile! I should never have left that case here. I should have carried it away with me. Ah, triple pig! And now it is gone. It is destroyed—but is it destroyed? Is there not yet a chance—we must leave no stone unturned—”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He rushed like a madman from the room, and I followed him as soon as I had sufficiently recovered my wits. But, by the time I had reached the top of the stairs, he was out of sight.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary Cavendish was standing where the staircase branched, staring down into the hall in the direction in which he had disappeared.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What has happened to your extraordinary little friend, Mr. Hastings? He has just rushed past me like a mad bull.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s rather upset about something,” I remarked feebly. I really did not know how much Poirot would wish me to disclose. As I saw a faint smile gather on Mrs. Cavendish’s expressive mouth, I endeavoured to try and turn the conversation by saying: “They haven’t met yet, have they?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Inglethorp and Miss Howard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She looked at me in rather a disconcerting manner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you think it would be such a disaster if they did meet?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, don’t you?” I said, rather taken aback.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.” She was smiling in her quiet way. “I should like to see a good flare up. It would clear the air. At present we are all thinking so much, and saying so little.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John doesn’t think so,” I remarked. “He’s anxious to keep them apart.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, John!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Something in her tone fired me, and I blurted out:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Old John’s an awfully good sort.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She studied me curiously for a minute or two, and then said, to my great surprise:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are loyal to your friend. I like you for that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Aren’t you my friend too?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am a very bad friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why do you say that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because it is true. I am charming to my friends one day, and forget all about them the next.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I don’t know what impelled me, but I was nettled, and I said foolishly and not in the best of taste:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yet you seem to be invariably charming to Dr. Bauerstein!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Instantly I regretted my words. Her face stiffened. I had the impression of a steel curtain coming down and blotting out the real woman. Without a word, she turned and went swiftly up the stairs, whilst I stood like an idiot gaping after her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was recalled to other matters by a frightful row going on below. I could hear Poirot shouting and expounding. I was vexed to think that my diplomacy had been in vain. The little man appeared to be taking the whole house into his confidence, a proceeding of which I, for one, doubted the wisdom. Once again I could not help regretting that my friend was so prone to lose his head in moments of excitement. I stepped briskly down the stairs. The sight of me calmed Poirot almost immediately. I drew him aside.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear fellow,” I said, “is this wise? Surely you don’t want the whole house to know of this occurrence? You are actually playing into the criminal’s hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You think so, Hastings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sure of it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, well, my friend, I will be guided by you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good. Although, unfortunately, it is a little too late now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He looked so crestfallen and abashed that I felt quite sorry, though I still thought my rebuke a just and wise one.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” he said at last, “let us go, <i>mon ami</i>.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have finished here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“For the moment, yes. You will walk back with me to the village?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Willingly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He picked up his little suit-case, and we went out through the open window in the drawing-room. Cynthia Murdoch was just coming in, and Poirot stood aside to let her pass.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excuse me, mademoiselle, one minute.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?” she turned inquiringly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you ever make up Mrs. Inglethorp’s medicines?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A slight flush rose in her face, as she answered rather constrainedly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only her powders?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The flush deepened as Cynthia replied:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, I did make up some sleeping powders for her once.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“These?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot produced the empty box which had contained powders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can you tell me what they were? Sulphonal? Veronal?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, they were bromide powders.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! Thank you, mademoiselle; good morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we walked briskly away from the house, I glanced at him more than once. I had often before noticed that, if anything excited him, his eyes turned green like a cat’s. They were shining like emeralds now.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My friend,” he broke out at last, “I have a little idea, a very strange, and probably utterly impossible idea. And yet—it fits in.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shrugged my shoulders. I privately thought that Poirot was rather too much given to these fantastic ideas. In this case, surely, the truth was only too plain and apparent.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So that is the explanation of the blank label on the box,” I remarked. “Very simple, as you said. I really wonder that I did not think of it myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot did not appear to be listening to me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They have made one more discovery, <i>là-bas</i>,” he observed, jerking his thumb over his shoulder in the direction of Styles. “Mr. Wells told me as we were going upstairs.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What was it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Locked up in the desk in the boudoir, they found a will of Mrs. Inglethorp’s, dated before her marriage, leaving her fortune to Alfred Inglethorp. It must have been made just at the time they were engaged. It came quite as a surprise to Wells—and to John Cavendish also. It was written on one of those printed will forms, and witnessed by two of the servants—not Dorcas.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did Mr. Inglethorp know of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He says not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One might take that with a grain of salt,” I remarked sceptically. “All these wills are very confusing. Tell me, how did those scribbled words on the envelope help you to discover that a will was made yesterday afternoon?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mon ami</i>, have you ever, when writing a letter, been arrested by the fact that you did not know how to spell a certain word?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, often. I suppose everyone has.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. And have you not, in such a case, tried the word once or twice on the edge of the blotting-paper, or a spare scrap of paper, to see if it looked right? Well, that is what Mrs. Inglethorp did. You will notice that the word ‘possessed’ is spelt first with one ‘s’ and subsequently with two—correctly. To make sure, she had further tried it in a sentence, thus: ‘I am possessed.’ Now, what did that tell me? It told me that Mrs. Inglethorp had been writing the word ‘possessed’ that afternoon, and, having the fragment of paper found in the grate fresh in my mind, the possibility of a will—(a document almost certain to contain that word)—occurred to me at once. This possibility was confirmed by a further circumstance. In the general confusion, the boudoir had not been swept that morning, and near the desk were several traces of brown mould and earth. The weather had been perfectly fine for some days, and no ordinary boots would have left such a heavy deposit.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I strolled to the window, and saw at once that the begonia beds had been newly planted. The mould in the beds was exactly similar to that on the floor of the boudoir, and also I learnt from you that they <i>had</i> been planted yesterday afternoon. I was now sure that one, or possibly both of the gardeners—for there were two sets of footprints in the bed—had entered the boudoir, for if Mrs. Inglethorp had merely wished to speak to them she would in all probability have stood at the window, and they would not have come into the room at all. I was now quite convinced that she had made a fresh will, and had called the two gardeners in to witness her signature. Events proved that I was right in my supposition.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was very ingenious,” I could not help admitting. “I must confess that the conclusions I drew from those few scribbled words were quite erroneous.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You gave too much rein to your imagination. Imagination is a good servant, and a bad master. The simplest explanation is always the most likely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Another point—how did you know that the key of the despatch-case had been lost?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did not know it. It was a guess that turned out to be correct. You observed that it had a piece of twisted wire through the handle. That suggested to me at once that it had possibly been wrenched off a flimsy key-ring. Now, if it had been lost and recovered, Mrs. Inglethorp would at once have replaced it on her bunch; but on her bunch I found what was obviously the duplicate key, very new and bright, which led me to the hypothesis that somebody else had inserted the original key in the lock of the despatch-case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” I said, “Alfred Inglethorp, without doubt.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked at me curiously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are very sure of his guilt?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, naturally. Every fresh circumstance seems to establish it more clearly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary,” said Poirot quietly, “there are several points in his favour.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, come now!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see only one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That he was not in the house last night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Bad shot!’ as you English say! You have chosen the one point that to my mind tells against him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How is that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because if Mr. Inglethorp knew that his wife would be poisoned last night, he would certainly have arranged to be away from the house. His excuse was an obviously trumped up one. That leaves us two possibilities: either he knew what was going to happen or he had a reason of his own for his absence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that reason?” I asked sceptically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How should I know? Discreditable, without doubt. This Mr. Inglethorp, I should say, is somewhat of a scoundrel—but that does not of necessity make him a murderer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head, unconvinced.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We do not agree, eh?” said Poirot. “Well, let us leave it. Time will show which of us is right. Now let us turn to other aspects of the case. What do you make of the fact that all the doors of the bedroom were bolted on the inside?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well——” I considered. “One must look at it logically.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“True.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should put it this way. The doors <i>were</i> bolted—our own eyes have told us that—yet the presence of the candle grease on the floor, and the destruction of the will, prove that during the night someone entered the room. You agree so far?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perfectly. Put with admirable clearness. Proceed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” I said, encouraged, “as the person who entered did not do so by the window, nor by miraculous means, it follows that the door must have been opened from inside by Mrs. Inglethorp herself. That strengthens the conviction that the person in question was her husband. She would naturally open the door to her own husband.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why should she? She had bolted the door leading into his room—a most unusual proceeding on her part—she had had a most violent quarrel with him that very afternoon. No, he was the last person she would admit.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you agree with me that the door must have been opened by Mrs. Inglethorp herself?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is another possibility. She may have forgotten to bolt the door into the passage when she went to bed, and have got up later, towards morning, and bolted it then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot, is that seriously your opinion?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I do not say it is so, but it might be. Now, to turn to another feature, what do you make of the scrap of conversation you overheard between Mrs. Cavendish and her mother-in-law?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I had forgotten that,” I said thoughtfully. “That is as enigmatical as ever. It seems incredible that a woman like Mrs. Cavendish, proud and reticent to the last degree, should interfere so violently in what was certainly not her affair.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely. It was an astonishing thing for a woman of her breeding to do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is certainly curious,” I agreed. “Still, it is unimportant, and need not be taken into account.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A groan burst from Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What have I always told you? Everything must be taken into account. If the fact will not fit the theory—let the theory go.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, we shall see,” I said, nettled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, we shall see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had reached Leastways Cottage, and Poirot ushered me upstairs to his own room. He offered me one of the tiny Russian cigarettes he himself occasionally smoked. I was amused to notice that he stowed away the used matches most carefully in a little china pot. My momentary annoyance vanished.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot had placed our two chairs in front of the open window which commanded a view of the village street. The fresh air blew in warm and pleasant. It was going to be a hot day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly my attention was arrested by a weedy looking young man rushing down the street at a great pace. It was the expression on his face that was extraordinary—a curious mingling of terror and agitation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look, Poirot!” I said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He leant forward.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Tiens!</i>” he said. “It is Mr. Mace, from the chemist’s shop. He is coming here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The young man came to a halt before Leastways Cottage, and, after hesitating a moment, pounded vigorously at the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A little minute,” cried Poirot from the window. “I come.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Motioning to me to follow him, he ran swiftly down the stairs and opened the door. Mr. Mace began at once.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, Mr. Poirot, I’m sorry for the inconvenience, but I heard that you’d just come back from the Hall?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, we have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The young man moistened his dry lips. His face was working curiously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s all over the village about old Mrs. Inglethorp dying so suddenly. They do say—” he lowered his voice cautiously—“that it’s poison?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot’s face remained quite impassive.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Only the doctors can tell us that, Mr. Mace.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, exactly—of course——” The young man hesitated, and then his agitation was too much for him. He clutched Poirot by the arm, and sank his voice to a whisper: “Just tell me this, Mr. Poirot, it isn’t—it isn’t strychnine, is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I hardly heard what Poirot replied. Something evidently of a non-committal nature. The young man departed, and as he closed the door Poirot’s eyes met mine.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” he said, nodding gravely. “He will have evidence to give at the inquest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We went slowly upstairs again. I was opening my lips, when Poirot stopped me with a gesture of his hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not now, not now, <i>mon ami</i>. I have need of reflection. My mind is in some disorder—which is not well.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For about ten minutes he sat in dead silence, perfectly still, except for several expressive motions of his eyebrows, and all the time his eyes grew steadily greener. At last he heaved a deep sigh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is well. The bad moment has passed. Now all is arranged and classified. One must never permit confusion. The case is not clear yet—no. For it is of the most complicated! It puzzles <i>me</i>. <i>Me</i>, Hercule Poirot! There are two facts of significance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what are they?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The first is the state of the weather yesterday. That is very important.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it was a glorious day!” I interrupted. “Poirot, you’re pulling my leg!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. The thermometer registered 80 degrees in the shade. Do not forget that, my friend. It is the key to the whole riddle!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the second point?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The important fact that Monsieur Inglethorp wears very peculiar clothes, has a black beard, and uses glasses.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot, I cannot believe you are serious.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am absolutely serious, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But this is childish!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, it is very momentous.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And supposing the Coroner’s jury returns a verdict of Wilful Murder against Alfred Inglethorp. What becomes of your theories, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They would not be shaken because twelve stupid men had happened to make a mistake! But that will not occur. For one thing, a country jury is not anxious to take responsibility upon itself, and Mr. Inglethorp stands practically in the position of local squire. Also,” he added placidly, “<i>I</i> should not allow it!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>You</i> would not allow it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked at the extraordinary little man, divided between annoyance and amusement. He was so tremendously sure of himself. As though he read my thoughts, he nodded gently.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, <i>mon ami</i>, I would do what I say.” He got up and laid his hand on my shoulder. His physiognomy underwent a complete change. Tears came into his eyes. “In all this, you see, I think of that poor Mrs. Inglethorp who is dead. She was not extravagantly loved—no. But she was very good to us Belgians—I owe her a debt.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I endeavoured to interrupt, but Poirot swept on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let me tell you this, Hastings. She would never forgive me if I let Alfred Inglethorp, her husband, be arrested <i>now</i>—when a word from me could save him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER VI.<br>\nTHE INQUEST</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In the interval before the inquest, Poirot was unfailing in his activity. Twice he was closeted with Mr. Wells. He also took long walks into the country. I rather resented his not taking me into his confidence, the more so as I could not in the least guess what he was driving at.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It occurred to me that he might have been making inquiries at Raikes’s farm; so, finding him out when I called at Leastways Cottage on Wednesday evening, I walked over there by the fields, hoping to meet him. But there was no sign of him, and I hesitated to go right up to the farm itself. As I walked away, I met an aged rustic, who leered at me cunningly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’m from the Hall, bain’t you?” he asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I’m looking for a friend of mine whom I thought might have walked this way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A little chap? As waves his hands when he talks? One of them Belgies from the village?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” I said eagerly. “He has been here, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, ay, he’s been here, right enough. More’n once too. Friend of yours, is he? Ah, you gentlemen from the Hall—you’m a pretty lot!” And he leered more jocosely than ever.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, do the gentlemen from the Hall come here often?” I asked, as carelessly as I could.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He winked at me knowingly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>One</i> does, mister. Naming no names, mind. And a very liberal gentleman too! Oh, thank you, sir, I’m sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I walked on sharply. Evelyn Howard had been right then, and I experienced a sharp twinge of disgust, as I thought of Alfred Inglethorp’s liberality with another woman’s money. Had that piquant gipsy face been at the bottom of the crime, or was it the baser mainspring of money? Probably a judicious mixture of both.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>On one point, Poirot seemed to have a curious obsession. He once or twice observed to me that he thought Dorcas must have made an error in fixing the time of the quarrel. He suggested to her repeatedly that it was four-thirty, and not four o’clock when she had heard the voices.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Dorcas was unshaken. Quite an hour, or even more, had elapsed between the time when she had heard the voices and five o’clock, when she had taken tea to her mistress.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The inquest was held on Friday at the Stylites Arms in the village. Poirot and I sat together, not being required to give evidence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The preliminaries were gone through. The jury viewed the body, and John Cavendish gave evidence of identification.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Further questioned, he described his awakening in the early hours of the morning, and the circumstances of his mother’s death.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The medical evidence was next taken. There was a breathless hush, and every eye was fixed on the famous London specialist, who was known to be one of the greatest authorities of the day on the subject of toxicology.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few brief words, he summed up the result of the post-mortem. Shorn of its medical phraseology and technicalities, it amounted to the fact that Mrs. Inglethorp had met her death as the result of strychnine poisoning. Judging from the quantity recovered, she must have taken not less than three-quarters of a grain of strychnine, but probably one grain or slightly over.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it possible that she could have swallowed the poison by accident?” asked the Coroner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should consider it very unlikely. Strychnine is not used for domestic purposes, as some poisons are, and there are restrictions placed on its sale.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Does anything in your examination lead you to determine how the poison was administered?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You arrived at Styles before Dr. Wilkins, I believe?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is so. The motor met me just outside the lodge gates, and I hurried there as fast as I could.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will you relate to us exactly what happened next?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I entered Mrs. Inglethorp’s room. She was at that moment in a typical tetanic convulsion. She turned towards me, and gasped out: ‘Alfred—Alfred——’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Could the strychnine have been administered in Mrs. Inglethorp’s after-dinner coffee which was taken to her by her husband?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Possibly, but strychnine is a fairly rapid drug in its action. The symptoms appear from one to two hours after it has been swallowed. It is retarded under certain conditions, none of which, however, appear to have been present in this case. I presume Mrs. Inglethorp took the coffee after dinner about eight o’clock, whereas the symptoms did not manifest themselves until the early hours of the morning, which, on the face of it, points to the drug having been taken much later in the evening.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Inglethorp was in the habit of drinking a cup of cocoa in the middle of the night. Could the strychnine have been administered in that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I myself took a sample of the cocoa remaining in the saucepan and had it analysed. There was no strychnine present.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I heard Poirot chuckle softly beside me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you know?” I whispered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Listen.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should say”—the doctor was continuing—“that I would have been considerably surprised at any other result.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Simply because strychnine has an unusually bitter taste. It can be detected in a solution of one in seventy thousand, and can only be disguised by some strongly flavoured substance. Cocoa would be quite powerless to mask it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>One of the jury wanted to know if the same objection applied to coffee.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. Coffee has a bitter taste of its own which would probably cover the taste of strychnine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you consider it more likely that the drug was administered in the coffee, but that for some unknown reason its action was delayed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but, the cup being completely smashed, there is no possibility of analyzing its contents.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This concluded Dr. Bauerstein’s evidence. Dr. Wilkins corroborated it on all points. Sounded as to the possibility of suicide, he repudiated it utterly. The deceased, he said, suffered from a weak heart, but otherwise enjoyed perfect health, and was of a cheerful and well-balanced disposition. She would be one of the last people to take her own life.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence Cavendish was next called. His evidence was quite unimportant, being a mere repetition of that of his brother. Just as he was about to step down, he paused, and said rather hesitatingly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should like to make a suggestion if I may?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He glanced deprecatingly at the Coroner, who replied briskly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, Mr. Cavendish, we are here to arrive at the truth of this matter, and welcome anything that may lead to further elucidation.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is just an idea of mine,” explained Lawrence. “Of course I may be quite wrong, but it still seems to me that my mother’s death might be accounted for by natural means.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you make that out, Mr. Cavendish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My mother, at the time of her death, and for some time before it, was taking a tonic containing strychnine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” said the Coroner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The jury looked up, interested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I believe,” continued Lawrence, “that there have been cases where the cumulative effect of a drug, administered for some time, has ended by causing death. Also, is it not possible that she may have taken an overdose of her medicine by accident?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is the first we have heard of the deceased taking strychnine at the time of her death. We are much obliged to you, Mr. Cavendish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dr. Wilkins was recalled and ridiculed the idea.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What Mr. Cavendish suggests is quite impossible. Any doctor would tell you the same. Strychnine is, in a certain sense, a cumulative poison, but it would be quite impossible for it to result in sudden death in this way. There would have to be a long period of chronic symptoms which would at once have attracted my attention. The whole thing is absurd.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the second suggestion? That Mrs. Inglethorp may have inadvertently taken an overdose?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Three, or even four doses, would not have resulted in death. Mrs. Inglethorp always had an extra large amount of medicine made up at a time, as she dealt with Coot’s, the Cash Chemists in Tadminster. She would have had to take very nearly the whole bottle to account for the amount of strychnine found at the post-mortem.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you consider that we may dismiss the tonic as not being in any way instrumental in causing her death?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly. The supposition is ridiculous.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The same juryman who had interrupted before here suggested that the chemist who made up the medicine might have committed an error.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That, of course, is always possible,” replied the doctor.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Dorcas, who was the next witness called, dispelled even that possibility. The medicine had not been newly made up. On the contrary, Mrs. Inglethorp had taken the last dose on the day of her death.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>So the question of the tonic was finally abandoned, and the Coroner proceeded with his task. Having elicited from Dorcas how she had been awakened by the violent ringing of her mistress’s bell, and had subsequently roused the household, he passed to the subject of the quarrel on the preceding afternoon.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas’s evidence on this point was substantially what Poirot and I had already heard, so I will not repeat it here.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The next witness was Mary Cavendish. She stood very upright, and spoke in a low, clear, and perfectly composed voice. In answer to the Coroner’s question, she told how, her alarm clock having aroused her at four-thirty as usual, she was dressing, when she was startled by the sound of something heavy falling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That would have been the table by the bed?” commented the Coroner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I opened my door,” continued Mary, “and listened. In a few minutes a bell rang violently. Dorcas came running down and woke my husband, and we all went to my mother-in-law’s room, but it was locked——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner interrupted her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I really do not think we need trouble you further on that point. We know all that can be known of the subsequent happenings. But I should be obliged if you would tell us all you overheard of the quarrel the day before.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a faint insolence in her voice. She raised her hand and adjusted the ruffle of lace at her neck, turning her head a little as she did so. And quite spontaneously the thought flashed across my mind: “She is gaining time!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I understand,” continued the Coroner deliberately, “that you were sitting reading on the bench just outside the long window of the boudoir. That is so, is it not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This was news to me and glancing sideways at Poirot, I fancied that it was news to him as well.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was the faintest pause, the mere hesitation of a moment, before she answered:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that is so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the boudoir window was open, was it not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Surely her face grew a little paler as she answered:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you cannot have failed to hear the voices inside, especially as they were raised in anger. In fact, they would be more audible where you were than in the hall.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Possibly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will you repeat to us what you overheard of the quarrel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I really do not remember hearing anything.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you mean to say you did not hear voices?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, I heard the voices, but I did not hear what they said.” A faint spot of colour came into her cheek. “I am not in the habit of listening to private conversations.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner persisted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you remember nothing at all? <i>Nothing</i>, Mrs. Cavendish? Not one stray word or phrase to make you realize that it <i>was</i> a private conversation?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She paused, and seemed to reflect, still outwardly as calm as ever.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes; I remember. Mrs. Inglethorp said something—I do not remember exactly what—about causing scandal between husband and wife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” the Coroner leant back satisfied. “That corresponds with what Dorcas heard. But excuse me, Mrs. Cavendish, although you realized it was a private conversation, you did not move away? You remained where you were?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I caught the momentary gleam of her tawny eyes as she raised them. I felt certain that at that moment she would willingly have torn the little lawyer, with his insinuations, into pieces, but she replied quietly enough:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. I was very comfortable where I was. I fixed my mind on my book.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that is all you can tell us?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The examination was over, though I doubted if the Coroner was entirely satisfied with it. I think he suspected that Mary Cavendish could tell more if she chose.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Amy Hill, shop assistant, was next called, and deposed to having sold a will form on the afternoon of the 17th to William Earl, under-gardener at Styles.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>William Earl and Manning succeeded her, and testified to witnessing a document. Manning fixed the time at about four-thirty, William was of the opinion that it was rather earlier.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia Murdoch came next. She had, however, little to tell. She had known nothing of the tragedy, until awakened by Mrs. Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You did not hear the table fall?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. I was fast asleep.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A good conscience makes a sound sleeper,” he observed. “Thank you, Miss Murdoch, that is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard produced the letter written to her by Mrs. Inglethorp on the evening of the 17th. Poirot and I had, of course already seen it. It added nothing to our knowledge of the tragedy. The following is a facsimile:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">STYLES COURT<br>\nESSEX<br>\nhand written note:<br>\n<br>\nJuly 17th<br>\nMy dear Evelyn<br>\nCan we not bury<br>\nthe hachet? I have<br>\nfound it hard to forgive<br>\nthe things you said<br>\nagainst my dear husband<br>\nbut I am an old woman<br>\n&amp; very fond of you<br>\nYours affectionately,<br>\nEmily Inglethorpe<br></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was handed to the jury who scrutinized it attentively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fear it does not help us much,” said the Coroner, with a sigh. “There is no mention of any of the events of that afternoon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Plain as a pikestaff to me,” said Miss Howard shortly. “It shows clearly enough that my poor old friend had just found out she’d been made a fool of!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It says nothing of the kind in the letter,” the Coroner pointed out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, because Emily never could bear to put herself in the wrong. But <i>I</i> know her. She wanted me back. But she wasn’t going to own that I’d been right. She went round about. Most people do. Don’t believe in it myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Wells smiled faintly. So, I noticed, did several of the jury. Miss Howard was obviously quite a public character.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Anyway, all this tomfoolery is a great waste of time,” continued the lady, glancing up and down the jury disparagingly. “Talk—talk—talk! When all the time we know perfectly well——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner interrupted her in an agony of apprehension:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you, Miss Howard, that is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I fancy he breathed a sigh of relief when she complied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then came the sensation of the day. The Coroner called Albert Mace, chemist’s assistant.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was our agitated young man of the pale face. In answer to the Coroner’s questions, he explained that he was a qualified pharmacist, but had only recently come to this particular shop, as the assistant formerly there had just been called up for the army.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>These preliminaries completed, the Coroner proceeded to business.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Mace, have you lately sold strychnine to any unauthorized person?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When was this?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Last Monday night.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Monday? Not Tuesday?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, Monday, the 16th.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Will you tell us to whom you sold it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>You could have heard a pin drop.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir. It was to Mr. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Every eye turned simultaneously to where Alfred Inglethorp was sitting, impassive and wooden. He started slightly, as the damning words fell from the young man’s lips. I half thought he was going to rise from his chair, but he remained seated, although a remarkably well acted expression of astonishment rose on his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are sure of what you say?” asked the Coroner sternly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite sure, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Are you in the habit of selling strychnine indiscriminately over the counter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The wretched young man wilted visibly under the Coroner’s frown.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, sir—of course not. But, seeing it was Mr. Inglethorp of the Hall, I thought there was no harm in it. He said it was to poison a dog.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inwardly I sympathized. It was only human nature to endeavour to please “The Hall”—especially when it might result in custom being transferred from Coot’s to the local establishment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it not customary for anyone purchasing poison to sign a book?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, Mr. Inglethorp did so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you got the book here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was produced; and, with a few words of stern censure, the Coroner dismissed the wretched Mr. Mace.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then, amidst a breathless silence, Alfred Inglethorp was called. Did he realize, I wondered, how closely the halter was being drawn around his neck?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner went straight to the point.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On Monday evening last, did you purchase strychnine for the purpose of poisoning a dog?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inglethorp replied with perfect calmness:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I did not. There is no dog at Styles, except an outdoor sheepdog, which is in perfect health.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You deny absolutely having purchased strychnine from Albert Mace on Monday last?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you also deny <i>this</i>?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner handed him the register in which his signature was inscribed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly I do. The hand-writing is quite different from mine. I will show you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He took an old envelope out of his pocket, and wrote his name on it, handing it to the jury. It was certainly utterly dissimilar.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then what is your explanation of Mr. Mace’s statement?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Alfred Inglethorp replied imperturbably:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Mace must have been mistaken.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner hesitated for a moment, and then said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Inglethorp, as a mere matter of form, would you mind telling us where you were on the evening of Monday, July 16th?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really—I cannot remember.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is absurd, Mr. Inglethorp,” said the Coroner sharply. “Think again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inglethorp shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I cannot tell you. I have an idea that I was out walking.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In what direction?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I really can’t remember.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner’s face grew graver.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Were you in company with anyone?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you meet anyone on your walk?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is a pity,” said the Coroner dryly. “I am to take it then that you decline to say where you were at the time that Mr. Mace positively recognized you as entering the shop to purchase strychnine?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you like to take it that way, yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Be careful, Mr. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was fidgeting nervously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Sacré!</i>” he murmured. “Does this imbecile of a man <i>want</i> to be arrested?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inglethorp was indeed creating a bad impression. His futile denials would not have convinced a child. The Coroner, however, passed briskly to the next point, and Poirot drew a deep breath of relief.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You had a discussion with your wife on Tuesday afternoon?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pardon me,” interrupted Alfred Inglethorp, “you have been misinformed. I had no quarrel with my dear wife. The whole story is absolutely untrue. I was absent from the house the entire afternoon.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you anyone who can testify to that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have my word,” said Inglethorp haughtily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner did not trouble to reply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There are two witnesses who will swear to having heard your disagreement with Mrs. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Those witnesses were mistaken.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was puzzled. The man spoke with such quiet assurance that I was staggered. I looked at Poirot. There was an expression of exultation on his face which I could not understand. Was he at last convinced of Alfred Inglethorp’s guilt?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Inglethorp,” said the Coroner, “you have heard your wife’s dying words repeated here. Can you explain them in any way?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly I can.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It seems to me very simple. The room was dimly lighted. Dr. Bauerstein is much of my height and build, and, like me, wears a beard. In the dim light, and suffering as she was, my poor wife mistook him for me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” murmured Poirot to himself. “But it is an idea, that!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You think it is true?” I whispered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not say that. But it is truly an ingenious supposition.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You read my wife’s last words as an accusation”—Inglethorp was continuing—“they were, on the contrary, an appeal to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The Coroner reflected a moment, then he said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I believe, Mr. Inglethorp, that you yourself poured out the coffee, and took it to your wife that evening?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I poured it out, yes. But I did not take it to her. I meant to do so, but I was told that a friend was at the hall door, so I laid down the coffee on the hall table. When I came through the hall again a few minutes later, it was gone.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This statement might, or might not, be true, but it did not seem to me to improve matters much for Inglethorp. In any case, he had had ample time to introduce the poison.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At that point, Poirot nudged me gently, indicating two men who were sitting together near the door. One was a little, sharp, dark, ferret-faced man, the other was tall and fair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I questioned Poirot mutely. He put his lips to my ear.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you know who that little man is?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is Detective Inspector James Japp of Scotland Yard—Jimmy Japp. The other man is from Scotland Yard too. Things are moving quickly, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I stared at the two men intently. There was certainly nothing of the policeman about them. I should never have suspected them of being official personages.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was still staring, when I was startled and recalled by the verdict being given:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wilful Murder against some person or persons unknown.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER VII.<br>\nPOIROT PAYS HIS DEBTS</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we came out of the Stylites Arms, Poirot drew me aside by a gentle pressure of the arm. I understood his object. He was waiting for the Scotland Yard men.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In a few moments, they emerged, and Poirot at once stepped forward, and accosted the shorter of the two.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I fear you do not remember me, Inspector Japp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, if it isn’t Mr. Poirot!” cried the Inspector. He turned to the other man. “You’ve heard me speak of Mr. Poirot? It was in 1904 he and I worked together—the Abercrombie forgery case—you remember, he was run down in Brussels. Ah, those were great days, moosier. Then, do you remember ‘Baron’ Altara? There was a pretty rogue for you! He eluded the clutches of half the police in Europe. But we nailed him in Antwerp—thanks to Mr. Poirot here.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As these friendly reminiscences were being indulged in, I drew nearer, and was introduced to Detective-Inspector Japp, who, in his turn, introduced us both to his companion, Superintendent Summerhaye.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I need hardly ask what you are doing here, gentlemen,” remarked Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Japp closed one eye knowingly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, indeed. Pretty clear case I should say.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Poirot answered gravely:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There I differ from you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, come!” said Summerhaye, opening his lips for the first time. “Surely the whole thing is clear as daylight. The man’s caught red-handed. How he could be such a fool beats me!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Japp was looking attentively at Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hold your fire, Summerhaye,” he remarked jocularly. “Me and Moosier here have met before—and there’s no man’s judgment I’d sooner take than his. If I’m not greatly mistaken, he’s got something up his sleeve. Isn’t that so, moosier?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have drawn certain conclusions—yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Summerhaye was still looking rather sceptical, but Japp continued his scrutiny of Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s this way,” he said, “so far, we’ve only seen the case from the outside. That’s where the Yard’s at a disadvantage in a case of this kind, where the murder’s only out, so to speak, after the inquest. A lot depends on being on the spot first thing, and that’s where Mr. Poirot’s had the start of us. We shouldn’t have been here as soon as this even, if it hadn’t been for the fact that there was a smart doctor on the spot, who gave us the tip through the Coroner. But you’ve been on the spot from the first, and you may have picked up some little hints. From the evidence at the inquest, Mr. Inglethorp murdered his wife as sure as I stand here, and if anyone but you hinted the contrary I’d laugh in his face. I must say I was surprised the jury didn’t bring it in Wilful Murder against him right off. I think they would have, if it hadn’t been for the Coroner—he seemed to be holding them back.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps, though, you have a warrant for his arrest in your pocket now,” suggested Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A kind of wooden shutter of officialdom came down from Japp’s expressive countenance.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps I have, and perhaps I haven’t,” he remarked dryly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked at him thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am very anxious, Messieurs, that he should not be arrested.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I dare say,” observed Summerhaye sarcastically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Japp was regarding Poirot with comical perplexity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can’t you go a little further, Mr. Poirot? A wink’s as good as a nod—from you. You’ve been on the spot—and the Yard doesn’t want to make any mistakes, you know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is exactly what I thought. Well, I will tell you this. Use your warrant: Arrest Mr. Inglethorp. But it will bring you no kudos—the case against him will be dismissed at once! <i>Comme ça!</i>” And he snapped his fingers expressively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Japp’s face grew grave, though Summerhaye gave an incredulous snort.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As for me, I was literally dumb with astonishment. I could only conclude that Poirot was mad.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Japp had taken out a handkerchief, and was gently dabbing his brow.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I daren’t do it, Mr. Poirot. <i>I</i>’d take your word, but there’s others over me who’ll be asking what the devil I mean by it. Can’t you give me a little more to go on?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot reflected a moment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It can be done,” he said at last. “I admit I do not wish it. It forces my hand. I would have preferred to work in the dark just for the present, but what you say is very just—the word of a Belgian policeman, whose day is past, is not enough! And Alfred Inglethorp must not be arrested. That I have sworn, as my friend Hastings here knows. See, then, my good Japp, you go at once to Styles?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, in about half an hour. We’re seeing the Coroner and the doctor first.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good. Call for me in passing—the last house in the village. I will go with you. At Styles, Mr. Inglethorp will give you, or if he refuses—as is probable—I will give you such proofs that shall satisfy you that the case against him could not possibly be sustained. Is that a bargain?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That’s a bargain,” said Japp heartily. “And, on behalf of the Yard, I’m much obliged to you, though I’m bound to confess I can’t at present see the faintest possible loop-hole in the evidence, but you always were a marvel! So long, then, moosier.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The two detectives strode away, Summerhaye with an incredulous grin on his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, my friend,” cried Poirot, before I could get in a word, “what do you think? <i>Mon Dieu!</i> I had some warm moments in that court; I did not figure to myself that the man would be so pig-headed as to refuse to say anything at all. Decidedly, it was the policy of an imbecile.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“H’m! There are other explanations besides that of imbecility,” I remarked. “For, if the case against him is true, how could he defend himself except by silence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, in a thousand ingenious ways,” cried Poirot. “See; say that it is I who have committed this murder, I can think of seven most plausible stories! Far more convincing than Mr. Inglethorp’s stony denials!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could not help laughing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Poirot, I am sure you are capable of thinking of seventy! But, seriously, in spite of what I heard you say to the detectives, you surely cannot still believe in the possibility of Alfred Inglethorp’s innocence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why not now as much as before? Nothing has changed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But the evidence is so conclusive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, too conclusive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We turned in at the gate of Leastways Cottage, and proceeded up the now familiar stairs.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, yes, too conclusive,” continued Poirot, almost to himself. “Real evidence is usually vague and unsatisfactory. It has to be examined—sifted. But here the whole thing is cut and dried. No, my friend, this evidence has been very cleverly manufactured—so cleverly that it has defeated its own ends.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you make that out?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because, so long as the evidence against him was vague and intangible, it was very hard to disprove. But, in his anxiety, the criminal has drawn the net so closely that one cut will set Inglethorp free.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was silent. And in a minute or two, Poirot continued:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let us look at the matter like this. Here is a man, let us say, who sets out to poison his wife. He has lived by his wits as the saying goes. Presumably, therefore, he has some wits. He is not altogether a fool. Well, how does he set about it? He goes boldly to the village chemist’s and purchases strychnine under his own name, with a trumped up story about a dog which is bound to be proved absurd. He does not employ the poison that night. No, he waits until he has had a violent quarrel with her, of which the whole household is cognisant, and which naturally directs their suspicions upon him. He prepares no defence—no shadow of an alibi, yet he knows the chemist’s assistant must necessarily come forward with the facts. Bah! Do not ask me to believe that any man could be so idiotic! Only a lunatic, who wished to commit suicide by causing himself to be hanged, would act so!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still—I do not see——” I began.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Neither do I see. I tell you, <i>mon ami</i>, it puzzles me. <i>Me</i>—Hercule Poirot!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But if you believe him innocent, how do you explain his buying the strychnine?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very simply. He did <i>not</i> buy it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But Mace recognized him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I beg your pardon, he saw a man with a black beard like Mr. Inglethorp’s, and wearing glasses like Mr. Inglethorp, and dressed in Mr. Inglethorp’s rather noticeable clothes. He could not recognize a man whom he had probably only seen in the distance, since, you remember, he himself had only been in the village a fortnight, and Mrs. Inglethorp dealt principally with Coot’s in Tadminster.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you think——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mon ami</i>, do you remember the two points I laid stress upon? Leave the first one for the moment, what was the second?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The important fact that Alfred Inglethorp wears peculiar clothes, has a black beard, and uses glasses,” I quoted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. Now suppose anyone wished to pass himself off as John or Lawrence Cavendish. Would it be easy?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I said thoughtfully. “Of course an actor——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Poirot cut me short ruthlessly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And why would it not be easy? I will tell you, my friend: Because they are both clean-shaven men. To make up successfully as one of these two in broad daylight, it would need an actor of genius, and a certain initial facial resemblance. But in the case of Alfred Inglethorp, all that is changed. His clothes, his beard, the glasses which hide his eyes—those are the salient points about his personal appearance. Now, what is the first instinct of the criminal? To divert suspicion from himself, is it not so? And how can he best do that? By throwing it on someone else. In this instance, there was a man ready to his hand. Everybody was predisposed to believe in Mr. Inglethorp’s guilt. It was a foregone conclusion that he would be suspected; but, to make it a sure thing there must be tangible proof—such as the actual buying of the poison, and that, with a man of the peculiar appearance of Mr. Inglethorp, was not difficult. Remember, this young Mace had never actually spoken to Mr. Inglethorp. How should he doubt that the man in his clothes, with his beard and his glasses, was not Alfred Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It may be so,” I said, fascinated by Poirot’s eloquence. “But, if that was the case, why does he not say where he was at six o’clock on Monday evening?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, why indeed?” said Poirot, calming down. “If he were arrested, he probably would speak, but I do not want it to come to that. I must make him see the gravity of his position. There is, of course, something discreditable behind his silence. If he did not murder his wife, he is, nevertheless, a scoundrel, and has something of his own to conceal, quite apart from the murder.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What can it be?” I mused, won over to Poirot’s views for the moment, although still retaining a faint conviction that the obvious deduction was the correct one.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can you not guess?” asked Poirot, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, can you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, I had a little idea sometime ago—and it has turned out to be correct.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You never told me,” I said reproachfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot spread out his hands apologetically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pardon me, <i>mon ami</i>, you were not precisely <i>sympathique</i>.” He turned to me earnestly. “Tell me—you see now that he must not be arrested?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps,” I said doubtfully, for I was really quite indifferent to the fate of Alfred Inglethorp, and thought that a good fright would do him no harm.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot, who was watching me intently, gave a sigh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come, my friend,” he said, changing the subject, “apart from Mr. Inglethorp, how did the evidence at the inquest strike you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, pretty much what I expected.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did nothing strike you as peculiar about it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My thoughts flew to Mary Cavendish, and I hedged:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In what way?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Mr. Lawrence Cavendish’s evidence for instance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was relieved.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, Lawrence! No, I don’t think so. He’s always a nervous chap.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His suggestion that his mother might have been poisoned accidentally by means of the tonic she was taking, that did not strike you as strange— <i>hein?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I can’t say it did. The doctors ridiculed it of course. But it was quite a natural suggestion for a layman to make.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But Monsieur Lawrence is not a layman. You told me yourself that he had started by studying medicine, and that he had taken his degree.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that’s true. I never thought of that.” I was rather startled. “It <i>is</i> odd.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From the first, his behaviour has been peculiar. Of all the household, he alone would be likely to recognize the symptoms of strychnine poisoning, and yet we find him the only member of the family to uphold strenuously the theory of death from natural causes. If it had been Monsieur John, I could have understood it. He has no technical knowledge, and is by nature unimaginative. But Monsieur Lawrence—no! And now, to-day, he puts forward a suggestion that he himself must have known was ridiculous. There is food for thought in this, <i>mon ami!</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s very confusing,” I agreed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then there is Mrs. Cavendish,” continued Poirot. “That’s another who is not telling all she knows! What do you make of her attitude?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t know what to make of it. It seems inconceivable that she should be shielding Alfred Inglethorp. Yet that is what it looks like.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded reflectively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it is queer. One thing is certain, she overheard a good deal more of that ‘private conversation’ than she was willing to admit.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet she is the last person one would accuse of stooping to eavesdrop!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. One thing her evidence <i>has</i> shown me. I made a mistake. Dorcas was quite right. The quarrel did take place earlier in the afternoon, about four o’clock, as she said.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked at him curiously. I had never understood his insistence on that point.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, a good deal that was peculiar came out to-day,” continued Poirot. “Dr. Bauerstein, now, what was <i>he</i> doing up and dressed at that hour in the morning? It is astonishing to me that no one commented on the fact.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He has insomnia, I believe,” I said doubtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which is a very good, or a very bad explanation,” remarked Poirot. “It covers everything, and explains nothing. I shall keep my eye on our clever Dr. Bauerstein.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Any more faults to find with the evidence?” I inquired satirically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mon ami</i>,” replied Poirot gravely, “when you find that people are not telling you the truth—look out! Now, unless I am much mistaken, at the inquest to-day only one—at most, two persons were speaking the truth without reservation or subterfuge.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, come now, Poirot! I won’t cite Lawrence, or Mrs. Cavendish. But there’s John—and Miss Howard, surely they were speaking the truth?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Both of them, my friend? One, I grant you, but both——!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His words gave me an unpleasant shock. Miss Howard’s evidence, unimportant as it was, had been given in such a downright straightforward manner that it had never occurred to me to doubt her sincerity. Still, I had a great respect for Poirot’s sagacity—except on the occasions when he was what I described to myself as “foolishly pig-headed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you really think so?” I asked. “Miss Howard had always seemed to me so essentially honest—almost uncomfortably so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot gave me a curious look, which I could not quite fathom. He seemed to speak, and then checked himself.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Murdoch too,” I continued, “there’s nothing untruthful about <i>her</i>.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. But it was strange that she never heard a sound, sleeping next door; whereas Mrs. Cavendish, in the other wing of the building, distinctly heard the table fall.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, she’s young. And she sleeps soundly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, yes, indeed! She must be a famous sleeper, that one!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not quite like the tone of his voice, but at that moment a smart knock reached our ears, and looking out of the window we perceived the two detectives waiting for us below.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot seized his hat, gave a ferocious twist to his moustache, and, carefully brushing an imaginary speck of dust from his sleeve, motioned me to precede him down the stairs; there we joined the detectives and set out for Styles.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I think the appearance of the two Scotland Yard men was rather a shock—especially to John, though of course after the verdict, he had realized that it was only a matter of time. Still, the presence of the detectives brought the truth home to him more than anything else could have done.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot had conferred with Japp in a low tone on the way up, and it was the latter functionary who requested that the household, with the exception of the servants, should be assembled together in the drawing-room. I realized the significance of this. It was up to Poirot to make his boast good.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Personally, I was not sanguine. Poirot might have excellent reasons for his belief in Inglethorp’s innocence, but a man of the type of Summerhaye would require tangible proofs, and these I doubted if Poirot could supply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Before very long we had all trooped into the drawing-room, the door of which Japp closed. Poirot politely set chairs for everyone. The Scotland Yard men were the cynosure of all eyes. I think that for the first time we realized that the thing was not a bad dream, but a tangible reality. We had read of such things—now we ourselves were actors in the drama. To-morrow the daily papers, all over England, would blazon out the news in staring headlines:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">“MYSTERIOUS TRAGEDY IN ESSEX”<br>\n“WEALTHY LADY POISONED”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There would be pictures of Styles, snap-shots of “The family leaving the Inquest”—the village photographer had not been idle! All the things that one had read a hundred times—things that happen to other people, not to oneself. And now, in this house, a murder had been committed. In front of us were “the detectives in charge of the case.” The well-known glib phraseology passed rapidly through my mind in the interval before Poirot opened the proceedings.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I think everyone was a little surprised that it should be he and not one of the official detectives who took the initiative.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mesdames</i> and <i>messieurs</i>,” said Poirot, bowing as though he were a celebrity about to deliver a lecture, “I have asked you to come here all together, for a certain object. That object, it concerns Mr. Alfred Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inglethorp was sitting a little by himself—I think, unconsciously, everyone had drawn his chair slightly away from him—and he gave a faint start as Poirot pronounced his name.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Inglethorp,” said Poirot, addressing him directly, “a very dark shadow is resting on this house—the shadow of murder.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Inglethorp shook his head sadly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My poor wife,” he murmured. “Poor Emily! It is terrible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not think, monsieur,” said Poirot pointedly, “that you quite realize how terrible it may be—for you.” And as Inglethorp did not appear to understand, he added: “Mr. Inglethorp, you are standing in very grave danger.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The two detectives fidgeted. I saw the official caution “Anything you say will be used in evidence against you,” actually hovering on Summerhaye’s lips. Poirot went on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you understand now, monsieur?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. What do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I mean,” said Poirot deliberately, “that you are suspected of poisoning your wife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A little gasp ran round the circle at this plain speaking.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” cried Inglethorp, starting up. “What a monstrous idea! <i>I</i>—poison my dearest Emily!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not think”—Poirot watched him narrowly—“that you quite realize the unfavourable nature of your evidence at the inquest. Mr. Inglethorp, knowing what I have now told you, do you still refuse to say where you were at six o’clock on Monday afternoon?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a groan, Alfred Inglethorp sank down again and buried his face in his hands. Poirot approached and stood over him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Speak!” he cried menacingly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With an effort, Inglethorp raised his face from his hands. Then, slowly and deliberately, he shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will not speak?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. I do not believe that anyone could be so monstrous as to accuse me of what you say.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded thoughtfully, like a man whose mind is made up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Soit!</i>” he said. “Then I must speak for you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Alfred Inglethorp sprang up again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You? How can you speak? You do not know——” he broke off abruptly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot turned to face us. “<i>Mesdames</i> and <i>messieurs</i>! I speak! Listen! I, Hercule Poirot, affirm that the man who entered the chemist’s shop, and purchased strychnine at six o’clock on Monday last was not Mr. Inglethorp, for at six o’clock on that day Mr. Inglethorp was escorting Mrs. Raikes back to her home from a neighbouring farm. I can produce no less than five witnesses to swear to having seen them together, either at six or just after and, as you may know, the Abbey Farm, Mrs. Raikes’s home, is at least two and a half miles distant from the village. There is absolutely no question as to the alibi!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER VIII.<br>\nFRESH SUSPICIONS</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a moment’s stupefied silence. Japp, who was the least surprised of any of us, was the first to speak.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My word,” he cried, “you’re the goods! And no mistake, Mr. Poirot! These witnesses of yours are all right, I suppose?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Voilà!</i> I have prepared a list of them—names and addresses. You must see them, of course. But you will find it all right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m sure of that.” Japp lowered his voice. “I’m much obliged to you. A pretty mare’s nest arresting him would have been.” He turned to Inglethorp. “But, if you’ll excuse me, sir, why couldn’t you say all this at the inquest?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will tell you why,” interrupted Poirot. “There was a certain rumour——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A most malicious and utterly untrue one,” interrupted Alfred Inglethorp in an agitated voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And Mr. Inglethorp was anxious to have no scandal revived just at present. Am I right?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite right.” Inglethorp nodded. “With my poor Emily not yet buried, can you wonder I was anxious that no more lying rumours should be started.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Between you and me, sir,” remarked Japp, “I’d sooner have any amount of rumours than be arrested for murder. And I venture to think your poor lady would have felt the same. And, if it hadn’t been for Mr. Poirot here, arrested you would have been, as sure as eggs is eggs!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was foolish, no doubt,” murmured Inglethorp. “But you do not know, inspector, how I have been persecuted and maligned.” And he shot a baleful glance at Evelyn Howard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, sir,” said Japp, turning briskly to John, “I should like to see the lady’s bedroom, please, and after that I’ll have a little chat with the servants. Don’t you bother about anything. Mr. Poirot, here, will show me the way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As they all went out of the room, Poirot turned and made me a sign to follow him upstairs. There he caught me by the arm, and drew me aside.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quick, go to the other wing. Stand there—just this side of the baize door. Do not move till I come.” Then, turning rapidly, he rejoined the two detectives.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I followed his instructions, taking up my position by the baize door, and wondering what on earth lay behind the request. Why was I to stand in this particular spot on guard? I looked thoughtfully down the corridor in front of me. An idea struck me. With the exception of Cynthia Murdoch’s, everyone’s room was in this left wing. Had that anything to do with it? Was I to report who came or went? I stood faithfully at my post. The minutes passed. Nobody came. Nothing happened.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It must have been quite twenty minutes before Poirot rejoined me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have not stirred?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I’ve stuck here like a rock. Nothing’s happened.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” Was he pleased, or disappointed? “You’ve seen nothing at all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you have probably heard something? A big bump—eh, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it possible? Ah, but I am vexed with myself! I am not usually clumsy. I made but a slight gesture”—I know Poirot’s gestures—“with the left hand, and over went the table by the bed!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He looked so childishly vexed and crest-fallen that I hastened to console him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind, old chap. What does it matter? Your triumph downstairs excited you. I can tell you, that was a surprise to us all. There must be more in this affair of Inglethorp’s with Mrs. Raikes than we thought, to make him hold his tongue so persistently. What are you going to do now? Where are the Scotland Yard fellows?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Gone down to interview the servants. I showed them all our exhibits. I am disappointed in Japp. He has no method!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hullo!” I said, looking out of the window. “Here’s Dr. Bauerstein. I believe you’re right about that man, Poirot. I don’t like him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is clever,” observed Poirot meditatively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, clever as the devil! I must say I was overjoyed to see him in the plight he was in on Tuesday. You never saw such a spectacle!” And I described the doctor’s adventure. “He looked a regular scarecrow! Plastered with mud from head to foot.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You saw him, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Of course, he didn’t want to come in—it was just after dinner—but Mr. Inglethorp insisted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?” Poirot caught me violently by the shoulders. “Was Dr. Bauerstein here on Tuesday evening? Here? And you never told me? Why did you not tell me? Why? Why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He appeared to be in an absolute frenzy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear Poirot,” I expostulated, “I never thought it would interest you. I didn’t know it was of any importance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Importance? It is of the first importance! So Dr. Bauerstein was here on Tuesday night—the night of the murder. Hastings, do you not see? That alters everything—everything!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had never seen him so upset. Loosening his hold of me, he mechanically straightened a pair of candlesticks, still murmuring to himself: “Yes, that alters everything—everything.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly he seemed to come to a decision.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Allons!</i>” he said. “We must act at once. Where is Mr. Cavendish?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John was in the smoking-room. Poirot went straight to him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Cavendish, I have some important business in Tadminster. A new clue. May I take your motor?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, of course. Do you mean at once?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If you please.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John rang the bell, and ordered round the car. In another ten minutes, we were racing down the park and along the high road to Tadminster.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now, Poirot,” I remarked resignedly, “perhaps you will tell me what all this is about?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, <i>mon ami</i>, a good deal you can guess for yourself. Of course you realize that, now Mr. Inglethorp is out of it, the whole position is greatly changed. We are face to face with an entirely new problem. We know now that there is one person who did not buy the poison. We have cleared away the manufactured clues. Now for the real ones. I have ascertained that anyone in the household, with the exception of Mrs. Cavendish, who was playing tennis with you, could have personated Mr. Inglethorp on Monday evening. In the same way, we have his statement that he put the coffee down in the hall. No one took much notice of that at the inquest—but now it has a very different significance. We must find out who did take that coffee to Mrs. Inglethorp eventually, or who passed through the hall whilst it was standing there. From your account, there are only two people whom we can positively say did not go near the coffee—Mrs. Cavendish, and Mademoiselle Cynthia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that is so.” I felt an inexpressible lightening of the heart. Mary Cavendish could certainly not rest under suspicion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In clearing Alfred Inglethorp,” continued Poirot, “I have been obliged to show my hand sooner than I intended. As long as I might be thought to be pursuing him, the criminal would be off his guard. Now, he will be doubly careful. Yes—doubly careful.” He turned to me abruptly. “Tell me, Hastings, you yourself—have you no suspicions of anybody?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I hesitated. To tell the truth, an idea, wild and extravagant in itself, had once or twice that morning flashed through my brain. I had rejected it as absurd, nevertheless it persisted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You couldn’t call it a suspicion,” I murmured. “It’s so utterly foolish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come now,” urged Poirot encouragingly. “Do not fear. Speak your mind. You should always pay attention to your instincts.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well then,” I blurted out, “it’s absurd—but I suspect Miss Howard of not telling all she knows!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes—you’ll laugh at me——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. Why should I?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I can’t help feeling,” I continued blunderingly; “that we’ve rather left her out of the possible suspects, simply on the strength of her having been away from the place. But, after all, she was only fifteen miles away. A car would do it in half an hour. Can we say positively that she was away from Styles on the night of the murder?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, my friend,” said Poirot unexpectedly, “we can. One of my first actions was to ring up the hospital where she was working.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I learnt that Miss Howard had been on afternoon duty on Tuesday, and that—a convoy coming in unexpectedly—she had kindly offered to remain on night duty, which offer was gratefully accepted. That disposes of that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh!” I said, rather nonplussed. “Really,” I continued, “it’s her extraordinary vehemence against Inglethorp that started me off suspecting her. I can’t help feeling she’d do anything against him. And I had an idea she might know something about the destroying of the will. She might have burnt the new one, mistaking it for the earlier one in his favour. She is so terribly bitter against him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You consider her vehemence unnatural?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Y—es. She is so very violent. I wondered really whether she is quite sane on that point.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head energetically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, you are on a wrong tack there. There is nothing weak-minded or degenerate about Miss Howard. She is an excellent specimen of well-balanced English beef and brawn. She is sanity itself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yet her hatred of Inglethorp seems almost a mania. My idea was—a very ridiculous one, no doubt—that she had intended to poison him—and that, in some way, Mrs. Inglethorp got hold of it by mistake. But I don’t at all see how it could have been done. The whole thing is absurd and ridiculous to the last degree.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still you are right in one thing. It is always wise to suspect everybody until you can prove logically, and to your own satisfaction, that they are innocent. Now, what reasons are there against Miss Howard’s having deliberately poisoned Mrs. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, she was devoted to her!” I exclaimed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tcha! Tcha!” cried Poirot irritably. “You argue like a child. If Miss Howard were capable of poisoning the old lady, she would be quite equally capable of simulating devotion. No, we must look elsewhere. You are perfectly correct in your assumption that her vehemence against Alfred Inglethorp is too violent to be natural; but you are quite wrong in the deduction you draw from it. I have drawn my own deductions, which I believe to be correct, but I will not speak of them at present.” He paused a minute, then went on. “Now, to my way of thinking, there is one insuperable objection to Miss Howard’s being the murderess.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that is?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That in no possible way could Mrs. Inglethorp’s death benefit Miss Howard. Now there is no murder without a motive.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I reflected.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Could not Mrs. Inglethorp have made a will in her favour?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you yourself suggested that possibility to Mr. Wells?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was for a reason. I did not want to mention the name of the person who was actually in my mind. Miss Howard occupied very much the same position, so I used her name instead.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, Mrs. Inglethorp might have done so. Why, that will, made on the afternoon of her death may——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Poirot’s shake of the head was so energetic that I stopped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, my friend. I have certain little ideas of my own about that will. But I can tell you this much—it was not in Miss Howard’s favour.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I accepted his assurance, though I did not really see how he could be so positive about the matter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” I said, with a sigh, “we will acquit Miss Howard, then. It is partly your fault that I ever came to suspect her. It was what you said about her evidence at the inquest that set me off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked puzzled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What did I say about her evidence at the inquest?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t you remember? When I cited her and John Cavendish as being above suspicion?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh—ah—yes.” He seemed a little confused, but recovered himself. “By the way, Hastings, there is something I want you to do for me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly. What is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Next time you happen to be alone with Lawrence Cavendish, I want you to say this to him. ‘I have a message for you, from Poirot. He says: “Find the extra coffee-cup, and you can rest in peace!”’ Nothing more. Nothing less.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Find the extra coffee-cup, and you can rest in peace.’ Is that right?” I asked, much mystified.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Excellent.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what does it mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, that I will leave you to find out. You have access to the facts. Just say that to him, and see what he says.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Very well—but it’s all extremely mysterious.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We were running into Tadminster now, and Poirot directed the car to the “Analytical Chemist.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot hopped down briskly, and went inside. In a few minutes he was back again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There,” he said. “That is all my business.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What were you doing there?” I asked, in lively curiosity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I left something to be analysed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The sample of cocoa I took from the saucepan in the bedroom.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But that has already been tested!” I cried, stupefied. “Dr. Bauerstein had it tested, and you yourself laughed at the possibility of there being strychnine in it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know Dr. Bauerstein had it tested,” replied Poirot quietly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I have a fancy for having it analysed again, that is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And not another word on the subject could I drag out of him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This proceeding of Poirot’s, in respect of the cocoa, puzzled me intensely. I could see neither rhyme nor reason in it. However, my confidence in him, which at one time had rather waned, was fully restored since his belief in Alfred Inglethorp’s innocence had been so triumphantly vindicated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The funeral of Mrs. Inglethorp took place the following day, and on Monday, as I came down to a late breakfast, John drew me aside, and informed me that Mr. Inglethorp was leaving that morning, to take up his quarters at the Stylites Arms until he should have completed his plans.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And really it’s a great relief to think he’s going, Hastings,” continued my honest friend. “It was bad enough before, when we thought he’d done it, but I’m hanged if it isn’t worse now, when we all feel guilty for having been so down on the fellow. The fact is, we’ve treated him abominably. Of course, things did look black against him. I don’t see how anyone could blame us for jumping to the conclusions we did. Still, there it is, we were in the wrong, and now there’s a beastly feeling that one ought to make amends; which is difficult, when one doesn’t like the fellow a bit better than one did before. The whole thing’s damned awkward! And I’m thankful he’s had the tact to take himself off. It’s a good thing Styles wasn’t the mater’s to leave to him. Couldn’t bear to think of the fellow lording it here. He’s welcome to her money.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’ll be able to keep up the place all right?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes. There are the death duties, of course, but half my father’s money goes with the place, and Lawrence will stay with us for the present, so there is his share as well. We shall be pinched at first, of course, because, as I once told you, I am in a bit of a hole financially myself. Still, the Johnnies will wait now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In the general relief at Inglethorp’s approaching departure, we had the most genial breakfast we had experienced since the tragedy. Cynthia, whose young spirits were naturally buoyant, was looking quite her pretty self again, and we all, with the exception of Lawrence, who seemed unalterably gloomy and nervous, were quietly cheerful, at the opening of a new and hopeful future.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The papers, of course, had been full of the tragedy. Glaring headlines, sandwiched biographies of every member of the household, subtle innuendoes, the usual familiar tag about the police having a clue. Nothing was spared us. It was a slack time. The war was momentarily inactive, and the newspapers seized with avidity on this crime in fashionable life: “The Mysterious Affair at Styles” was the topic of the moment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Naturally it was very annoying for the Cavendishes. The house was constantly besieged by reporters, who were consistently denied admission, but who continued to haunt the village and the grounds, where they lay in wait with cameras, for any unwary members of the household. We all lived in a blast of publicity. The Scotland Yard men came and went, examining, questioning, lynx-eyed and reserved of tongue. Towards what end they were working, we did not know. Had they any clue, or would the whole thing remain in the category of undiscovered crimes?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After breakfast, Dorcas came up to me rather mysteriously, and asked if she might have a few words with me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly. What is it, Dorcas?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it’s just this, sir. You’ll be seeing the Belgian gentleman to-day perhaps?” I nodded. “Well, sir, you know how he asked me so particular if the mistress, or anyone else, had a green dress?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, yes. You have found one?” My interest was aroused.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, not that, sir. But since then I’ve remembered what the young gentlemen”—John and Lawrence were still the “young gentlemen” to Dorcas—“call the ‘dressing-up box.’ It’s up in the front attic, sir. A great chest, full of old clothes and fancy dresses, and what not. And it came to me sudden like that there might be a green dress amongst them. So, if you’d tell the Belgian gentleman——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will tell him, Dorcas,” I promised.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you very much, sir. A very nice gentleman he is, sir. And quite a different class from them two detectives from London, what goes prying about, and asking questions. I don’t hold with foreigners as a rule, but from what the newspapers say I make out as how these brave Belges isn’t the ordinary run of foreigners, and certainly he’s a most polite spoken gentleman.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dear old Dorcas! As she stood there, with her honest face upturned to mine, I thought what a fine specimen she was of the old-fashioned servant that is so fast dying out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I thought I might as well go down to the village at once, and look up Poirot; but I met him half-way, coming up to the house, and at once gave him Dorcas’s message.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, the brave Dorcas! We will look at the chest, although—but no matter—we will examine it all the same.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We entered the house by one of the windows. There was no one in the hall, and we went straight up to the attic.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sure enough, there was the chest, a fine old piece, all studded with brass nails, and full to overflowing with every imaginable type of garment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot bundled everything out on the floor with scant ceremony. There were one or two green fabrics of varying shades; but Poirot shook his head over them all. He seemed somewhat apathetic in the search, as though he expected no great results from it. Suddenly he gave an exclamation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The chest was nearly empty, and there, reposing right at the bottom, was a magnificent black beard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Ohó!</i>” said Poirot. “<i>Ohó!</i>” He turned it over in his hands, examining it closely. “New,” he remarked. “Yes, quite new.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After a moment’s hesitation, he replaced it in the chest, heaped all the other things on top of it as before, and made his way briskly downstairs. He went straight to the pantry, where we found Dorcas busily polishing her silver.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot wished her good morning with Gallic politeness, and went on:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We have been looking through that chest, Dorcas. I am much obliged to you for mentioning it. There is, indeed, a fine collection there. Are they often used, may I ask?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, sir, not very often nowadays, though from time to time we do have what the young gentlemen call ‘a dress-up night.’ And very funny it is sometimes, sir. Mr. Lawrence, he’s wonderful. Most comic! I shall never forget the night he came down as the Char of Persia, I think he called it—a sort of Eastern King it was. He had the big paper knife in his hand, and ‘Mind, Dorcas,’ he says, ‘you’ll have to be very respectful. This is my specially sharpened scimitar, and it’s off with your head if I’m at all displeased with you!’ Miss Cynthia, she was what they call an Apache, or some such name—a Frenchified sort of cut-throat, I take it to be. A real sight she looked. You’d never have believed a pretty young lady like that could have made herself into such a ruffian. Nobody would have known her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“These evenings must have been great fun,” said Poirot genially. “I suppose Mr. Lawrence wore that fine black beard in the chest upstairs, when he was Shah of Persia?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He did have a beard, sir,” replied Dorcas, smiling. “And well I know it, for he borrowed two skeins of my black wool to make it with! And I’m sure it looked wonderfully natural at a distance. I didn’t know as there was a beard up there at all. It must have been got quite lately, I think. There was a red wig, I know, but nothing else in the way of hair. Burnt corks they use mostly—though ‘tis messy getting it off again. Miss Cynthia was a nigger once, and, oh, the trouble she had.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So Dorcas knows nothing about that black beard,” said Poirot thoughtfully, as we walked out into the hall again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you think it is <i>the</i> one?” I whispered eagerly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do. You notice it had been trimmed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. It was cut exactly the shape of Mr. Inglethorp’s, and I found one or two snipped hairs. Hastings, this affair is very deep.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who put it in the chest, I wonder?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Someone with a good deal of intelligence,” remarked Poirot dryly. “You realize that he chose the one place in the house to hide it where its presence would not be remarked? Yes, he is intelligent. But we must be more intelligent. We must be so intelligent that he does not suspect us of being intelligent at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I acquiesced.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There, <i>mon ami</i>, you will be of great assistance to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was pleased with the compliment. There had been times when I hardly thought that Poirot appreciated me at my true worth.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” he continued, staring at me thoughtfully, “you will be invaluable.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This was naturally gratifying, but Poirot’s next words were not so welcome.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must have an ally in the house,” he observed reflectively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have me,” I protested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“True, but you are not sufficient.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was hurt, and showed it. Poirot hurried to explain himself.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not quite take my meaning. You are known to be working with me. I want somebody who is not associated with us in any way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, I see. How about John?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I think not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The dear fellow isn’t perhaps very bright,” I said thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here comes Miss Howard,” said Poirot suddenly. “She is the very person. But I am in her black books, since I cleared Mr. Inglethorp. Still, we can but try.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a nod that was barely civil, Miss Howard assented to Poirot’s request for a few minutes’ conversation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We went into the little morning-room, and Poirot closed the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, Monsieur Poirot,” said Miss Howard impatiently, “what is it? Out with it. I’m busy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you remember, mademoiselle, that I once asked you to help me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I do.” The lady nodded. “And I told you I’d help you with pleasure—to hang Alfred Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” Poirot studied her seriously. “Miss Howard, I will ask you one question. I beg of you to reply to it truthfully.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never tell lies,” replied Miss Howard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is this. Do you still believe that Mrs. Inglethorp was poisoned by her husband?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?” she asked sharply. “You needn’t think your pretty explanations influence me in the slightest. I’ll admit that it wasn’t he who bought strychnine at the chemist’s shop. What of that? I dare say he soaked fly paper, as I told you at the beginning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is arsenic—not strychnine,” said Poirot mildly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What does that matter? Arsenic would put poor Emily out of the way just as well as strychnine. If I’m convinced he did it, it doesn’t matter a jot to me <i>how</i> he did it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. <i>If</i> you are convinced he did it,” said Poirot quietly. “I will put my question in another form. Did you ever in your heart of hearts believe that Mrs. Inglethorp was poisoned by her husband?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” cried Miss Howard. “Haven’t I always told you the man is a villain? Haven’t I always told you he would murder her in her bed? Haven’t I always hated him like poison?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly,” said Poirot. “That bears out my little idea entirely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What little idea?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard, do you remember a conversation that took place on the day of my friend’s arrival here? He repeated it to me, and there is a sentence of yours that has impressed me very much. Do you remember affirming that if a crime had been committed, and anyone you loved had been murdered, you felt certain that you would know by instinct who the criminal was, even if you were quite unable to prove it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I remember saying that. I believe it too. I suppose you think it nonsense?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet you will pay no attention to my instinct against Alfred Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” said Poirot curtly. “Because your instinct is not against Mr. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. You wish to believe he committed the crime. You believe him capable of committing it. But your instinct tells you he did not commit it. It tells you more—shall I go on?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She was staring at him, fascinated, and made a slight affirmative movement of the hand.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Shall I tell you why you have been so vehement against Mr. Inglethorp? It is because you have been trying to believe what you wish to believe. It is because you are trying to drown and stifle your instinct, which tells you another name——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, no!” cried Miss Howard wildly, flinging up her hands. “Don’t say it! Oh, don’t say it! It isn’t true! It can’t be true. I don’t know what put such a wild—such a dreadful—idea into my head!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am right, am I not?” asked Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, yes; you must be a wizard to have guessed. But it can’t be so—it’s too monstrous, too impossible. It <i>must</i> be Alfred Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t ask me about it,” continued Miss Howard, “because I shan’t tell you. I won’t admit it, even to myself. I must be mad to think of such a thing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded, as if satisfied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will ask you nothing. It is enough for me that it is as I thought. And I—I, too, have an instinct. We are working together towards a common end.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t ask me to help you, because I won’t. I wouldn’t lift a finger to—to——” She faltered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will help me in spite of yourself. I ask you nothing—but you will be my ally. You will not be able to help yourself. You will do the only thing that I want of you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that is?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will watch!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Evelyn Howard bowed her head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I can’t help doing that. I am always watching—always hoping I shall be proved wrong.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If we are wrong, well and good,” said Poirot. “No one will be more pleased than I shall. But, if we are right? If we are right, Miss Howard, on whose side are you then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t know, I don’t know——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come now.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It could be hushed up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There must be no hushing up.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But Emily herself——” She broke off.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard,” said Poirot gravely, “this is unworthy of you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly she took her face from her hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” she said quietly, “that was not Evelyn Howard who spoke!” She flung her head up proudly. “<i>This</i> is Evelyn Howard! And she is on the side of Justice! Let the cost be what it may.” And with these words, she walked firmly out of the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There,” said Poirot, looking after her, “goes a very valuable ally. That woman, Hastings, has got brains as well as a heart.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not reply.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Instinct is a marvellous thing,” mused Poirot. “It can neither be explained nor ignored.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You and Miss Howard seem to know what you are talking about,” I observed coldly. “Perhaps you don’t realize that <i>I</i> am still in the dark.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really? Is that so, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Enlighten me, will you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot studied me attentively for a moment or two. Then, to my intense surprise, he shook his head decidedly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, my friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, look here, why not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Two is enough for a secret.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, I think it is very unfair to keep back facts from me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am not keeping back facts. Every fact that I know is in your possession. You can draw your own deductions from them. This time it is a question of ideas.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, it would be interesting to know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked at me very earnestly, and again shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You see,” he said sadly, “<i>you</i> have no instincts.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was intelligence you were requiring just now,” I pointed out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The two often go together,” said Poirot enigmatically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The remark seemed so utterly irrelevant that I did not even take the trouble to answer it. But I decided that if I made any interesting and important discoveries—as no doubt I should—I would keep them to myself, and surprise Poirot with the ultimate result.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There are times when it is one’s duty to assert oneself.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER IX.<br>\nDR. BAUERSTEIN</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had had no opportunity as yet of passing on Poirot’s message to Lawrence. But now, as I strolled out on the lawn, still nursing a grudge against my friend’s high-handedness, I saw Lawrence on the croquet lawn, aimlessly knocking a couple of very ancient balls about, with a still more ancient mallet.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It struck me that it would be a good opportunity to deliver my message. Otherwise, Poirot himself might relieve me of it. It was true that I did not quite gather its purport, but I flattered myself that by Lawrence’s reply, and perhaps a little skillful cross-examination on my part, I should soon perceive its significance. Accordingly I accosted him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’ve been looking for you,” I remarked untruthfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. The truth is, I’ve got a message for you—from Poirot.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He told me to wait until I was alone with you,” I said, dropping my voice significantly, and watching him intently out of the corner of my eye. I have always been rather good at what is called, I believe, creating an atmosphere.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was no change of expression in the dark melancholic face. Had he any idea of what I was about to say?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“This is the message.” I dropped my voice still lower. “‘Find the extra coffee-cup, and you can rest in peace.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What on earth does he mean?” Lawrence stared at me in quite unaffected astonishment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t you know?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not in the least. Do you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was compelled to shake my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What extra coffee-cup?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t know.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’d better ask Dorcas, or one of the maids, if he wants to know about coffee-cups. It’s their business, not mine. I don’t know anything about the coffee-cups, except that we’ve got some that are never used, which are a perfect dream! Old Worcester. You’re not a connoisseur, are you, Hastings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You miss a lot. A really perfect bit of old china—it’s pure delight to handle it, or even to look at it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, what am I to tell Poirot?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tell him I don’t know what he’s talking about. It’s double Dutch to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was moving off towards the house again when he suddenly called me back.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I say, what was the end of that message? Say it over again, will you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘Find the extra coffee-cup, and you can rest in peace.’ Are you sure you don’t know what it means?” I asked him earnestly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” he said musingly, “I don’t. I—I wish I did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The boom of the gong sounded from the house, and we went in together. Poirot had been asked by John to remain to lunch, and was already seated at the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>By tacit consent, all mention of the tragedy was barred. We conversed on the war, and other outside topics. But after the cheese and biscuits had been handed round, and Dorcas had left the room, Poirot suddenly leant forward to Mrs. Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pardon me, madame, for recalling unpleasant memories, but I have a little idea”—Poirot’s “little ideas” were becoming a perfect byword—“and would like to ask one or two questions.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of me? Certainly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are too amiable, madame. What I want to ask is this: the door leading into Mrs. Inglethorp’s room from that of Mademoiselle Cynthia, it was bolted, you say?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly it was bolted,” replied Mary Cavendish, rather surprised. “I said so at the inquest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Bolted?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.” She looked perplexed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I mean,” explained Poirot, “you are sure it was bolted, and not merely locked?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, I see what you mean. No, I don’t know. I said bolted, meaning that it was fastened, and I could not open it, but I believe all the doors were found bolted on the inside.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, as far as you are concerned, the door might equally well have been locked?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You yourself did not happen to notice, madame, when you entered Mrs. Inglethorp’s room, whether that door was bolted or not?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I believe it was.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you did not see it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. I—never looked.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But <i>I</i> did,” interrupted Lawrence suddenly. “I happened to notice that it <i>was</i> bolted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, that settles it.” And Poirot looked crestfallen.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could not help rejoicing that, for once, one of his “little ideas” had come to naught.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After lunch Poirot begged me to accompany him home. I consented rather stiffly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are annoyed, is it not so?” he asked anxiously, as we walked through the park.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all,” I said coldly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is well. That lifts a great load from my mind.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This was not quite what I had intended. I had hoped that he would have observed the stiffness of my manner. Still, the fervour of his words went towards the appeasing of my just displeasure. I thawed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I gave Lawrence your message,” I said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what did he say? He was entirely puzzled?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I am quite sure he had no idea of what you meant.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had expected Poirot to be disappointed; but, to my surprise, he replied that that was as he had thought, and that he was very glad. My pride forbade me to ask any questions.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot switched off on another tack.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mademoiselle Cynthia was not at lunch to-day? How was that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She is at the hospital again. She resumed work to-day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, she is an industrious little demoiselle. And pretty too. She is like pictures I have seen in Italy. I would rather like to see that dispensary of hers. Do you think she would show it to me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sure she would be delighted. It’s an interesting little place.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Does she go there every day?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She has all Wednesdays off, and comes back to lunch on Saturdays. Those are her only times off.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will remember. Women are doing great work nowadays, and Mademoiselle Cynthia is clever—oh, yes, she has brains, that little one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I believe she has passed quite a stiff exam.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Without doubt. After all, it is very responsible work. I suppose they have very strong poisons there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, she showed them to us. They are kept locked up in a little cupboard. I believe they have to be very careful. They always take out the key before leaving the room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Indeed. It is near the window, this cupboard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, right the other side of the room. Why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I wondered. That is all. Will you come in?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had reached the cottage.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. I think I’ll be getting back. I shall go round the long way through the woods.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The woods round Styles were very beautiful. After the walk across the open park, it was pleasant to saunter lazily through the cool glades. There was hardly a breath of wind, the very chirp of the birds was faint and subdued. I strolled on a little way, and finally flung myself down at the foot of a grand old beech-tree. My thoughts of mankind were kindly and charitable. I even forgave Poirot for his absurd secrecy. In fact, I was at peace with the world. Then I yawned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I thought about the crime, and it struck me as being very unreal and far off.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I yawned again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Probably, I thought, it really never happened. Of course, it was all a bad dream. The truth of the matter was that it was Lawrence who had murdered Alfred Inglethorp with a croquet mallet. But it was absurd of John to make such a fuss about it, and to go shouting out: “I tell you I won’t have it!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I woke up with a start.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At once I realized that I was in a very awkward predicament. For, about twelve feet away from me, John and Mary Cavendish were standing facing each other, and they were evidently quarrelling. And, quite as evidently, they were unaware of my vicinity, for before I could move or speak John repeated the words which had aroused me from my dream.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I tell you, Mary, I won’t have it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary’s voice came, cool and liquid:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have <i>you</i> any right to criticize my actions?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It will be the talk of the village! My mother was only buried on Saturday, and here you are gadding about with the fellow.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh,” she shrugged her shoulders, “if it is only village gossip that you mind!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it isn’t. I’ve had enough of the fellow hanging about. He’s a Polish Jew, anyway.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A tinge of Jewish blood is not a bad thing. It leavens the”—she looked at him—“stolid stupidity of the ordinary Englishman.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Fire in her eyes, ice in her voice. I did not wonder that the blood rose to John’s face in a crimson tide.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mary!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?” Her tone did not change.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The pleading died out of his voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Am I to understand that you will continue to see Bauerstein against my express wishes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If I choose.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You defy me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but I deny your right to criticize my actions. Have <i>you</i> no friends of whom I should disapprove?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John fell back a pace. The colour ebbed slowly from his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?” he said, in an unsteady voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You see!” said Mary quietly. “You <i>do</i> see, don’t you, that <i>you</i> have no right to dictate to <i>me</i> as to the choice of my friends?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John glanced at her pleadingly, a stricken look on his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No right? Have I <i>no</i> right, Mary?” he said unsteadily. He stretched out his hands. “Mary——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>For a moment, I thought she wavered. A softer expression came over her face, then suddenly she turned almost fiercely away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“None!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She was walking away when John sprang after her, and caught her by the arm.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mary”—his voice was very quiet now—“are you in love with this fellow Bauerstein?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She hesitated, and suddenly there swept across her face a strange expression, old as the hills, yet with something eternally young about it. So might some Egyptian sphinx have smiled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She freed herself quietly from his arm, and spoke over her shoulder.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps,” she said; and then swiftly passed out of the little glade, leaving John standing there as though he had been turned to stone.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Rather ostentatiously, I stepped forward, crackling some dead branches with my feet as I did so. John turned. Luckily, he took it for granted that I had only just come upon the scene.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hullo, Hastings. Have you seen the little fellow safely back to his cottage? Quaint little chap! Is he any good, though, really?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He was considered one of the finest detectives of his day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, well, I suppose there must be something in it, then. What a rotten world it is, though!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You find it so?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good Lord, yes! There’s this terrible business to start with. Scotland Yard men in and out of the house like a jack-in-the-box! Never know where they won’t turn up next. Screaming headlines in every paper in the country—damn all journalists, I say! Do you know there was a whole crowd staring in at the lodge gates this morning. Sort of Madame Tussaud’s chamber of horrors business that can be seen for nothing. Pretty thick, isn’t it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Cheer up, John!” I said soothingly. “It can’t last for ever.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can’t it, though? It can last long enough for us never to be able to hold up our heads again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, you’re getting morbid on the subject.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Enough to make a man morbid, to be stalked by beastly journalists and stared at by gaping moon-faced idiots, wherever he goes! But there’s worse than that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John lowered his voice:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you ever thought, Hastings—it’s a nightmare to me—who did it? I can’t help feeling sometimes it must have been an accident. Because—because—who could have done it? Now Inglethorp’s out of the way, there’s no one else; no one, I mean, except—one of us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Yes, indeed, that was nightmare enough for any man! One of us? Yes, surely it must be so, unless——-</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A new idea suggested itself to my mind. Rapidly, I considered it. The light increased. Poirot’s mysterious doings, his hints—they all fitted in. Fool that I was not to have thought of this possibility before, and what a relief for us all.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, John,” I said, “it isn’t one of us. How could it be?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know, but, still, who else is there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Can’t you guess?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked cautiously round, and lowered my voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dr. Bauerstein!” I whispered.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Impossible!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But what earthly interest could he have in my mother’s death?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That I don’t see,” I confessed, “but I’ll tell you this: Poirot thinks so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot? Does he? How do you know?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I told him of Poirot’s intense excitement on hearing that Dr. Bauerstein had been at Styles on the fatal night, and added:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He said twice: ‘That alters everything.’ And I’ve been thinking. You know Inglethorp said he had put down the coffee in the hall? Well, it was just then that Bauerstein arrived. Isn’t it possible that, as Inglethorp brought him through the hall, the doctor dropped something into the coffee in passing?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“H’m,” said John. “It would have been very risky.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but it was possible.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And then, how could he know it was her coffee? No, old fellow, I don’t think that will wash.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But I had remembered something else.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You’re quite right. That wasn’t how it was done. Listen.” And I then told him of the cocoa sample which Poirot had taken to be analysed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John interrupted just as I had done.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But, look here, Bauerstein had had it analysed already?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, yes, that’s the point. I didn’t see it either until now. Don’t you understand? Bauerstein had it analysed—that’s just it! If Bauerstein’s the murderer, nothing could be simpler than for him to substitute some ordinary cocoa for his sample, and send that to be tested. And of course they would find no strychnine! But no one would dream of suspecting Bauerstein, or think of taking another sample—except Poirot,” I added, with belated recognition.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but what about the bitter taste that cocoa won’t disguise?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, we’ve only his word for that. And there are other possibilities. He’s admittedly one of the world’s greatest toxicologists——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One of the world’s greatest what? Say it again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He knows more about poisons than almost anybody,” I explained. “Well, my idea is, that perhaps he’s found some way of making strychnine tasteless. Or it may not have been strychnine at all, but some obscure drug no one has ever heard of, which produces much the same symptoms.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“H’m, yes, that might be,” said John. “But look here, how could he have got at the cocoa? That wasn’t downstairs?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, it wasn’t,” I admitted reluctantly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And then, suddenly, a dreadful possibility flashed through my mind. I hoped and prayed it would not occur to John also. I glanced sideways at him. He was frowning perplexedly, and I drew a deep breath of relief, for the terrible thought that had flashed across my mind was this: that Dr. Bauerstein might have had an accomplice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Yet surely it could not be! Surely no woman as beautiful as Mary Cavendish could be a murderess. Yet beautiful women had been known to poison.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And suddenly I remembered that first conversation at tea on the day of my arrival, and the gleam in her eyes as she had said that poison was a woman’s weapon. How agitated she had been on that fatal Tuesday evening! Had Mrs. Inglethorp discovered something between her and Bauerstein, and threatened to tell her husband? Was it to stop that denunciation that the crime had been committed?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then I remembered that enigmatical conversation between Poirot and Evelyn Howard. Was this what they had meant? Was this the monstrous possibility that Evelyn had tried not to believe?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Yes, it all fitted in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>No wonder Miss Howard had suggested “hushing it up.” Now I understood that unfinished sentence of hers: “Emily herself——” And in my heart I agreed with her. Would not Mrs. Inglethorp have preferred to go unavenged rather than have such terrible dishonour fall upon the name of Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There’s another thing,” said John suddenly, and the unexpected sound of his voice made me start guiltily. “Something which makes me doubt if what you say can be true.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What’s that?” I asked, thankful that he had gone away from the subject of how the poison could have been introduced into the cocoa.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, the fact that Bauerstein demanded a post-mortem. He needn’t have done so. Little Wilkins would have been quite content to let it go at heart disease.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” I said doubtfully. “But we don’t know. Perhaps he thought it safer in the long run. Someone might have talked afterwards. Then the Home Office might have ordered exhumation. The whole thing would have come out, then, and he would have been in an awkward position, for no one would have believed that a man of his reputation could have been deceived into calling it heart disease.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that’s possible,” admitted John. “Still,” he added, “I’m blest if I can see what his motive could have been.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I trembled.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look here,” I said, “I may be altogether wrong. And, remember, all this is in confidence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, of course—that goes without saying.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We had walked, as we talked, and now we passed through the little gate into the garden. Voices rose near at hand, for tea was spread out under the sycamore-tree, as it had been on the day of my arrival.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia was back from the hospital, and I placed my chair beside her, and told her of Poirot’s wish to visit the dispensary.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of course! I’d love him to see it. He’d better come to tea there one day. I must fix it up with him. He’s such a dear little man! But he <i>is</i> funny. He made me take the brooch out of my tie the other day, and put it in again, because he said it wasn’t straight.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I laughed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s quite a mania with him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, isn’t it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We were silent for a minute or two, and then, glancing in the direction of Mary Cavendish, and dropping her voice, Cynthia said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Hastings.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“After tea, I want to talk to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Her glance at Mary had set me thinking. I fancied that between these two there existed very little sympathy. For the first time, it occurred to me to wonder about the girl’s future. Mrs. Inglethorp had made no provisions of any kind for her, but I imagined that John and Mary would probably insist on her making her home with them—at any rate until the end of the war. John, I knew, was very fond of her, and would be sorry to let her go.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John, who had gone into the house, now reappeared. His good-natured face wore an unaccustomed frown of anger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Confound those detectives! I can’t think what they’re after! They’ve been in every room in the house—turning things inside out, and upside down. It really is too bad! I suppose they took advantage of our all being out. I shall go for that fellow Japp, when I next see him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Lot of Paul Prys,” grunted Miss Howard.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence opined that they had to make a show of doing something.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary Cavendish said nothing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After tea, I invited Cynthia to come for a walk, and we sauntered off into the woods together.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?” I inquired, as soon as we were protected from prying eyes by the leafy screen.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a sigh, Cynthia flung herself down, and tossed off her hat. The sunlight, piercing through the branches, turned the auburn of her hair to quivering gold.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Hastings—you are always so kind, and you know such a lot.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It struck me at this moment that Cynthia was really a very charming girl! Much more charming than Mary, who never said things of that kind.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well?” I asked benignantly, as she hesitated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I want to ask your advice. What shall I do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. You see, Aunt Emily always told me I should be provided for. I suppose she forgot, or didn’t think she was likely to die—anyway, I am <i>not</i> provided for! And I don’t know what to do. Do you think I ought to go away from here at once?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens, no! They don’t want to part with you, I’m sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia hesitated a moment, plucking up the grass with her tiny hands. Then she said: “Mrs. Cavendish does. She hates me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hates you?” I cried, astonished.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I don’t know why, but she can’t bear me; and <i>he</i> can’t, either.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There I know you’re wrong,” I said warmly. “On the contrary, John is very fond of you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes—<i>John</i>. I meant Lawrence. Not, of course, that I care whether Lawrence hates me or not. Still, it’s rather horrid when no one loves you, isn’t it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But they do, Cynthia dear,” I said earnestly. “I’m sure you are mistaken. Look, there is John—and Miss Howard——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia nodded rather gloomily. “Yes, John likes me, I think, and of course Evie, for all her gruff ways, wouldn’t be unkind to a fly. But Lawrence never speaks to me if he can help it, and Mary can hardly bring herself to be civil to me. She wants Evie to stay on, is begging her to, but she doesn’t want me, and—and—I don’t know what to do.” Suddenly the poor child burst out crying.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I don’t know what possessed me. Her beauty, perhaps, as she sat there, with the sunlight glinting down on her head; perhaps the sense of relief at encountering someone who so obviously could have no connection with the tragedy; perhaps honest pity for her youth and loneliness. Anyway, I leant forward, and taking her little hand, I said awkwardly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Marry me, Cynthia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Unwittingly, I had hit upon a sovereign remedy for her tears. She sat up at once, drew her hand away, and said, with some asperity:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t be silly!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was a little annoyed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’m not being silly. I am asking you to do me the honour of becoming my wife.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To my intense surprise, Cynthia burst out laughing, and called me a “funny dear.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s perfectly sweet of you,” she said, “but you know you don’t want to!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I do. I’ve got——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind what you’ve got. You don’t really want to—and I don’t either.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, of course, that settles it,” I said stiffly. “But I don’t see anything to laugh at. There’s nothing funny about a proposal.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, indeed,” said Cynthia. “Somebody might accept you next time. Good-bye, you’ve cheered me up <i>very</i> much.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, with a final uncontrollable burst of merriment, she vanished through the trees.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Thinking over the interview, it struck me as being profoundly unsatisfactory.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It occurred to me suddenly that I would go down to the village, and look up Bauerstein. Somebody ought to be keeping an eye on the fellow. At the same time, it would be wise to allay any suspicions he might have as to his being suspected. I remembered how Poirot had relied on my diplomacy. Accordingly, I went to the little house with the “Apartments” card inserted in the window, where I knew he lodged, and tapped on the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>An old woman came and opened it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good afternoon,” I said pleasantly. “Is Dr. Bauerstein in?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She stared at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Haven’t you heard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Heard what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“About him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What about him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’s took.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Took? Dead?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, took by the perlice.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By the police!” I gasped. “Do you mean they’ve arrested him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, that’s it, and——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I waited to hear no more, but tore up the village to find Poirot.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER X.<br>\nTHE ARREST</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>To my extreme annoyance, Poirot was not in, and the old Belgian who answered my knock informed me that he believed he had gone to London.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was dumbfounded. What on earth could Poirot be doing in London! Was it a sudden decision on his part, or had he already made up his mind when he parted from me a few hours earlier?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I retraced my steps to Styles in some annoyance. With Poirot away, I was uncertain how to act. Had he foreseen this arrest? Had he not, in all probability, been the cause of it? Those questions I could not resolve. But in the meantime what was I to do? Should I announce the arrest openly at Styles, or not? Though I did not acknowledge it to myself, the thought of Mary Cavendish was weighing on me. Would it not be a terrible shock to her? For the moment, I set aside utterly any suspicions of her. She could not be implicated—otherwise I should have heard some hint of it.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Of course, there was no possibility of being able permanently to conceal Dr. Bauerstein’s arrest from her. It would be announced in every newspaper on the morrow. Still, I shrank from blurting it out. If only Poirot had been accessible, I could have asked his advice. What possessed him to go posting off to London in this unaccountable way?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In spite of myself, my opinion of his sagacity was immeasurably heightened. I would never have dreamt of suspecting the doctor, had not Poirot put it into my head. Yes, decidedly, the little man was clever.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After some reflecting, I decided to take John into my confidence, and leave him to make the matter public or not, as he thought fit.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He gave vent to a prodigious whistle, as I imparted the news.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Great Scott! You <i>were</i> right, then. I couldn’t believe it at the time.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, it is astonishing until you get used to the idea, and see how it makes everything fit in. Now, what are we to do? Of course, it will be generally known to-morrow.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John reflected.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Never mind,” he said at last, “we won’t say anything at present. There is no need. As you say, it will be known soon enough.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But to my intense surprise, on getting down early the next morning, and eagerly opening the newspapers, there was not a word about the arrest! There was a column of mere padding about “The Styles Poisoning Case,” but nothing further. It was rather inexplicable, but I supposed that, for some reason or other, Japp wished to keep it out of the papers. It worried me just a little, for it suggested the possibility that there might be further arrests to come.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After breakfast, I decided to go down to the village, and see if Poirot had returned yet; but, before I could start, a well-known face blocked one of the windows, and the well-known voice said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Bonjour, mon ami!</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I exclaimed, with relief, and seizing him by both hands, I dragged him into the room. “I was never so glad to see anyone. Listen, I have said nothing to anybody but John. Is that right?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My friend,” replied Poirot, “I do not know what you are talking about.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dr. Bauerstein’s arrest, of course,” I answered impatiently.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is Bauerstein arrested, then?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you not know it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not the least in the world.” But, pausing a moment, he added: “Still, it does not surprise me. After all, we are only four miles from the coast.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The coast?” I asked, puzzled. “What has that got to do with it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Surely, it is obvious!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not to me. No doubt I am very dense, but I cannot see what the proximity of the coast has got to do with the murder of Mrs. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nothing at all, of course,” replied Poirot, smiling. “But we were speaking of the arrest of Dr. Bauerstein.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, he is arrested for the murder of Mrs. Inglethorp——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?” cried Poirot, in apparently lively astonishment. “Dr. Bauerstein arrested for the murder of Mrs. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Impossible! That would be too good a farce! Who told you that, my friend?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, no one exactly told me,” I confessed. “But he is arrested.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, very likely. But for espionage, <i>mon ami</i>.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Espionage?” I gasped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Precisely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not for poisoning Mrs. Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not unless our friend Japp has taken leave of his senses,” replied Poirot placidly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But—but I thought you thought so too?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot gave me one look, which conveyed a wondering pity, and his full sense of the utter absurdity of such an idea.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you mean to say,” I asked, slowly adapting myself to the new idea, “that Dr. Bauerstein is a spy?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Have you never suspected it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It never entered my head.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It did not strike you as peculiar that a famous London doctor should bury himself in a little village like this, and should be in the habit of walking about at all hours of the night, fully dressed?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I confessed, “I never thought of such a thing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He is, of course, a German by birth,” said Poirot thoughtfully, “though he has practised so long in this country that nobody thinks of him as anything but an Englishman. He was naturalized about fifteen years ago. A very clever man—a Jew, of course.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The blackguard!” I cried indignantly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. He is, on the contrary, a patriot. Think what he stands to lose. I admire the man myself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But I could not look at it in Poirot’s philosophical way.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And this is the man with whom Mrs. Cavendish has been wandering about all over the country!” I cried indignantly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. I should fancy he had found her very useful,” remarked Poirot. “So long as gossip busied itself in coupling their names together, any other vagaries of the doctor’s passed unobserved.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you think he never really cared for her?” I asked eagerly—rather too eagerly, perhaps, under the circumstances.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That, of course, I cannot say, but—shall I tell you my own private opinion, Hastings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is this: that Mrs. Cavendish does not care, and never has cared one little jot about Dr. Bauerstein!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you really think so?” I could not disguise my pleasure.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am quite sure of it. And I will tell you why.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because she cares for someone else, <i>mon ami</i>.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh!” What did he mean? In spite of myself, an agreeable warmth spread over me. I am not a vain man where women are concerned, but I remembered certain evidences, too lightly thought of at the time, perhaps, but which certainly seemed to indicate——</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My pleasing thoughts were interrupted by the sudden entrance of Miss Howard. She glanced round hastily to make sure there was no one else in the room, and quickly produced an old sheet of brown paper. This she handed to Poirot, murmuring as she did so the cryptic words:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On top of the wardrobe.” Then she hurriedly left the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot unfolded the sheet of paper eagerly, and uttered an exclamation of satisfaction. He spread it out on the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come here, Hastings. Now tell me, what is that initial—J. or L.?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was a medium sized sheet of paper, rather dusty, as though it had lain by for some time. But it was the label that was attracting Poirot’s attention. At the top, it bore the printed stamp of Messrs. Parkson’s, the well-known theatrical costumiers, and it was addressed to “—(the debatable initial) Cavendish, Esq., Styles Court, Styles St. Mary, Essex.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It might be T., or it might be L.,” I said, after studying the thing for a minute or two. “It certainly isn’t a J.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good,” replied Poirot, folding up the paper again. “I, also, am of your way of thinking. It is an L., depend upon it!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did it come from?” I asked curiously. “Is it important?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Moderately so. It confirms a surmise of mine. Having deduced its existence, I set Miss Howard to search for it, and, as you see, she has been successful.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What did she mean by ‘On the top of the wardrobe’?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She meant,” replied Poirot promptly, “that she found it on top of a wardrobe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A funny place for a piece of brown paper,” I mused.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. The top of a wardrobe is an excellent place for brown paper and cardboard boxes. I have kept them there myself. Neatly arranged, there is nothing to offend the eye.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I asked earnestly, “have you made up your mind about this crime?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes—that is to say, I believe I know how it was committed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Unfortunately, I have no proof beyond my surmise, unless——” With sudden energy, he caught me by the arm, and whirled me down the hall, calling out in French in his excitement: “Mademoiselle Dorcas, Mademoiselle Dorcas, <i>un moment, s’il vous plaît!</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas, quite flurried by the noise, came hurrying out of the pantry.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My good Dorcas, I have an idea—a little idea—if it should prove justified, what magnificent chance! Tell me, on Monday, not Tuesday, Dorcas, but Monday, the day before the tragedy, did anything go wrong with Mrs. Inglethorp’s bell?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas looked very surprised.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, sir, now you mention it, it did; though I don’t know how you came to hear of it. A mouse, or some such, must have nibbled the wire through. The man came and put it right on Tuesday morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a long drawn exclamation of ecstasy, Poirot led the way back to the morning-room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“See you, one should not ask for outside proof—no, reason should be enough. But the flesh is weak, it is consolation to find that one is on the right track. Ah, my friend, I am like a giant refreshed. I run! I leap!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, in very truth, run and leap he did, gambolling wildly down the stretch of lawn outside the long window.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is your remarkable little friend doing?” asked a voice behind me, and I turned to find Mary Cavendish at my elbow. She smiled, and so did I. “What is it all about?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really, I can’t tell you. He asked Dorcas some question about a bell, and appeared so delighted with her answer that he is capering about as you see!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary laughed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How ridiculous! He’s going out of the gate. Isn’t he coming back to-day?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t know. I’ve given up trying to guess what he’ll do next.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is he quite mad, Mr. Hastings?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I honestly don’t know. Sometimes, I feel sure he is as mad as a hatter; and then, just as he is at his maddest, I find there is method in his madness.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In spite of her laugh, Mary was looking thoughtful this morning. She seemed grave, almost sad.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It occurred to me that it would be a good opportunity to tackle her on the subject of Cynthia. I began rather tactfully, <i>I</i> thought, but I had not gone far before she stopped me authoritatively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are an excellent advocate, I have no doubt, Mr. Hastings, but in this case your talents are quite thrown away. Cynthia will run no risk of encountering any unkindness from me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I began to stammer feebly that I hoped she hadn’t thought—— But again she stopped me, and her words were so unexpected that they quite drove Cynthia, and her troubles, out of my mind.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mr. Hastings,” she said, “do you think I and my husband are happy together?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was considerably taken aback, and murmured something about it’s not being my business to think anything of the sort.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” she said quietly, “whether it is your business or not, I will tell you that we are <i>not</i> happy.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I said nothing, for I saw that she had not finished.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She began slowly, walking up and down the room, her head a little bent, and that slim, supple figure of hers swaying gently as she walked. She stopped suddenly, and looked up at me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You don’t know anything about me, do you?” she asked. “Where I come from, who I was before I married John—anything, in fact? Well, I will tell you. I will make a father confessor of you. You are kind, I think—yes, I am sure you are kind.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Somehow, I was not quite as elated as I might have been. I remembered that Cynthia had begun her confidences in much the same way. Besides, a father confessor should be elderly, it is not at all the role for a young man.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My father was English,” said Mrs. Cavendish, “but my mother was a Russian.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah,” I said, “now I understand——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Understand what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A hint of something foreign—different—that there has always been about you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My mother was very beautiful, I believe. I don’t know, because I never saw her. She died when I was quite a little child. I believe there was some tragedy connected with her death—she took an overdose of some sleeping draught by mistake. However that may be, my father was broken-hearted. Shortly afterwards, he went into the Consular Service. Everywhere he went, I went with him. When I was twenty-three, I had been nearly all over the world. It was a splendid life—I loved it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a smile on her face, and her head was thrown back. She seemed living in the memory of those old glad days.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then my father died. He left me very badly off. I had to go and live with some old aunts in Yorkshire.” She shuddered. “You will understand me when I say that it was a deadly life for a girl brought up as I had been. The narrowness, the deadly monotony of it, almost drove me mad.” She paused a minute, and added in a different tone: “And then I met John Cavendish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You can imagine that, from my aunts’ point of view, it was a very good match for me. But I can honestly say it was not this fact which weighed with me. No, he was simply a way of escape from the insufferable monotony of my life.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I said nothing, and after a moment, she went on:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t misunderstand me. I was quite honest with him. I told him, what was true, that I liked him very much, that I hoped to come to like him more, but that I was not in any way what the world calls ‘in love’ with him. He declared that that satisfied him, and so—we were married.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She waited a long time, a little frown had gathered on her forehead. She seemed to be looking back earnestly into those past days.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think—I am sure—he cared for me at first. But I suppose we were not well matched. Almost at once, we drifted apart. He—it is not a pleasing thing for my pride, but it is the truth—tired of me very soon.” I must have made some murmur of dissent, for she went on quickly: “Oh, yes, he did! Not that it matters now—now that we’ve come to the parting of the ways.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She answered quietly:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I mean that I am not going to remain at Styles.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You and John are not going to live here?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John may live here, but I shall not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are going to leave him?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She paused a long time, and said at last:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps—because I want to be—free!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, as she spoke, I had a sudden vision of broad spaces, virgin tracts of forests, untrodden lands—and a realization of what freedom would mean to such a nature as Mary Cavendish. I seemed to see her for a moment as she was, a proud wild creature, as untamed by civilization as some shy bird of the hills. A little cry broke from her lips:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You don’t know, you don’t know, how this hateful place has been prison to me!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I understand,” I said, “but—but don’t do anything rash.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, rash!” Her voice mocked at my prudence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then suddenly I said a thing I could have bitten out my tongue for:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You know that Dr. Bauerstein has been arrested?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>An instant coldness passed like a mask over her face, blotting out all expression.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“John was so kind as to break that to me this morning.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, what do you think?” I asked feebly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Of the arrest?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What should I think? Apparently he is a German spy; so the gardener had told John.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Her face and voice were absolutely cold and expressionless. Did she care, or did she not?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She moved away a step or two, and fingered one of the flower vases.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“These are quite dead. I must do them again. Would you mind moving—thank you, Mr. Hastings.” And she walked quietly past me out of the window, with a cool little nod of dismissal.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>No, surely she could not care for Bauerstein. No woman could act her part with that icy unconcern.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000003999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot did not make his appearance the following morning, and there was no sign of the Scotland Yard men.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But, at lunch-time, there arrived a new piece of evidence—or rather lack of evidence. We had vainly tried to trace the fourth letter, which Mrs. Inglethorp had written on the evening preceding her death. Our efforts having been in vain, we had abandoned the matter, hoping that it might turn up of itself one day. And this is just what did happen, in the shape of a communication, which arrived by the second post from a firm of French music publishers, acknowledging Mrs. Inglethorp’s cheque, and regretting they had been unable to trace a certain series of Russian folksongs. So the last hope of solving the mystery, by means of Mrs. Inglethorp’s correspondence on the fatal evening, had to be abandoned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Just before tea, I strolled down to tell Poirot of the new disappointment, but found, to my annoyance, that he was once more out.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Gone to London again?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, no, monsieur, he has but taken the train to Tadminster. ‘To see a young lady’s dispensary,’ he said.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Silly ass!” I ejaculated. “I told him Wednesday was the one day she wasn’t there! Well, tell him to look us up to-morrow morning, will you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly, monsieur.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But, on the following day, no sign of Poirot. I was getting angry. He was really treating us in the most cavalier fashion.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After lunch, Lawrence drew me aside, and asked if I was going down to see him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I don’t think I shall. He can come up here if he wants to see us.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh!” Lawrence looked indeterminate. Something unusually nervous and excited in his manner roused my curiosity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it?” I asked. “I could go if there’s anything special.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s nothing much, but—well, if you are going, will you tell him——” he dropped his voice to a whisper—“I think I’ve found the extra coffee-cup!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I had almost forgotten that enigmatical message of Poirot’s, but now my curiosity was aroused afresh.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence would say no more, so I decided that I would descend from my high horse, and once more seek out Poirot at Leastways Cottage.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This time I was received with a smile. Monsieur Poirot was within. Would I mount? I mounted accordingly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was sitting by the table, his head buried in his hands. He sprang up at my entrance.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it?” I asked solicitously. “You are not ill, I trust?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no, not ill. But I decide an affair of great moment.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Whether to catch the criminal or not?” I asked facetiously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But, to my great surprise, Poirot nodded gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘To speak or not to speak,’ as your so great Shakespeare says, ‘that is the question.’”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not trouble to correct the quotation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are not serious, Poirot?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am of the most serious. For the most serious of all things hangs in the balance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that is?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A woman’s happiness, <i>mon ami</i>,” he said gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not quite know what to say.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The moment has come,” said Poirot thoughtfully, “and I do not know what to do. For, see you, it is a big stake for which I play. No one but I, Hercule Poirot, would attempt it!” And he tapped himself proudly on the breast.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After pausing a few minutes respectfully, so as not to spoil his effect, I gave him Lawrence’s message.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Aha!” he cried. “So he has found the extra coffee-cup. That is good. He has more intelligence than would appear, this long-faced Monsieur Lawrence of yours!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I did not myself think very highly of Lawrence’s intelligence; but I forebore to contradict Poirot, and gently took him to task for forgetting my instructions as to which were Cynthia’s days off.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is true. I have the head of a sieve. However, the other young lady was most kind. She was sorry for my disappointment, and showed me everything in the kindest way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, well, that’s all right, then, and you must go to tea with Cynthia another day.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I told him about the letter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am sorry for that,” he said. “I always had hopes of that letter. But no, it was not to be. This affair must all be unravelled from within.” He tapped his forehead. “These little grey cells. It is ‘up to them’—as you say over here.” Then, suddenly, he asked: “Are you a judge of finger-marks, my friend?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I said, rather surprised, “I know that there are no two finger-marks alike, but that’s as far as my science goes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He unlocked a little drawer, and took out some photographs which he laid on the table.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have numbered them, 1, 2, 3. Will you describe them to me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I studied the proofs attentively.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All greatly magnified, I see. No. 1, I should say, are a man’s finger-prints; thumb and first finger. No. 2 are a lady’s; they are much smaller, and quite different in every way. No. 3”—I paused for some time—“there seem to be a lot of confused finger-marks, but here, very distinctly, are No. 1’s.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Overlapping the others?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You recognize them beyond fail?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes; they are identical.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded, and gently taking the photographs from me locked them up again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose,” I said, “that as usual, you are not going to explain?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the contrary. No. 1 were the finger-prints of Monsieur Lawrence. No. 2 were those of Mademoiselle Cynthia. They are not important. I merely obtained them for comparison. No. 3 is a little more complicated.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is, as you see, highly magnified. You may have noticed a sort of blur extending all across the picture. I will not describe to you the special apparatus, dusting powder, etc., which I used. It is a well-known process to the police, and by means of it you can obtain a photograph of the finger-prints of any object in a very short space of time. Well, my friend, you have seen the finger-marks—it remains to tell you the particular object on which they had been left.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Go on—I am really excited.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Eh bien!</i> Photo No. 3 represents the highly magnified surface of a tiny bottle in the top poison cupboard of the dispensary in the Red Cross Hospital at Tadminster—which sounds like the house that Jack built!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” I exclaimed. “But what were Lawrence Cavendish’s finger-marks doing on it? He never went near the poison cupboard the day we were there!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, yes, he did!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Impossible! We were all together the whole time.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shook his head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, my friend, there was a moment when you were not all together. There was a moment when you could not have been all together, or it would not have been necessary to call to Monsieur Lawrence to come and join you on the balcony.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I’d forgotten that,” I admitted. “But it was only for a moment.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Long enough.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Long enough for what?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot’s smile became rather enigmatical.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Long enough for a gentleman who had once studied medicine to gratify a very natural interest and curiosity.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our eyes met. Poirot’s were pleasantly vague. He got up and hummed a little tune. I watched him suspiciously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I said, “what was in this particular little bottle?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot looked out of the window.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Hydro-chloride of strychnine,” he said, over his shoulder, continuing to hum.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens!” I said it quite quietly. I was not surprised. I had expected that answer.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They use the pure hydro-chloride of strychnine very little—only occasionally for pills. It is the official solution, Liq. Strychnine Hydro-clor. that is used in most medicines. That is why the finger-marks have remained undisturbed since then.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you manage to take this photograph?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I dropped my hat from the balcony,” explained Poirot simply. “Visitors were not permitted below at that hour, so, in spite of my many apologies, Mademoiselle Cynthia’s colleague had to go down and fetch it for me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you knew what you were going to find?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, not at all. I merely realized that it was possible, from your story, for Monsieur Lawrence to go to the poison cupboard. The possibility had to be confirmed, or eliminated.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot,” I said, “your gaiety does not deceive me. This is a very important discovery.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not know,” said Poirot. “But one thing does strike me. No doubt it has struck you too.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, that there is altogether too much strychnine about this case. This is the third time we run up against it. There was strychnine in Mrs. Inglethorp’s tonic. There is the strychnine sold across the counter at Styles St. Mary by Mace. Now we have more strychnine, handled by one of the household. It is confusing; and, as you know, I do not like confusion.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Before I could reply, one of the other Belgians opened the door and stuck his head in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is a lady below, asking for Mr Hastings.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A lady?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I jumped up. Poirot followed me down the narrow stairs. Mary Cavendish was standing in the doorway.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have been visiting an old woman in the village,” she explained, “and as Lawrence told me you were with Monsieur Poirot I thought I would call for you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Alas, madame,” said Poirot, “I thought you had come to honour me with a visit!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I will some day, if you ask me,” she promised him, smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is well. If you should need a father confessor, madame”—she started ever so slightly—“remember, Papa Poirot is always at your service.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She stared at him for a few minutes, as though seeking to read some deeper meaning into his words. Then she turned abruptly away.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come, will you not walk back with us too, Monsieur Poirot?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Enchanted, madame.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>All the way to Styles, Mary talked fast and feverishly. It struck me that in some way she was nervous of Poirot’s eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The weather had broken, and the sharp wind was almost autumnal in its shrewishness. Mary shivered a little, and buttoned her black sports coat closer. The wind through the trees made a mournful noise, like some great giant sighing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We walked up to the great door of Styles, and at once the knowledge came to us that something was wrong.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas came running out to meet us. She was crying and wringing her hands. I was aware of other servants huddled together in the background, all eyes and ears.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, m’am! Oh, m’am! I don’t know how to tell you——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it, Dorcas?” I asked impatiently. “Tell us at once.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It’s those wicked detectives. They’ve arrested him—they’ve arrested Mr. Cavendish!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Arrested Lawrence?” I gasped.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I saw a strange look come into Dorcas’s eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir. Not Mr. Lawrence—Mr. John.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Behind me, with a wild cry, Mary Cavendish fell heavily against me, and as I turned to catch her I met the quiet triumph in Poirot’s eyes.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER XI.<br>\nTHE CASE FOR THE PROSECUTION</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The trial of John Cavendish for the murder of his stepmother took place two months later.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Of the intervening weeks I will say little, but my admiration and sympathy went out unfeignedly to Mary Cavendish. She ranged herself passionately on her husband’s side, scorning the mere idea of his guilt, and fought for him tooth and nail.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I expressed my admiration to Poirot, and he nodded thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, she is of those women who show at their best in adversity. It brings out all that is sweetest and truest in them. Her pride and her jealousy have——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Jealousy?” I queried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Have you not realized that she is an unusually jealous woman? As I was saying, her pride and jealousy have been laid aside. She thinks of nothing but her husband, and the terrible fate that is hanging over him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He spoke very feelingly, and I looked at him earnestly, remembering that last afternoon, when he had been deliberating whether or not to speak. With his tenderness for “a woman’s happiness,” I felt glad that the decision had been taken out of his hands.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Even now,” I said, “I can hardly believe it. You see, up to the very last minute, I thought it was Lawrence!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot grinned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I know you did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But John! My old friend John!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Every murderer is probably somebody’s old friend,” observed Poirot philosophically. “You cannot mix up sentiment and reason.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I must say I think you might have given me a hint.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps, <i>mon ami</i>, I did not do so, just because he <i>was</i> your old friend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I was rather disconcerted by this, remembering how I had busily passed on to John what I believed to be Poirot’s views concerning Bauerstein. He, by the way, had been acquitted of the charge brought against him. Nevertheless, although he had been too clever for them this time, and the charge of espionage could not be brought home to him, his wings were pretty well clipped for the future.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I asked Poirot whether he thought John would be condemned. To my intense surprise, he replied that, on the contrary, he was extremely likely to be acquitted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But, Poirot——” I protested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh, my friend, have I not said to you all along that I have no proofs. It is one thing to know that a man is guilty, it is quite another matter to prove him so. And, in this case, there is terribly little evidence. That is the whole trouble. I, Hercule Poirot, know, but I lack the last link in my chain. And unless I can find that missing link——” He shook his head gravely.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did you first suspect John Cavendish?” I asked, after a minute or two.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you not suspect him at all?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, indeed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not after that fragment of conversation you overheard between Mrs. Cavendish and her mother-in-law, and her subsequent lack of frankness at the inquest?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you not put two and two together, and reflect that if it was not Alfred Inglethorp who was quarrelling with his wife—and you remember, he strenuously denied it at the inquest—it must be either Lawrence or John. Now, if it was Lawrence, Mary Cavendish’s conduct was just as inexplicable. But if, on the other hand, it was John, the whole thing was explained quite naturally.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So,” I cried, a light breaking in upon me, “it was John who quarrelled with his mother that afternoon?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And you have known this all along?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly. Mrs. Cavendish’s behaviour could only be explained that way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet you say he may be acquitted?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot shrugged his shoulders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly I do. At the police court proceedings, we shall hear the case for the prosecution, but in all probability his solicitors will advise him to reserve his defence. That will be sprung upon us at the trial. And—ah, by the way, I have a word of caution to give you, my friend. I must not appear in the case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. Officially, I have nothing to do with it. Until I have found that last link in my chain, I must remain behind the scenes. Mrs. Cavendish must think I am working for her husband, not against him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I say, that’s playing it a bit low down,” I protested.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. We have to deal with a most clever and unscrupulous man, and we must use any means in our power—otherwise he will slip through our fingers. That is why I have been careful to remain in the background. All the discoveries have been made by Japp, and Japp will take all the credit. If I am called upon to give evidence at all”—he smiled broadly—“it will probably be as a witness for the defence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could hardly believe my ears.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is quite <i>en règle</i>,” continued Poirot. “Strangely enough, I can give evidence that will demolish one contention of the prosecution.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Which one?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The one that relates to the destruction of the will. John Cavendish did not destroy that will.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot was a true prophet. I will not go into the details of the police court proceedings, as it involves many tiresome repetitions. I will merely state baldly that John Cavendish reserved his defence, and was duly committed for trial.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>September found us all in London. Mary took a house in Kensington, Poirot being included in the family party.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I myself had been given a job at the War Office, so was able to see them continually.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As the weeks went by, the state of Poirot’s nerves grew worse and worse. That “last link” he talked about was still lacking. Privately, I hoped it might remain so, for what happiness could there be for Mary, if John were not acquitted?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>On September 15th John Cavendish appeared in the dock at the Old Bailey, charged with “The Wilful Murder of Emily Agnes Inglethorp,” and pleaded “Not Guilty.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest Heavywether, the famous K.C., had been engaged to defend him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Philips, K.C., opened the case for the Crown.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The murder, he said, was a most premeditated and cold-blooded one. It was neither more nor less than the deliberate poisoning of a fond and trusting woman by the stepson to whom she had been more than a mother. Ever since his boyhood, she had supported him. He and his wife had lived at Styles Court in every luxury, surrounded by her care and attention. She had been their kind and generous benefactress.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He proposed to call witnesses to show how the prisoner, a profligate and spendthrift, had been at the end of his financial tether, and had also been carrying on an intrigue with a certain Mrs. Raikes, a neighbouring farmer’s wife. This having come to his stepmother’s ears, she taxed him with it on the afternoon before her death, and a quarrel ensued, part of which was overheard. On the previous day, the prisoner had purchased strychnine at the village chemist’s shop, wearing a disguise by means of which he hoped to throw the onus of the crime upon another man—to wit, Mrs. Inglethorp’s husband, of whom he had been bitterly jealous. Luckily for Mr. Inglethorp, he had been able to produce an unimpeachable alibi.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>On the afternoon of July 17th, continued Counsel, immediately after the quarrel with her son, Mrs. Inglethorp made a new will. This will was found destroyed in the grate of her bedroom the following morning, but evidence had come to light which showed that it had been drawn up in favour of her husband. Deceased had already made a will in his favour before her marriage, but—and Mr. Philips wagged an expressive forefinger—the prisoner was not aware of that. What had induced the deceased to make a fresh will, with the old one still extant, he could not say. She was an old lady, and might possibly have forgotten the former one; or—this seemed to him more likely—she may have had an idea that it was revoked by her marriage, as there had been some conversation on the subject. Ladies were not always very well versed in legal knowledge. She had, about a year before, executed a will in favour of the prisoner. He would call evidence to show that it was the prisoner who ultimately handed his stepmother her coffee on the fatal night. Later in the evening, he had sought admission to her room, on which occasion, no doubt, he found an opportunity of destroying the will which, as far as he knew, would render the one in his favour valid.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The prisoner had been arrested in consequence of the discovery, in his room, by Detective Inspector Japp—a most brilliant officer—of the identical phial of strychnine which had been sold at the village chemist’s to the supposed Mr. Inglethorp on the day before the murder. It would be for the jury to decide whether or not these damning facts constituted an overwhelming proof of the prisoner’s guilt.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>And, subtly implying that a jury which did not so decide, was quite unthinkable, Mr. Philips sat down and wiped his forehead.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The first witnesses for the prosecution were mostly those who had been called at the inquest, the medical evidence being again taken first.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest Heavywether, who was famous all over England for the unscrupulous manner in which he bullied witnesses, only asked two questions.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I take it, Dr. Bauerstein, that strychnine, as a drug, acts quickly?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And that you are unable to account for the delay in this case?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thank you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Mace identified the phial handed him by Counsel as that sold by him to “Mr. Inglethorp.” Pressed, he admitted that he only knew Mr. Inglethorp by sight. He had never spoken to him. The witness was not cross-examined.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Alfred Inglethorp was called, and denied having purchased the poison. He also denied having quarrelled with his wife. Various witnesses testified to the accuracy of these statements.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The gardeners’ evidence, as to the witnessing of the will was taken, and then Dorcas was called.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas, faithful to her “young gentlemen,” denied strenuously that it could have been John’s voice she heard, and resolutely declared, in the teeth of everything, that it was Mr. Inglethorp who had been in the boudoir with her mistress. A rather wistful smile passed across the face of the prisoner in the dock. He knew only too well how useless her gallant defiance was, since it was not the object of the defence to deny this point. Mrs. Cavendish, of course, could not be called upon to give evidence against her husband.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After various questions on other matters, Mr. Philips asked:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the month of June last, do you remember a parcel arriving for Mr. Lawrence Cavendish from Parkson’s?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Dorcas shook her head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t remember, sir. It may have done, but Mr. Lawrence was away from home part of June.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In the event of a parcel arriving for him whilst he was away, what would be done with it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It would either be put in his room or sent on after him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“By you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, sir, I should leave it on the hall table. It would be Miss Howard who would attend to anything like that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Evelyn Howard was called and, after being examined on other points, was questioned as to the parcel.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t remember. Lots of parcels come. Can’t remember one special one.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not know if it was sent after Mr. Lawrence Cavendish to Wales, or whether it was put in his room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Don’t think it was sent after him. Should have remembered it if it was.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Supposing a parcel arrived addressed to Mr. Lawrence Cavendish, and afterwards it disappeared, should you remark its absence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, don’t think so. I should think someone had taken charge of it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I believe, Miss Howard, that it was you who found this sheet of brown paper?” He held up the same dusty piece which Poirot and I had examined in the morning-room at Styles.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I did.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How did you come to look for it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The Belgian detective who was employed on the case asked me to search for it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where did you eventually discover it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On the top of—of—a wardrobe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On top of the prisoner’s wardrobe?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I believe so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you not find it yourself?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then you must know where you found it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, it was on the prisoner’s wardrobe.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is better.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>An assistant from Parkson’s, Theatrical Costumiers, testified that on June 29th, they had supplied a black beard to Mr. L. Cavendish, as requested. It was ordered by letter, and a postal order was enclosed. No, they had not kept the letter. All transactions were entered in their books. They had sent the beard, as directed, to “L. Cavendish, Esq., Styles Court.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest Heavywether rose ponderously.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Where was the letter written from?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“From Styles Court.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The same address to which you sent the parcel?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And the letter came from there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Like a beast of prey, Heavywether fell upon him:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you know?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I don’t understand.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you know that letter came from Styles? Did you notice the postmark?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No—but——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, you did <i>not</i> notice the postmark! And yet you affirm so confidently that it came from Styles. It might, in fact, have been any postmark?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Y—es.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In fact, the letter, though written on stamped notepaper, might have been posted from anywhere? From Wales, for instance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The witness admitted that such might be the case, and Sir Ernest signified that he was satisfied.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Elizabeth Wells, second housemaid at Styles, stated that after she had gone to bed she remembered that she had bolted the front door, instead of leaving it on the latch as Mr. Inglethorp had requested. She had accordingly gone downstairs again to rectify her error. Hearing a slight noise in the West wing, she had peeped along the passage, and had seen Mr. John Cavendish knocking at Mrs. Inglethorp’s door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest Heavywether made short work of her, and under his unmerciful bullying she contradicted herself hopelessly, and Sir Ernest sat down again with a satisfied smile on his face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With the evidence of Annie, as to the candle grease on the floor, and as to seeing the prisoner take the coffee into the boudoir, the proceedings were adjourned until the following day.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As we went home, Mary Cavendish spoke bitterly against the prosecuting counsel.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That hateful man! What a net he has drawn around my poor John! How he twisted every little fact until he made it seem what it wasn’t!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” I said consolingly, “it will be the other way about to-morrow.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes,” she said meditatively; then suddenly dropped her voice. “Mr. Hastings, you do not think—surely it could not have been Lawrence—Oh, no, that could not be!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But I myself was puzzled, and as soon as I was alone with Poirot I asked him what he thought Sir Ernest was driving at.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah!” said Poirot appreciatively. “He is a clever man, that Sir Ernest.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you think he believes Lawrence guilty?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do not think he believes or cares anything! No, what he is trying for is to create such confusion in the minds of the jury that they are divided in their opinion as to which brother did it. He is endeavouring to make out that there is quite as much evidence against Lawrence as against John—and I am not at all sure that he will not succeed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Detective-inspector Japp was the first witness called when the trial was reopened, and gave his evidence succinctly and briefly. After relating the earlier events, he proceeded:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Acting on information received, Superintendent Summerhaye and myself searched the prisoner’s room, during his temporary absence from the house. In his chest of drawers, hidden beneath some underclothing, we found: first, a pair of gold-rimmed pince-nez similar to those worn by Mr. Inglethorp”—these were exhibited—“secondly, this phial.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The phial was that already recognized by the chemist’s assistant, a tiny bottle of blue glass, containing a few grains of a white crystalline powder, and labelled: “Strychnine Hydro-chloride. POISON.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A fresh piece of evidence discovered by the detectives since the police court proceedings was a long, almost new piece of blotting-paper. It had been found in Mrs. Inglethorp’s cheque book, and on being reversed at a mirror, showed clearly the words: “. . . erything of which I die possessed I leave to my beloved husband Alfred Ing...” This placed beyond question the fact that the destroyed will had been in favour of the deceased lady’s husband. Japp then produced the charred fragment of paper recovered from the grate, and this, with the discovery of the beard in the attic, completed his evidence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But Sir Ernest’s cross-examination was yet to come.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What day was it when you searched the prisoner’s room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Tuesday, the 24th of July.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly a week after the tragedy?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You found these two objects, you say, in the chest of drawers. Was the drawer unlocked?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Does it not strike you as unlikely that a man who had committed a crime should keep the evidence of it in an unlocked drawer for anyone to find?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He might have stowed them there in a hurry.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But you have just said it was a whole week since the crime. He would have had ample time to remove them and destroy them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There is no perhaps about it. Would he, or would he not have had plenty of time to remove and destroy them?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Was the pile of underclothes under which the things were hidden heavy or light?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Heavyish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In other words, it was winter underclothing. Obviously, the prisoner would not be likely to go to that drawer?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Kindly answer my question. Would the prisoner, in the hottest week of a hot summer, be likely to go to a drawer containing winter underclothing. Yes, or no?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In that case, is it not possible that the articles in question might have been put there by a third person, and that the prisoner was quite unaware of their presence?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should not think it likely.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But it is possible?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>More evidence followed. Evidence as to the financial difficulties in which the prisoner had found himself at the end of July. Evidence as to his intrigue with Mrs. Raikes—poor Mary, that must have been bitter hearing for a woman of her pride. Evelyn Howard had been right in her facts, though her animosity against Alfred Inglethorp had caused her to jump to the conclusion that he was the person concerned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence Cavendish was then put into the box. In a low voice, in answer to Mr. Philips’ questions, he denied having ordered anything from Parkson’s in June. In fact, on June 29th, he had been staying away, in Wales.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Instantly, Sir Ernest’s chin was shooting pugnaciously forward.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You deny having ordered a black beard from Parkson’s on June 29th?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I do.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! In the event of anything happening to your brother, who will inherit Styles Court?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The brutality of the question called a flush to Lawrence’s pale face. The judge gave vent to a faint murmur of disapprobation, and the prisoner in the dock leant forward angrily.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Heavywether cared nothing for his client’s anger.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Answer my question, if you please.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose,” said Lawrence quietly, “that I should.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What do you mean by you ‘suppose’? Your brother has no children. You <i>would</i> inherit it, wouldn’t you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, that’s better,” said Heavywether, with ferocious geniality. “And you’d inherit a good slice of money too, wouldn’t you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Really, Sir Ernest,” protested the judge, “these questions are not relevant.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest bowed, and having shot his arrow proceeded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On Tuesday, the 17th July, you went, I believe, with another guest, to visit the dispensary at the Red Cross Hospital in Tadminster?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you—while you happened to be alone for a few seconds—unlock the poison cupboard, and examine some of the bottles?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I—may have done so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I put it to you that you did do so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest fairly shot the next question at him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Did you examine one bottle in particular?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I do not think so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Be careful, Mr. Cavendish. I am referring to a little bottle of Hydro-chloride of Strychnine.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence was turning a sickly greenish colour.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“N—o—I am sure I didn’t.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then how do you account for the fact that you left the unmistakable impress of your finger-prints on it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The bullying manner was highly efficacious with a nervous disposition.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I suppose I must have taken up the bottle.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I suppose so too! Did you abstract any of the contents of the bottle?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Certainly not.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then why did you take it up?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I once studied to be a doctor. Such things naturally interest me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah! So poisons ‘naturally interest’ you, do they? Still, you waited to be alone before gratifying that ‘interest’ of yours?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That was pure chance. If the others had been there, I should have done just the same.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Still, as it happens, the others were not there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In fact, during the whole afternoon, you were only alone for a couple of minutes, and it happened—I say, it happened—to be during those two minutes that you displayed your ‘natural interest’ in Hydro-chloride of Strychnine?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence stammered pitiably.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a satisfied and expressive countenance, Sir Ernest observed:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I have nothing more to ask you, Mr. Cavendish.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>This bit of cross-examination had caused great excitement in court. The heads of the many fashionably attired women present were busily laid together, and their whispers became so loud that the judge angrily threatened to have the court cleared if there was not immediate silence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was little more evidence. The hand-writing experts were called upon for their opinion of the signature of “Alfred Inglethorp” in the chemist’s poison register. They all declared unanimously that it was certainly not his hand-writing, and gave it as their view that it might be that of the prisoner disguised. Cross-examined, they admitted that it might be the prisoner’s hand-writing cleverly counterfeited.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest Heavywether’s speech in opening the case for the defence was not a long one, but it was backed by the full force of his emphatic manner. Never, he said, in the course of his long experience, had he known a charge of murder rest on slighter evidence. Not only was it entirely circumstantial, but the greater part of it was practically unproved. Let them take the testimony they had heard and sift it impartially. The strychnine had been found in a drawer in the prisoner’s room. That drawer was an unlocked one, as he had pointed out, and he submitted that there was no evidence to prove that it was the prisoner who had concealed the poison there. It was, in fact, a wicked and malicious attempt on the part of some third person to fix the crime on the prisoner. The prosecution had been unable to produce a shred of evidence in support of their contention that it was the prisoner who ordered the black beard from Parkson’s. The quarrel which had taken place between prisoner and his stepmother was freely admitted, but both it and his financial embarrassments had been grossly exaggerated.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His learned friend—Sir Ernest nodded carelessly at Mr. Philips—had stated that if the prisoner were an innocent man, he would have come forward at the inquest to explain that it was he, and not Mr. Inglethorp, who had been the participator in the quarrel. He thought the facts had been misrepresented. What had actually occurred was this. The prisoner, returning to the house on Tuesday evening, had been authoritatively told that there had been a violent quarrel between Mr. and Mrs. Inglethorp. No suspicion had entered the prisoner’s head that anyone could possibly have mistaken his voice for that of Mr. Inglethorp. He naturally concluded that his stepmother had had two quarrels.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The prosecution averred that on Monday, July 16th, the prisoner had entered the chemist’s shop in the village, disguised as Mr. Inglethorp. The prisoner, on the contrary, was at that time at a lonely spot called Marston’s Spinney, where he had been summoned by an anonymous note, couched in blackmailing terms, and threatening to reveal certain matters to his wife unless he complied with its demands. The prisoner had, accordingly, gone to the appointed spot, and after waiting there vainly for half an hour had returned home. Unfortunately, he had met with no one on the way there or back who could vouch for the truth of his story, but luckily he had kept the note, and it would be produced as evidence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>As for the statement relating to the destruction of the will, the prisoner had formerly practised at the Bar, and was perfectly well aware that the will made in his favour a year before was automatically revoked by his stepmother’s remarriage. He would call evidence to show who did destroy the will, and it was possible that that might open up quite a new view of the case.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Finally, he would point out to the jury that there was evidence against other people besides John Cavendish. He would direct their attention to the fact that the evidence against Mr. Lawrence Cavendish was quite as strong, if not stronger than that against his brother.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He would now call the prisoner.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>John acquitted himself well in the witness-box. Under Sir Ernest’s skilful handling, he told his tale credibly and well. The anonymous note received by him was produced, and handed to the jury to examine. The readiness with which he admitted his financial difficulties, and the disagreement with his stepmother, lent value to his denials.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>At the close of his examination, he paused, and said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I should like to make one thing clear. I utterly reject and disapprove of Sir Ernest Heavywether’s insinuations against my brother. My brother, I am convinced, had no more to do with the crime than I have.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Sir Ernest merely smiled, and noted with a sharp eye that John’s protest had produced a very favourable impression on the jury.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Then the cross-examination began.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I understand you to say that it never entered your head that the witnesses at the inquest could possibly have mistaken your voice for that of Mr. Inglethorp. Is not that very surprising?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I don’t think so. I was told there had been a quarrel between my mother and Mr. Inglethorp, and it never occurred to me that such was not really the case.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not when the servant Dorcas repeated certain fragments of the conversation—fragments which you must have recognized?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did not recognize them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Your memory must be unusually short!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but we were both angry, and, I think, said more than we meant. I paid very little attention to my mother’s actual words.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mr. Philips’ incredulous sniff was a triumph of forensic skill. He passed on to the subject of the note.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You have produced this note very opportunely. Tell me, is there nothing familiar about the hand-writing of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not that I know of.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you not think that it bears a marked resemblance to your own hand-writing—carelessly disguised?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I do not think so.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I put it to you that it is your own hand-writing!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I put it to you that, anxious to prove an alibi, you conceived the idea of a fictitious and rather incredible appointment, and wrote this note yourself in order to bear out your statement!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it not a fact that, at the time you claim to have been waiting about at a solitary and unfrequented spot, you were really in the chemist’s shop in Styles St. Mary, where you purchased strychnine in the name of Alfred Inglethorp?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, that is a lie.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I put it to you that, wearing a suit of Mr. Inglethorp’s clothes, with a black beard trimmed to resemble his, you were there—and signed the register in his name!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is absolutely untrue.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I will leave the remarkable similarity of hand-writing between the note, the register, and your own, to the consideration of the jury,” said Mr. Philips, and sat down with the air of a man who has done his duty, but who was nevertheless horrified by such deliberate perjury.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>After this, as it was growing late, the case was adjourned till Monday.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot, I noticed, was looking profoundly discouraged. He had that little frown between the eyes that I knew so well.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it, Poirot?” I inquired.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, <i>mon ami</i>, things are going badly, badly.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In spite of myself, my heart gave a leap of relief. Evidently there was a likelihood of John Cavendish being acquitted.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>When we reached the house, my little friend waved aside Mary’s offer of tea.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, I thank you, madame. I will mount to my room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I followed him. Still frowning, he went across to the desk and took out a small pack of patience cards. Then he drew up a chair to the table, and, to my utter amazement, began solemnly to build card houses!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>My jaw dropped involuntarily, and he said at once:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, <i>mon ami</i>, I am not in my second childhood! I steady my nerves, that is all. This employment requires precision of the fingers. With precision of the fingers goes precision of the brain. And never have I needed that more than now!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is the trouble?” I asked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>With a great thump on the table, Poirot demolished his carefully built up edifice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is this, <i>mon ami!</i> That I can build card houses seven stories high, but I cannot”—thump—“find”—thump—“ that last link of which I spoke to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I could not quite tell what to say, so I held my peace, and he began slowly building up the cards again, speaking in jerks as he did so.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It is done—so! By placing—one card—on another—with mathematical—precision!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I watched the card house rising under his hands, story by story. He never hesitated or faltered. It was really almost like a conjuring trick.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What a steady hand you’ve got,” I remarked. “I believe I’ve only seen your hand shake once.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On an occasion when I was enraged, without doubt,” observed Poirot, with great placidity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes indeed! You were in a towering rage. Do you remember? It was when you discovered that the lock of the despatch-case in Mrs. Inglethorp’s bedroom had been forced. You stood by the mantelpiece, twiddling the things on it in your usual fashion, and your hand shook like a leaf! I must say——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But I stopped suddenly. For Poirot, uttering a hoarse and inarticulate cry, again annihilated his masterpiece of cards, and putting his hands over his eyes swayed backwards and forwards, apparently suffering the keenest agony.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Good heavens, Poirot!” I cried. “What is the matter? Are you taken ill?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no,” he gasped. “It is—it is—that I have an idea!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Oh!” I exclaimed, much relieved. “One of your ‘little ideas’?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, <i>ma foi</i>, no!” replied Poirot frankly. “This time it is an idea gigantic! Stupendous! And you—<i>you</i>, my friend, have given it to me!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly clasping me in his arms, he kissed me warmly on both cheeks, and before I had recovered from my surprise ran headlong from the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary Cavendish entered at that moment.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What <i>is</i> the matter with Monsieur Poirot? He rushed past me crying out: ‘A garage! For the love of Heaven, direct me to a garage, madame!’ And, before I could answer, he had dashed out into the street.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I hurried to the window. True enough, there he was, tearing down the street, hatless, and gesticulating as he went. I turned to Mary with a gesture of despair.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“He’ll be stopped by a policeman in another minute. There he goes, round the corner!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Our eyes met, and we stared helplessly at one another.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What can be the matter?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t know. He was building card houses, when suddenly he said he had an idea, and rushed off as you saw.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” said Mary, “I expect he will be back before dinner.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>But night fell, and Poirot had not returned.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER XII.<br>\nTHE LAST LINK</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot’s abrupt departure had intrigued us all greatly. Sunday morning wore away, and still he did not reappear. But about three o’clock a ferocious and prolonged hooting outside drove us to the window, to see Poirot alighting from a car, accompanied by Japp and Summerhaye. The little man was transformed. He radiated an absurd complacency. He bowed with exaggerated respect to Mary Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Madame, I have your permission to hold a little <i>réunion</i> in the <i>salon</i>? It is necessary for everyone to attend.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Mary smiled sadly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You know, Monsieur Poirot, that you have <i>carte blanche</i> in every way.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are too amiable, madame.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Still beaming, Poirot marshalled us all into the drawing-room, bringing forward chairs as he did so.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard—here. Mademoiselle Cynthia. Monsieur Lawrence. The good Dorcas. And Annie. <i>Bien!</i> We must delay our proceedings a few minutes until Mr. Inglethorp arrives. I have sent him a note.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Miss Howard rose immediately from her seat.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“If that man comes into the house, I leave it!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, no!” Poirot went up to her and pleaded in a low voice.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Finally Miss Howard consented to return to her chair. A few minutes later Alfred Inglethorp entered the room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>The company once assembled, Poirot rose from his seat with the air of a popular lecturer, and bowed politely to his audience.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Messieurs, mesdames</i>, as you all know, I was called in by Monsieur John Cavendish to investigate this case. I at once examined the bedroom of the deceased which, by the advice of the doctors, had been kept locked, and was consequently exactly as it had been when the tragedy occurred. I found: first, a fragment of green material; second, a stain on the carpet near the window, still damp; thirdly, an empty box of bromide powders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To take the fragment of green material first, I found it caught in the bolt of the communicating door between that room and the adjoining one occupied by Mademoiselle Cynthia. I handed the fragment over to the police who did not consider it of much importance. Nor did they recognize it for what it was—a piece torn from a green land armlet.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>There was a little stir of excitement.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now there was only one person at Styles who worked on the land—Mrs. Cavendish. Therefore it must have been Mrs. Cavendish who entered the deceased’s room through the door communicating with Mademoiselle Cynthia’s room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But that door was bolted on the inside!” I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I examined the room, yes. But in the first place we have only her word for it, since it was she who tried that particular door and reported it fastened. In the ensuing confusion she would have had ample opportunity to shoot the bolt across. I took an early opportunity of verifying my conjectures. To begin with, the fragment corresponds exactly with a tear in Mrs. Cavendish’s armlet. Also, at the inquest, Mrs. Cavendish declared that she had heard, from her own room, the fall of the table by the bed. I took an early opportunity of testing that statement by stationing my friend Monsieur Hastings in the left wing of the building, just outside Mrs. Cavendish’s door. I myself, in company with the police, went to the deceased’s room, and whilst there I, apparently accidentally, knocked over the table in question, but found that, as I had expected, Monsieur Hastings had heard no sound at all. This confirmed my belief that Mrs. Cavendish was not speaking the truth when she declared that she had been dressing in her room at the time of the tragedy. In fact, I was convinced that, far from having been in her own room, Mrs. Cavendish was actually in the deceased’s room when the alarm was given.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shot a quick glance at Mary. She was very pale, but smiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I proceeded to reason on that assumption. Mrs. Cavendish is in her mother-in-law’s room. We will say that she is seeking for something and has not yet found it. Suddenly Mrs. Inglethorp awakens and is seized with an alarming paroxysm. She flings out her arm, overturning the bed table, and then pulls desperately at the bell. Mrs. Cavendish, startled, drops her candle, scattering the grease on the carpet. She picks it up, and retreats quickly to Mademoiselle Cynthia’s room, closing the door behind her. She hurries out into the passage, for the servants must not find her where she is. But it is too late! Already footsteps are echoing along the gallery which connects the two wings. What can she do? Quick as thought, she hurries back to the young girl’s room, and starts shaking her awake. The hastily aroused household come trooping down the passage. They are all busily battering at Mrs. Inglethorp’s door. It occurs to nobody that Mrs. Cavendish has not arrived with the rest, but—and this is significant—I can find no one who saw her come from the other wing.” He looked at Mary Cavendish. “Am I right, madame?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She bowed her head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Quite right, monsieur. You understand that, if I had thought I would do my husband any good by revealing these facts, I would have done so. But it did not seem to me to bear upon the question of his guilt or innocence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In a sense, that is correct, madame. But it cleared my mind of many misconceptions, and left me free to see other facts in their true significance.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The will!” cried Lawrence. “Then it was you, Mary, who destroyed the will?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She shook her head, and Poirot shook his also.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” he said quietly. “There is only one person who could possibly have destroyed that will—Mrs. Inglethorp herself!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Impossible!” I exclaimed. “She had only made it out that very afternoon!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Nevertheless, <i>mon ami</i>, it was Mrs. Inglethorp. Because, in no other way can you account for the fact that, on one of the hottest days of the year, Mrs. Inglethorp ordered a fire to be lighted in her room.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I gave a gasp. What idiots we had been never to think of that fire as being incongruous! Poirot was continuing:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“The temperature on that day, messieurs, was 80 degrees in the shade. Yet Mrs. Inglethorp ordered a fire! Why? Because she wished to destroy something, and could think of no other way. You will remember that, in consequence of the War economics practiced at Styles, no waste paper was thrown away. There was therefore no means of destroying a thick document such as a will. The moment I heard of a fire being lighted in Mrs. Inglethorp’s room, I leaped to the conclusion that it was to destroy some important document—possibly a will. So the discovery of the charred fragment in the grate was no surprise to me. I did not, of course, know at the time that the will in question had only been made this afternoon, and I will admit that, when I learnt that fact, I fell into a grievous error. I came to the conclusion that Mrs. Inglethorp’s determination to destroy her will arose as a direct consequence of the quarrel she had that afternoon, and that therefore the quarrel took place after, and not before the making of the will.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here, as we know, I was wrong, and I was forced to abandon that idea. I faced the problem from a new standpoint. Now, at four o’clock, Dorcas overheard her mistress saying angrily: ‘You need not think that any fear of publicity, or scandal between husband and wife will deter me.” I conjectured, and conjectured rightly, that these words were addressed, not to her husband, but to Mr. John Cavendish. At five o’clock, an hour later, she uses almost the same words, but the standpoint is different. She admits to Dorcas, ‘I don’t know what to do; scandal between husband and wife is a dreadful thing.’ At four o’clock she has been angry, but completely mistress of herself. At five o’clock she is in violent distress, and speaks of having had a great shock.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Looking at the matter psychologically, I drew one deduction which I was convinced was correct. The second ‘scandal’ she spoke of was not the same as the first—and it concerned herself!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Let us reconstruct. At four o’clock, Mrs. Inglethorp quarrels with her son, and threatens to denounce him to his wife—who, by the way, overheard the greater part of the conversation. At four-thirty, Mrs. Inglethorp, in consequence of a conversation on the validity of wills, makes a will in favour of her husband, which the two gardeners witness. At five o’clock, Dorcas finds her mistress in a state of considerable agitation, with a slip of paper—‘a letter,’ Dorcas thinks—in her hand, and it is then that she orders the fire in her room to be lighted. Presumably, then, between four-thirty and five o’clock, something has occurred to occasion a complete revolution of feeling, since she is now as anxious to destroy the will, as she was before to make it. What was that something?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“As far as we know, she was quite alone during that half-hour. Nobody entered or left that boudoir. What then occasioned this sudden change of sentiment?</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One can only guess, but I believe my guess to be correct. Mrs. Inglethorp had no stamps in her desk. We know this, because later she asked Dorcas to bring her some. Now in the opposite corner of the room stood her husband’s desk—locked. She was anxious to find some stamps, and, according to my theory, she tried her own keys in the desk. That one of them fitted I know. She therefore opened the desk, and in searching for the stamps she came across something else—that slip of paper which Dorcas saw in her hand, and which assuredly was never meant for Mrs. Inglethorp’s eyes. On the other hand, Mrs. Cavendish believed that the slip of paper to which her mother-in-law clung so tenaciously was a written proof of her own husband’s infidelity. She demanded it from Mrs. Inglethorp who assured her, quite truly, that it had nothing to do with that matter. Mrs. Cavendish did not believe her. She thought that Mrs. Inglethorp was shielding her stepson. Now Mrs. Cavendish is a very resolute woman, and, behind her mask of reserve, she was madly jealous of her husband. She determined to get hold of that paper at all costs, and in this resolution chance came to her aid. She happened to pick up the key of Mrs. Inglethorp’s despatch-case, which had been lost that morning. She knew that her mother-in-law invariably kept all important papers in this particular case.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Cavendish, therefore, made her plans as only a woman driven desperate through jealousy could have done. Some time in the evening she unbolted the door leading into Mademoiselle Cynthia’s room. Possibly she applied oil to the hinges, for I found that it opened quite noiselessly when I tried it. She put off her project until the early hours of the morning as being safer, since the servants were accustomed to hearing her move about her room at that time. She dressed completely in her land kit, and made her way quietly through Mademoiselle Cynthia’s room into that of Mrs. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>He paused a moment, and Cynthia interrupted:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I should have woken up if anyone had come through my room?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not if you were drugged, mademoiselle.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Drugged?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Mais, oui!</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You remember”—he addressed us collectively again—“that through all the tumult and noise next door Mademoiselle Cynthia slept. That admitted of two possibilities. Either her sleep was feigned—which I did not believe—or her unconsciousness was induced by artificial means.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“With this latter idea in my mind, I examined all the coffee-cups most carefully, remembering that it was Mrs. Cavendish who had brought Mademoiselle Cynthia her coffee the night before. I took a sample from each cup, and had them analysed—with no result. I had counted the cups carefully, in the event of one having been removed. Six persons had taken coffee, and six cups were duly found. I had to confess myself mistaken.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then I discovered that I had been guilty of a very grave oversight. Coffee had been brought in for seven persons, not six, for Dr. Bauerstein had been there that evening. This changed the face of the whole affair, for there was now one cup missing. The servants noticed nothing, since Annie, the housemaid, who took in the coffee, brought in seven cups, not knowing that Mr. Inglethorp never drank it, whereas Dorcas, who cleared them away the following morning, found six as usual—or strictly speaking she found five, the sixth being the one found broken in Mrs. Inglethorp’s room.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was confident that the missing cup was that of Mademoiselle Cynthia. I had an additional reason for that belief in the fact that all the cups found contained sugar, which Mademoiselle Cynthia never took in her coffee. My attention was attracted by the story of Annie about some ‘salt’ on the tray of cocoa which she took every night to Mrs. Inglethorp’s room. I accordingly secured a sample of that cocoa, and sent it to be analysed.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But that had already been done by Dr. Bauerstein,” said Lawrence quickly.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not exactly. The analyst was asked by him to report whether strychnine was, or was not, present. He did not have it tested, as I did, for a narcotic.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“For a narcotic?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Here is the analyst’s report. Mrs. Cavendish administered a safe, but effectual, narcotic to both Mrs. Inglethorp and Mademoiselle Cynthia. And it is possible that she had a <i>mauvais quart d’heure</i> in consequence! Imagine her feelings when her mother-in-law is suddenly taken ill and dies, and immediately after she hears the word ‘Poison’! She has believed that the sleeping draught she administered was perfectly harmless, but there is no doubt that for one terrible moment she must have feared that Mrs. Inglethorp’s death lay at her door. She is seized with panic, and under its influence she hurries downstairs, and quickly drops the coffee-cup and saucer used by Mademoiselle Cynthia into a large brass vase, where it is discovered later by Monsieur Lawrence. The remains of the cocoa she dare not touch. Too many eyes are upon her. Guess at her relief when strychnine is mentioned, and she discovers that after all the tragedy is not her doing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“We are now able to account for the symptoms of strychnine poisoning being so long in making their appearance. A narcotic taken with strychnine will delay the action of the poison for some hours.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot paused. Mary looked up at him, the colour slowly rising in her face.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“All you have said is quite true, Monsieur Poirot. It was the most awful hour of my life. I shall never forget it. But you are wonderful. I understand now——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What I meant when I told you that you could safely confess to Papa Poirot, eh? But you would not trust me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I see everything now,” said Lawrence. “The drugged cocoa, taken on top of the poisoned coffee, amply accounts for the delay.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly. But was the coffee poisoned, or was it not? We come to a little difficulty here, since Mrs. Inglethorp never drank it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What?” The cry of surprise was universal.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. You will remember my speaking of a stain on the carpet in Mrs. Inglethorp’s room? There were some peculiar points about that stain. It was still damp, it exhaled a strong odour of coffee, and imbedded in the nap of the carpet I found some little splinters of china. What had happened was plain to me, for not two minutes before I had placed my little case on the table near the window, and the table, tilting up, had deposited it upon the floor on precisely the identical spot. In exactly the same way, Mrs. Inglethorp had laid down her cup of coffee on reaching her room the night before, and the treacherous table had played her the same trick.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What happened next is mere guess work on my part, but I should say that Mrs. Inglethorp picked up the broken cup and placed it on the table by the bed. Feeling in need of a stimulant of some kind, she heated up her cocoa, and drank it off then and there. Now we are faced with a new problem. We know the cocoa contained no strychnine. The coffee was never drunk. Yet the strychnine must have been administered between seven and nine o’clock that evening. What third medium was there—a medium so suitable for disguising the taste of strychnine that it is extraordinary no one has thought of it?” Poirot looked round the room, and then answered himself impressively. “Her medicine!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you mean that the murderer introduced the strychnine into her tonic?” I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There was no need to introduce it. It was already there—in the mixture. The strychnine that killed Mrs. Inglethorp was the identical strychnine prescribed by Dr. Wilkins. To make that clear to you, I will read you an extract from a book on dispensing which I found in the Dispensary of the Red Cross Hospital at Tadminster:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“‘The following prescription has become famous in text books:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Strychninae Sulph. . . . . .</td>\n<td>1 gr.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Potass Bromide . . . . . . .</td>\n<td><sup>3</sup>vi</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Aqua ad. . . . . . . . . . . . .</td>\n<td><sup>3</sup>viii</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Fiat Mistura</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p><i>This solution deposits in a few hours the greater part of the strychnine salt as an insoluble bromide in transparent crystals. A lady in England lost her life by taking a similar mixture: the precipitated strychnine collected at the bottom, and in taking the last dose she swallowed nearly all of it!</i></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Now there was, of course, no bromide in Dr. Wilkins’ prescription, but you will remember that I mentioned an empty box of bromide powders. One or two of those powders introduced into the full bottle of medicine would effectually precipitate the strychnine, as the book describes, and cause it to be taken in the last dose. You will learn later that the person who usually poured out Mrs. Inglethorp’s medicine was always extremely careful not to shake the bottle, but to leave the sediment at the bottom of it undisturbed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Throughout the case, there have been evidences that the tragedy was intended to take place on Monday evening. On that day, Mrs. Inglethorp’s bell wire was neatly cut, and on Monday evening Mademoiselle Cynthia was spending the night with friends, so that Mrs. Inglethorp would have been quite alone in the right wing, completely shut off from help of any kind, and would have died, in all probability, before medical aid could have been summoned. But in her hurry to be in time for the village entertainment Mrs. Inglethorp forgot to take her medicine, and the next day she lunched away from home, so that the last—and fatal—dose was actually taken twenty-four hours later than had been anticipated by the murderer; and it is owing to that delay that the final proof—the last link of the chain—is now in my hands.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Amid breathless excitement, he held out three thin strips of paper.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“A letter in the murderer’s own hand-writing, <i>mes amis!</i> Had it been a little clearer in its terms, it is possible that Mrs. Inglethorp, warned in time, would have escaped. As it was, she realized her danger, but not the manner of it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>In the deathly silence, Poirot pieced together the slips of paper and, clearing his throat, read:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">Dearest Evelyn:<br>\n    ‘You will be anxious at hearing nothing. It is all right—only it will be to-night instead of last night. You understand. There’s a good time coming once the old woman is dead and out of the way. No one can possibly bring home the crime to me. That idea of yours about the bromides was a stroke of genius! But we must be very circumspect. A false step——’</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here, my friends, the letter breaks off. Doubtless the writer was interrupted; but there can be no question as to his identity. We all know this hand-writing and——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A howl that was almost a scream broke the silence.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You devil! How did you get it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>A chair was overturned. Poirot skipped nimbly aside. A quick movement on his part, and his assailant fell with a crash.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Messieurs, mesdames</i>,” said Poirot, with a flourish, “let me introduce you to the murderer, Mr. Alfred Inglethorp!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER XIII.<br>\nPOIROT EXPLAINS</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Poirot, you old villain,” I said, “I’ve half a mind to strangle you! What do you mean by deceiving me as you have done?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>We were sitting in the library. Several hectic days lay behind us. In the room below, John and Mary were together once more, while Alfred Inglethorp and Miss Howard were in custody. Now at last, I had Poirot to myself, and could relieve my still burning curiosity.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot did not answer me for a moment, but at last he said:</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I did not deceive you, <i>mon ami</i>. At most, I permitted you to deceive yourself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, it is difficult to explain. You see, my friend, you have a nature so honest, and a countenance so transparent, that—<i>enfin</i>, to conceal your feelings is impossible! If I had told you my ideas, the very first time you saw Mr. Alfred Inglethorp that astute gentleman would have—in your so expressive idiom—‘smelt a rat’! And then, <i>bonjour</i> to our chances of catching him!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I think that I have more diplomacy than you give me credit for.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My friend,” besought Poirot, “I implore you, do not enrage yourself! Your help has been of the most invaluable. It is but the extremely beautiful nature that you have, which made me pause.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well,” I grumbled, a little mollified. “I still think you might have given me a hint.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I did, my friend. Several hints. You would not take them. Think now, did I ever say to you that I believed John Cavendish guilty? Did I not, on the contrary, tell you that he would almost certainly be acquitted?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And did I not immediately afterwards speak of the difficulty of bringing the murderer to justice? Was it not plain to you that I was speaking of two entirely different persons?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I said, “it was not plain to me!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then again,” continued Poirot, “at the beginning, did I not repeat to you several times that I didn’t want Mr. Inglethorp arrested <i>now</i>? That should have conveyed something to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you mean to say you suspected him as long ago as that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. To begin with, whoever else might benefit by Mrs. Inglethorp’s death, her husband would benefit the most. There was no getting away from that. When I went up to Styles with you that first day, I had no idea as to how the crime had been committed, but from what I knew of Mr. Inglethorp I fancied that it would be very hard to find anything to connect him with it. When I arrived at the château, I realized at once that it was Mrs. Inglethorp who had burnt the will; and there, by the way, you cannot complain, my friend, for I tried my best to force on you the significance of that bedroom fire in midsummer.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, yes,” I said impatiently. “Go on.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, my friend, as I say, my views as to Mr. Inglethorp’s guilt were very much shaken. There was, in fact, so much evidence against him that I was inclined to believe that he had not done it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When did you change your mind?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I found that the more efforts I made to clear him, the more efforts he made to get himself arrested. Then, when I discovered that Inglethorp had nothing to do with Mrs. Raikes and that in fact it was John Cavendish who was interested in that quarter, I was quite sure.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Simply this. If it had been Inglethorp who was carrying on an intrigue with Mrs. Raikes, his silence was perfectly comprehensible. But, when I discovered that it was known all over the village that it was John who was attracted by the farmer’s pretty wife, his silence bore quite a different interpretation. It was nonsense to pretend that he was afraid of the scandal, as no possible scandal could attach to him. This attitude of his gave me furiously to think, and I was slowly forced to the conclusion that Alfred Inglethorp wanted to be arrested. <i>Eh bien!</i> from that moment, I was equally determined that he should not be arrested.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Wait a minute. I don’t see why he wished to be arrested?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because, <i>mon ami</i>, it is the law of your country that a man once acquitted can never be tried again for the same offence. Aha! but it was clever—his idea! Assuredly, he is a man of method. See here, he knew that in his position he was bound to be suspected, so he conceived the exceedingly clever idea of preparing a lot of manufactured evidence against himself. He wished to be arrested. He would then produce his irreproachable alibi—and, hey presto, he was safe for life!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I still don’t see how he managed to prove his alibi, and yet go to the chemist’s shop?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot stared at me in surprise.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Is it possible? My poor friend! You have not yet realized that it was Miss Howard who went to the chemist’s shop?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Miss Howard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But, certainly. Who else? It was most easy for her. She is of a good height, her voice is deep and manly; moreover, remember, she and Inglethorp are cousins, and there is a distinct resemblance between them, especially in their gait and bearing. It was simplicity itself. They are a clever pair!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I am still a little fogged as to how exactly the bromide business was done,” I remarked.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>Bon!</i> I will reconstruct for you as far as possible. I am inclined to think that Miss Howard was the master mind in that affair. You remember her once mentioning that her father was a doctor? Possibly she dispensed his medicines for him, or she may have taken the idea from one of the many books lying about when Mademoiselle Cynthia was studying for her exam. Anyway, she was familiar with the fact that the addition of a bromide to a mixture containing strychnine would cause the precipitation of the latter. Probably the idea came to her quite suddenly. Mrs. Inglethorp had a box of bromide powders, which she occasionally took at night. What could be easier than quietly to dissolve one or more of those powders in Mrs. Inglethorp’s large sized bottle of medicine when it came from Coot’s? The risk is practically nil. The tragedy will not take place until nearly a fortnight later. If anyone has seen either of them touching the medicine, they will have forgotten it by that time. Miss Howard will have engineered her quarrel, and departed from the house. The lapse of time, and her absence, will defeat all suspicion. Yes, it was a clever idea! If they had left it alone, it is possible the crime might never have been brought home to them. But they were not satisfied. They tried to be too clever—and that was their undoing.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot puffed at his tiny cigarette, his eyes fixed on the ceiling.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They arranged a plan to throw suspicion on John Cavendish, by buying strychnine at the village chemist’s, and signing the register in his hand-writing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“On Monday Mrs. Inglethorp will take the last dose of her medicine. On Monday, therefore, at six o’clock, Alfred Inglethorp arranges to be seen by a number of people at a spot far removed from the village. Miss Howard has previously made up a cock and bull story about him and Mrs. Raikes to account for his holding his tongue afterwards. At six o’clock, Miss Howard, disguised as Alfred Inglethorp, enters the chemist’s shop, with her story about a dog, obtains the strychnine, and writes the name of Alfred Inglethorp in John’s handwriting, which she had previously studied carefully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But, as it will never do if John, too, can prove an alibi, she writes him an anonymous note—still copying his hand-writing—which takes him to a remote spot where it is exceedingly unlikely that anyone will see him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“So far, all goes well. Miss Howard goes back to Middlingham. Alfred Inglethorp returns to Styles. There is nothing that can compromise him in any way, since it is Miss Howard who has the strychnine, which, after all, is only wanted as a blind to throw suspicion on John Cavendish.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But now a hitch occurs. Mrs. Inglethorp does not take her medicine that night. The broken bell, Cynthia’s absence—arranged by Inglethorp through his wife—all these are wasted. And then—he makes his slip.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Mrs. Inglethorp is out, and he sits down to write to his accomplice, who, he fears, may be in a panic at the non-success of their plan. It is probable that Mrs. Inglethorp returned earlier than he expected. Caught in the act, and somewhat flurried he hastily shuts and locks his desk. He fears that if he remains in the room he may have to open it again, and that Mrs. Inglethorp might catch sight of the letter before he could snatch it up. So he goes out and walks in the woods, little dreaming that Mrs. Inglethorp will open his desk, and discover the incriminating document.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But this, as we know, is what happened. Mrs. Inglethorp reads it, and becomes aware of the perfidy of her husband and Evelyn Howard, though, unfortunately, the sentence about the bromides conveys no warning to her mind. She knows that she is in danger—but is ignorant of where the danger lies. She decides to say nothing to her husband, but sits down and writes to her solicitor, asking him to come on the morrow, and she also determines to destroy immediately the will which she has just made. She keeps the fatal letter.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It was to discover that letter, then, that her husband forced the lock of the despatch-case?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and from the enormous risk he ran we can see how fully he realized its importance. That letter excepted, there was absolutely nothing to connect him with the crime.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There’s only one thing I can’t make out, why didn’t he destroy it at once when he got hold of it?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because he did not dare take the biggest risk of all—that of keeping it on his own person.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t understand.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Look at it from his point of view. I have discovered that there were only five short minutes in which he could have taken it—the five minutes immediately before our own arrival on the scene, for before that time Annie was brushing the stairs, and would have seen anyone who passed going to the right wing. Figure to yourself the scene! He enters the room, unlocking the door by means of one of the other doorkeys—they were all much alike. He hurries to the despatch-case—it is locked, and the keys are nowhere to be seen. That is a terrible blow to him, for it means that his presence in the room cannot be concealed as he had hoped. But he sees clearly that everything must be risked for the sake of that damning piece of evidence. Quickly, he forces the lock with a penknife, and turns over the papers until he finds what he is looking for.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But now a fresh dilemma arises: he dare not keep that piece of paper on him. He may be seen leaving the room—he may be searched. If the paper is found on him, it is certain doom. Probably, at this minute, too, he hears the sounds below of Mr. Wells and John leaving the boudoir. He must act quickly. Where can he hide this terrible slip of paper? The contents of the waste-paper-basket are kept and in any case, are sure to be examined. There are no means of destroying it; and he dare not keep it. He looks round, and he sees—what do you think, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I shook my head.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“In a moment, he has torn the letter into long thin strips, and rolling them up into spills he thrusts them hurriedly in amongst the other spills in the vase on the mantle-piece.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I uttered an exclamation.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No one would think of looking there,” Poirot continued. “And he will be able, at his leisure, to come back and destroy this solitary piece of evidence against him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then, all the time, it was in the spill vase in Mrs. Inglethorp’s bedroom, under our very noses?” I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Poirot nodded.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, my friend. That is where I discovered my ‘last link,’ and I owe that very fortunate discovery to you.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“To me?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Do you remember telling me that my hand shook as I was straightening the ornaments on the mantelpiece?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but I don’t see——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No, but I saw. Do you know, my friend, I remembered that earlier in the morning, when we had been there together, I had straightened all the objects on the mantelpiece. And, if they were already straightened, there would be no need to straighten them again, unless, in the meantime, someone else had touched them.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dear me,” I murmured, “so that is the explanation of your extraordinary behaviour. You rushed down to Styles, and found it still there?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, and it was a race for time.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But I still can’t understand why Inglethorp was such a fool as to leave it there when he had plenty of opportunity to destroy it.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Ah, but he had no opportunity. <i>I</i> saw to that.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. Do you remember reproving me for taking the household into my confidence on the subject?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Well, my friend, I saw there was just one chance. I was not sure then if Inglethorp was the criminal or not, but if he was I reasoned that he would not have the paper on him, but would have hidden it somewhere, and by enlisting the sympathy of the household I could effectually prevent his destroying it. He was already under suspicion, and by making the matter public I secured the services of about ten amateur detectives, who would be watching him unceasingly, and being himself aware of their watchfulness he would not dare seek further to destroy the document. He was therefore forced to depart from the house, leaving it in the spill vase.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But surely Miss Howard had ample opportunities of aiding him.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000004999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but Miss Howard did not know of the paper’s existence. In accordance with their prearranged plan, she never spoke to Alfred Inglethorp. They were supposed to be deadly enemies, and until John Cavendish was safely convicted they neither of them dared risk a meeting. Of course I had a watch kept on Mr. Inglethorp, hoping that sooner or later he would lead me to the hiding-place. But he was too clever to take any chances. The paper was safe where it was; since no one had thought of looking there in the first week, it was not likely they would do so afterwards. But for your lucky remark, we might never have been able to bring him to justice.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I understand that now; but when did you first begin to suspect Miss Howard?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“When I discovered that she had told a lie at the inquest about the letter she had received from Mrs. Inglethorp.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Why, what was there to lie about?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You saw that letter? Do you recall its general appearance?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes—more or less.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You will recollect, then, that Mrs. Inglethorp wrote a very distinctive hand, and left large clear spaces between her words. But if you look at the date at the top of the letter you will notice that ‘July 17th’ is quite different in this respect. Do you see what I mean?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I confessed, “I don’t.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You do not see that that letter was not written on the 17th, but on the 7th—the day after Miss Howard’s departure? The ‘1’ was written in before the ‘7’ to turn it into the ‘17th’.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“That is exactly what I asked myself. Why does Miss Howard suppress the letter written on the 17th, and produce this faked one instead? Because she did not wish to show the letter of the 17th. Why, again? And at once a suspicion dawned in my mind. You will remember my saying that it was wise to beware of people who were not telling you the truth.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And yet,” I cried indignantly, “after that, you gave me two reasons why Miss Howard could not have committed the crime!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And very good reasons too,” replied Poirot. “For a long time they were a stumbling-block to me until I remembered a very significant fact: that she and Alfred Inglethorp were cousins. She could not have committed the crime single-handed, but the reasons against that did not debar her from being an accomplice. And, then, there was that rather over-vehement hatred of hers! It concealed a very opposite emotion. There was, undoubtedly, a tie of passion between them long before he came to Styles. They had already arranged their infamous plot—that he should marry this rich, but rather foolish old lady, induce her to make a will leaving her money to him, and then gain their ends by a very cleverly conceived crime. If all had gone as they planned, they would probably have left England, and lived together on their poor victim’s money.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They are a very astute and unscrupulous pair. While suspicion was to be directed against him, she would be making quiet preparations for a very different <i>dénouement</i>. She arrives from Middlingham with all the compromising items in her possession. No suspicion attaches to her. No notice is paid to her coming and going in the house. She hides the strychnine and glasses in John’s room. She puts the beard in the attic. She will see to it that sooner or later they are duly discovered.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I don’t quite see why they tried to fix the blame on John,” I remarked. “It would have been much easier for them to bring the crime home to Lawrence.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, but that was mere chance. All the evidence against him arose out of pure accident. It must, in fact, have been distinctly annoying to the pair of schemers.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“His manner was unfortunate,” I observed thoughtfully.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes. You realize, of course, what was at the back of that?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You did not understand that he believed Mademoiselle Cynthia guilty of the crime?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No,” I exclaimed, astonished. “Impossible!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Not at all. I myself nearly had the same idea. It was in my mind when I asked Mr. Wells that first question about the will. Then there were the bromide powders which she had made up, and her clever male impersonations, as Dorcas recounted them to us. There was really more evidence against her than anyone else.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“You are joking, Poirot!”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“No. Shall I tell you what made Monsieur Lawrence turn so pale when he first entered his mother’s room on the fatal night? It was because, whilst his mother lay there, obviously poisoned, he saw, over your shoulder, that the door into Mademoiselle Cynthia’s room was unbolted.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But he declared that he saw it bolted!” I cried.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Exactly,” said Poirot dryly. “And that was just what confirmed my suspicion that it was not. He was shielding Mademoiselle Cynthia.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why should he shield her?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Because he is in love with her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I laughed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“There, Poirot, you are quite wrong! I happen to know for a fact that, far from being in love with her, he positively dislikes her.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Who told you that, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Cynthia herself.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“<i>La pauvre petite!</i> And she was concerned?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“She said that she did not mind at all.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Then she certainly did mind very much,” remarked Poirot. “They are like that—<i>les femmes!</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What you say about Lawrence is a great surprise to me,” I said.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But why? It was most obvious. Did not Monsieur Lawrence make the sour face every time Mademoiselle Cynthia spoke and laughed with his brother? He had taken it into his long head that Mademoiselle Cynthia was in love with Monsieur John. When he entered his mother’s room, and saw her obviously poisoned, he jumped to the conclusion that Mademoiselle Cynthia knew something about the matter. He was nearly driven desperate. First he crushed the coffee-cup to powder under his feet, remembering that <i>she</i> had gone up with his mother the night before, and he determined that there should be no chance of testing its contents. Thenceforward, he strenuously, and quite uselessly, upheld the theory of ‘Death from natural causes’.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And what about the ‘extra coffee-cup’?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I was fairly certain that it was Mrs. Cavendish who had hidden it, but I had to make sure. Monsieur Lawrence did not know at all what I meant; but, on reflection, he came to the conclusion that if he could find an extra coffee-cup anywhere his lady love would be cleared of suspicion. And he was perfectly right.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“One thing more. What did Mrs. Inglethorp mean by her dying words?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“They were, of course, an accusation against her husband.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Dear me, Poirot,” I said with a sigh, “I think you have explained everything. I am glad it has all ended so happily. Even John and his wife are reconciled.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Thanks to me.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“How do you mean—thanks to you?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“My dear friend, do you not realize that it was simply and solely the trial which has brought them together again? That John Cavendish still loved his wife, I was convinced. Also, that she was equally in love with him. But they had drifted very far apart. It all arose from a misunderstanding. She married him without love. He knew it. He is a sensitive man in his way, he would not force himself upon her if she did not want him. And, as he withdrew, her love awoke. But they are both unusually proud, and their pride held them inexorably apart. He drifted into an entanglement with Mrs. Raikes, and she deliberately cultivated the friendship of Dr. Bauerstein. Do you remember the day of John Cavendish’s arrest, when you found me deliberating over a big decision?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, I quite understood your distress.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Pardon me, <i>mon ami</i>, but you did not understand it in the least. I was trying to decide whether or not I would clear John Cavendish at once. I could have cleared him—though it might have meant a failure to convict the real criminals. They were entirely in the dark as to my real attitude up to the very last moment—which partly accounts for my success.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Do you mean that you could have saved John Cavendish from being brought to trial?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes, my friend. But I eventually decided in favour of ‘a woman’s happiness’. Nothing but the great danger through which they have passed could have brought these two proud souls together again.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I looked at Poirot in silent amazement. The colossal cheek of the little man! Who on earth but Poirot would have thought of a trial for murder as a restorer of conjugal happiness!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I perceive your thoughts, <i>mon ami</i>,” said Poirot, smiling at me. “No one but Hercule Poirot would have attempted such a thing! And you are wrong in condemning it. The happiness of one man and one woman is the greatest thing in all the world.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>His words took me back to earlier events. I remembered Mary as she lay white and exhausted on the sofa, listening, listening. There had come the sound of the bell below. She had started up. Poirot had opened the door, and meeting her agonized eyes had nodded gently. “Yes, madame,” he said. “I have brought him back to you.” He had stood aside, and as I went out I had seen the look in Mary’s eyes, as John Cavendish had caught his wife in his arms.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Perhaps you are right, Poirot,” I said gently. “Yes, it is the greatest thing in the world.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Suddenly, there was a tap at the door, and Cynthia peeped in.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—I only——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Come in,” I said, springing up.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>She came in, but did not sit down.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“I—only wanted to tell you something——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Yes?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Cynthia fidgeted with a little tassel for some moments, then, suddenly exclaiming: “You dears!” kissed first me and then Poirot, and rushed out of the room again.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What on earth does this mean?” I asked, surprised.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>It was very nice to be kissed by Cynthia, but the publicity of the salute rather impaired the pleasure.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“It means that she has discovered Monsieur Lawrence does not dislike her as much as she thought,” replied Poirot philosophically.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“But——”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Here he is.”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence at that moment passed the door.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“Eh! Monsieur Lawrence,” called Poirot. “We must congratulate you, is it not so?”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>Lawrence blushed, and then smiled awkwardly. A man in love is a sorry spectacle. Now Cynthia had looked charming.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>I sighed.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“What is it, <i>mon ami?</i>”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\">\n</div></div>"
        },
