            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/3cb6b9d5e88177c1/text/000005141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p>“And neither of them is for you?” finished Poirot. “Never mind. Console yourself, my friend. We may hunt together again, who knows? And then——”<br>\n<br></p></div></div>"
        },
