            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-fb4c94 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-a7aea7 twpub-3cb6b9d5e88177c1-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c16\"><div class=\"c2\">Project Gutenberg™ eBooks are often created from several printed editions, all of which are confirmed as not protected by copyright in the U.S. unless a copyright notice is included. Thus, we do not necessarily keep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</div></div></div>"
        },
